#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Requirements"
msgstr "Zahteve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To run &kile;, you need to have the following components installed on your "
"system:"
msgstr ""
"Da lahko zaženete &kile;, morate imeti na vašem sistemu nameščene naslednje "
"komponente:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"http://www.kde.org/\">K Desktop environment (&kde;)</ulink>: "
"&kde; is a popular open-source desktop environment."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"http://www.kde.org/\">K Desktop okolje (&kde;)</ulink>: &kde; "
"je priljubljeno odprtokodno namizno okolje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://qt.io/\">&Qt;</ulink>: &Qt; is a C++ &GUI; and network "
"library needed to compile &kile;."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://qt.io/\">&Qt;</ulink>: &Qt; je &GUI; za C++ in omrežna "
"knjižnica, ki je potrebna, da se prevede &kile;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"http://www.ctan.org/\">&latex;</ulink>: high-quality document "
"typesetting program. Most likely you want the &texlive; (or on older systems "
"the &tetex;) package, if you are on a &UNIX;-like system."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"http://www.ctan.org/\">&latex;</ulink>: zelo kvaliteten program "
"za sestavljanje dokumentov. Najbrž boste želeli paket &texlive; (ali &tetex; "
"na starejših sistemih), če uporabljate sistem podoben &UNIX;-u."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Most of these items might be included in your &Linux; distribution; please "
"refer to your distribution documentation, or refer to your installation &CD; "
"or DVD, for adding these packages to your computer."
msgstr ""
"Večina teh elementov je morda že vključenih v vašo distribucijo &Linux;-a; "
"prosimo, da si ogledate dokumentacijo vaše distribucije ali vaš &CD; ali DVD "
"za nameščanje, za dodajanje teh paketov na vaš računalnik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kile; might also be available as a pre-compiled package for your &Linux; "
"distribution already. Please check with the package manager of your "
"distribution."
msgstr ""
"&kile; je morda že na voljo tudi kot vnaprej preveden paket za vašo &Linux; "
"distribucijo. Preverite pri upravljalniku paketov vaše distribucije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid "Intended Audience"
msgstr "Predvideno občinstvo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This manual is intended for any individual, regardless of her or his "
"experience with &latex;, &kde;, &kile; or &Linux;."
msgstr ""
"Ta priročnik je namenjen vsakemu posamezniku, ne glede na njene/njegove "
"izkušnje z &latex;-om, &kde;-jem, &kile;-om ali &Linux;-om."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Advanced users are not likely to read this manual, but all suggestions on "
"documentation will be considered. If you would like to contribute to this "
"project or the documentation, please consult the <ulink url=\"http://kile."
"sourceforge.net/\">&kile; web page</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Napredni uporabniki verjetno ne bodo brali tega priročnika, vendar bodo "
"upoštevani vsi predlogi glede dokumentacije. Če bi želeli prispevati k temu "
"projektu ali dokumentaciji, se posvetujte z <ulink url=\"http://kile."
"sourceforge.net/\">&kile;-ovo spletno stranjo</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Do you need answers about &kile;? Are you stuck with the compilation "
"process? Do you want to see a new feature implemented? The preferred way to "
"ask technical questions or to start a discussion is to use our mailing list: "
"<email>kile-devel@lists.sourceforge.net</email>."
msgstr ""
"Potrebujete odgovore glede &kile;-a? Ste se zataknili pri procesu "
"prevajanja? Želite, da se uvede nova funkcija? Priporočen način za "
"spraševanje tehničnih vprašanj ali da začnete razpravo je, da uporabite naš "
"seznam e-poštnih naslovov: <email>kile-devel@lists.sourceforge.net</email>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "Basic facts"
msgstr "Osnovna dejstva"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid "About &kile;"
msgstr "O programu &kile;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kile; is an integrated &latex; environment for the &kde; desktop. &kile; "
"gives you the ability to use all the functionality of &latex; in a graphical "
"interface, giving you easy, immediate, and customized access to all programs "
"for &latex; code-completion, compiling, postprocessing, debugging, "
"conversion and viewing tools; you also get very handy wizards, a &latex; "
"reference and a powerful project manager."
msgstr ""
"&kile; je integrirano &latex;-ovo okolje za &kde;-jevo namizje. &kile; "
"ponuja zmožnost uporabe vseh funkcionalnosti &latex;-a z grafičnim "
"vmesnikom, kar vam omogoča enostaven, takojšen in prilagodljiv dostop do "
"vseh programov za dopolnjevanje &latex;-ove kode, prevajanje, naknadno "
"obdelavo, razhroščevanje in orodij za ogled; prav tako dobite zelo priročne "
"čarovnike, &latex;-ov priročnik in zmogljiv upravljalnik projektov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kile; and the &kate; Editor Component"
msgstr "&kile; in Urejevalna Komponenta &kate;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kile; is based on the &kate; editor component, &ie; a lot of its editing "
"capabilities stem from the &kate; editor component itself. &kile; extends "
"these capabilities with features to edit &latex; documents. To learn more "
"about the &kate; editor component and its capabilities, see the <ulink url="
"\"http://kate-editor.org\">&kate; webpage</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"&kile; je zasnovan na urejevalni komponenti &kate;, &ie; veliko njegovih "
"zmožnosti za urejanje izvirajo iz urejevalne komponente &kate;. &kile; "
"razširi te zmožnosti z značilnostmi za urejanje &latex;-ovih dokumentov. Če "
"želite izvedeti več o urejevalni komponenti &kate; in njenih zmožnostih, "
"glejte <ulink url=\"http://kate-editor.org\">spletno stran &kate;-a</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid "What is &latex;?"
msgstr "Kaj je &latex;?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&latex; is a text-processing system derived from &tex;, a program developed "
"originally in 1977 by Donald Knuth to help layout text in a professional way "
"and obtain a layout quality that is on a par with the work of a professional "
"typesetter. &latex; was created by Leslie Lamport to give authors an "
"automatic typesetter, especially to ease the expensive and painstaking "
"process of typesetting of mathematical formulas and expressions, which are "
"enclosed within dollar signs in &latex; <emphasis>for a reason</emphasis>. "
"Today, word-processing programs let any user act as typesetter, but what is "
"often needed is a document that simply looks good without having to spend "
"hours to bring it into shape. &latex; takes that burden on its shoulders, "
"and lets you concentrate on the document instead of on the layout. And yes, "
"it <emphasis>will</emphasis> look good!"
msgstr ""
"&latex; je sistem za procesiranje besedila, izpeljan iz &tex;-a, program, ki "
"ga je prvotno razvil Donald Knuth leta 1977, da bi pomagal pri razporeditvi "
"besedila na profesionalen način in pridobiti kakovost razporeditve, ki je na "
"ravni profesionalnega stavkarja (typesetter). &latex; je ustvaril Leslie "
"Lamport, da bi avtorjem ponudil samodejno stavkanje, posebno da bi olajšal "
"drag in mukotrpen proces oblikovanja matematičnih formul in izrazov, ki so v "
"&latex;-u med dvema znakoma za dolar <emphasis>z razlogom</emphasis>. "
"Današnji programi za procesiranje besed omogočajo vsakemu uporabniku, da "
"deluje kot stavkar, toda pogosto je potreben dokument, ki enostavno izgleda "
"lepo, brez da bi bilo potrebno zapraviti ure in ure, da ga ustrezno "
"oblikujemo. &latex; vam to delo olajša, da se vi lažje osredotočite na "
"vsebino dokumenta namesto na njegov izgled. In verjemite, da <emphasis>bo</"
"emphasis> izgledal lepo!"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do you pronounce it? Why that strange typesetting?"
msgstr "Kako se to izgovarja? Zakaj taka nenavadna oblika besede?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is a funny tradition of &tex;-related packages to have the strangest "
"pronunciation and typesetting possible. &tex; was supposed to be brought in "
"from the Greek <emphasis>τεχ</emphasis>, in Latin letters <emphasis>tech</"
"emphasis>. There are a lot of explanations why, but most likely it is "
"because &tex; was originally conceived for technical reports, and indeed its "
"foremost ability was the correct and easy typesetting of mathematical "
"formulae, then an extremely expensive, time-consuming and frustrating "
"business."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja hecna tradicija paketov, ki so povezani s &tex;, da imajo kolikor se "
"le da nenavadne izgovorjave in oblike. &tex; naj bi izviral iz Grškega "
"<emphasis>τεχ</emphasis>, v latinici <emphasis>tech</emphasis>. Veliko je "
"razlag zakaj, najbolj verjetna pa je, da je bil &tex; prvotno ustvarjen za "
"tehnična poročila in res, njegova najpomembnejša lastnost je pravilno in "
"enostavno oblikovanje matematičnih formul, kar je bile takrat ekstremno "
"drag, zamuden in nadležen posel."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The pronunciation is supposed to be as follows: <emphasis>T</emphasis> as "
"you would expect, <emphasis>E</emphasis> as in <emphasis>get</emphasis>, and "
"<emphasis>X</emphasis> as in the German i<emphasis>ch</emphasis>. If you do "
"not know what <emphasis>ch</emphasis> sounds like, it is more or less like "
"the sound a hissing cat produces; the IPA symbol is /ç/. Many people report "
"a different pronunciation of <emphasis>ach</emphasis> (IPA symbol /x/), but "
"according to some Greeks, the first version is indeed correct. You should be "
"aware that a lot of people mispronounce &tex; as /teks/ or /tek/."
msgstr ""
"Izgovorjava naj bi bila sledeča: <emphasis>T</emphasis> kot bi lahko "
"pričakovali, <emphasis>E</emphasis> kot v <emphasis>get</emphasis> in "
"<emphasis>X</emphasis> kot v nemškem i<emphasis>ch</emphasis>. Če ne veste "
"kako zveni <emphasis>ch</emphasis>, je bolj kot ne podoben zvoku pihajoče "
"mačke; IPA simbol je /ç/. Večina ljudi poroča o drugačnem izgovarjanju, "
"<emphasis>ach</emphasis> (IPA simbol /x/), toda po mnenju nekaterih Grkov je "
"v resnici pravilen prvi način. Zavedati se morate, da  veliko ljudi napačno "
"izgovarja &tex; kot /teks/ ali /tek/."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Last, in &latex; the first L<superscript>A</superscript> is pronounced as "
"<emphasis>lay</emphasis>: the idea being, while raw &tex; is difficult, even "
"a <emphasis>lay</emphasis>man can use &latex; macros. A less inspiring, but "
"more realistic explanation is that it stems from the surname of Leslie "
"Lamport, the creator of &latex;. Now you know!"
msgstr ""
"Nazadnje, L<superscript>A</superscript> na začetku v &latex; se izgovori kot "
"<emphasis>lay</emphasis>: kar predstavlja, da čeprav je &tex; zahteven, "
"lahko &latex; makrote uporablja tudi navaden <emphasis>lai</emphasis>k. Manj "
"zanimiva razlaga je, da LA izvira iz priimka Leslie-ja Lamport-a, "
"ustvarjalca &latex;-a. Zdaj veste!"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid "&latex; 101"
msgstr "&latex; 101"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &latex; typesetting system is similar to other markup languages such as "
"&XML;, which is used in many types of documents (including the one you are "
"reading), or &HTML;, which is used for web pages. The general idea behind "
"markup languages is to have special keywords, called <emphasis> tags</"
"emphasis>, that tell a program (a word processor, a web browser, or the "
"&latex; compiler) how the text enclosed within the tags is to be "
"interpreted. &kile; offers a number of such tags in the <guimenu>LaTeX</"
"guimenu> menu in the menu bar."
msgstr ""
"&latex;-ov sistem za stavkanje je podoben drugim jezikom z značkami, kot na "
"primer &XML;, ki se ga uporablja v veliko različnih vrstah dokumentov "
"(vključno s tem, ki ga trenutno berete), ali &HTML;, ki se ga uporablja za "
"spletne strani. Splošna ideja jezikov z značkami je, da obstajajo posebne "
"ključne besede, imenovane <emphasis>značke</emphasis>, po katerih lahko "
"program (urejevalnik besedil, spletni brskalnik ali &latex;-ov prevajalnik) "
"ve, kako naj interpretira besedilo med značkami. &kile; ponuja številne "
"takšne oznake v <guimenu>LaTeX</guimenu>-a v vrstici menija."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"While we will try to give you a good idea of what &latex; is, this document "
"is, of course, not The Definitive Book on &latex;. If you want to learn "
"&latex; in depth, you may want to borrow a specialized book from your local "
"library."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav vam bomo poskusili čim bolje opisati, kaj je &latex;, ta dokument "
"vseeno ni Dokončna Knjiga o &latex;-u. Če se želite podrobno naučiti "
"&latex;, si morda izposodite za to specializirano knjigo iz bližnje "
"knjižnice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As with any other markup language, &latex; documents contain a "
"<emphasis>preamble</emphasis>, which defines global properties, such as "
"paper size, page numbering, dimensions of the text on the page, and a "
"document <emphasis>body</emphasis>, which contains the text of the document. "
"The preamble is composed at least of the <userinput>\\documentclass</"
"userinput> command. It precedes the document body, which starts with the "
"command <userinput>\\begin{document}</userinput> and is concluded with the "
"command <userinput>\\end{document}</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Kot pri vsakem drugem jeziku z značkami, je tudi pri &latex;-ovih dokumentih "
"vsebovana <emphasis>preambula</emphasis>, ki definira globalne lastnosti, "
"kot si velikost papirja, številčenje strani in dimenzije besedila na strani, "
"poleg tega pa tudi <emphasis>telo</emphasis> dokumenta, ki vsebuje besedilo "
"dokumenta. Preambula je sestavljena vsaj iz ukaza <userinput>"
"\\documentclass</userinput>. Je pred telesom dokumenta, ta pa se začne z "
"ukazom <userinput>\\begin{document}</userinput> in zaključi z ukazom "
"<userinput>\\end{document}</userinput>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kile;'s Main Features"
msgstr "Glavne Lastnosti &kile;-a"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:249 index.docbook:1705
#, no-c-format
msgid "QuickStart Wizard"
msgstr "Čarovnik za Hiter Začetek (QuickStart Wizard)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The QuickStart wizard built into &kile; is a useful feature to quickly start "
"creating documents in &kile;. Choosing the wizard from the menubar gives you "
"several choices for the creation of your document. You can also specify some "
"options related to the document right away."
msgstr ""
"Čarovnik za hiter začetek je vgrajen v &kile; in je uporabna lastnost, da "
"hitro začnete ustvarjati dokumente v &kile;-u. Uporaba čarovnika iz vrstice "
"menija vam ponuja nekaj možnosti za ustvarjanje vašega dokumenta. Prav tako "
"lahko takoj navedete nekaj možnosti povezane z dokumentom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid "Class options:"
msgstr "Možnosti razreda:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Document Class</guilabel>: choose the type of document you want to "
"create: article, book, letter, report, scrartcl, scrreprt, scrbook, prosper, "
"beamer or other custom-defined."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Razred Dokumenta</guilabel>: izberite vrsto dokumenta, ki ga "
"želite ustvariti: članek, knjiga, pismo, poročilo, scrartcl, scrreprt "
"scrbook, prosper, beamer ali druge poljubno definirane vrste."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Typeface Size</guilabel>: tell &kile; what point size (pt) you "
"want to use."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Velikost črk</guilabel>: povejte &kile;-u, kakšno velikost črk "
"(pt) želite uporabljati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Paper Size</guilabel>: choose the size or style of sheets."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Velikost Papirja</guilabel>: izberite velikost ali slog strani."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Encoding</guilabel>: In general it is a good idea to use your "
"system's standard encoding. Modern systems now move more and more to UTF-8 "
"as the standard encoding. If you can, use utf8 or utf8x (which is indeed the "
"correct spelling for &latex; documents)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Kodiranje znakov</guilabel>: Ponavadi je dobro uporabljati "
"standardno kodiranje vašega sistema. Moderni sistemi vedno bolj prevzemajo "
"UTF-8 za standardno kodiranje. Če lahko, uporabite utf8 ali utf8x (ki je "
"pravilno črkovanje za dokumente &latex;)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Other options</guilabel>: this allows you to set further options "
"such as printing, draft, and others."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Druge možnosti</guilabel>: to vam omogoča, da nastavite nadaljnje "
"možnosti, kot so tiskanje, osnutek in drugo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid "Packages"
msgstr "Paketi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This lists some of the most common additional packages used in &latex;. "
"Select the check box to include it."
msgstr ""
"Tu je navedenih nekaj najpogostejših dodatnih paketov uporabljenih v &latex;-"
"u. Označite polje, da ga vključite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid "Document Properties:"
msgstr "Lastnosti Dokumenta:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:278
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Author</guilabel>: put your name here."
msgstr "<guilabel>Avtor</guilabel>: sem vnesite svoje ime."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Title</guilabel>: add the document title here."
msgstr "<guilabel>Naslov</guilabel>: sem dodajte naslov dokumenta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Date</guilabel>: specify the date."
msgstr "<guilabel>Datum</guilabel>: navedite datum."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:287
#, no-c-format
msgid "Predefined Templates"
msgstr "Vnaprej Določene Predloge"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid "The predefined templates in &kile; are:"
msgstr "Vnaprej določene predloge v &kile;-u so:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "Empty document: real freaks start from scratch!"
msgstr "Empty document (prazen dokument): le redki začnejo od začetka!"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Article: sets the article format, for a document short enough not to be "
"broken down to chapters."
msgstr ""
"Article (članek): nastavi format članka, za dokument, ki je dovolj kratek, "
"da se ga ne razdeli na poglavja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Report: sets the report format, for a middle-sized document, with, for "
"example, page numbering on the page's outer edge."
msgstr ""
"Report (poročilo): nastavi format poročila, za srednje velike dokumente, z "
"npr. številčenjem strani na zunanjem robu strani."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Book: sets the book format, a full-fledged flavor, so powerful that it is "
"used to write many university textbooks."
msgstr ""
"Book (knjiga): nastavi format knjige, poln okus, tako močan, da se uporablja "
"za pisanje številnih univerzitetnih učbenikov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid "Letter: sets the letter format."
msgstr "Letter (pismo): nastavi format pisma."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Beamer, HA-Prosper: create nice presentations in PDF with a superior look "
"and all &latex; power."
msgstr ""
"Beamer, HA-Prosper: ustvari lepe predstavitve v PDF-ju z vrhunskim videzom "
"in vso zmogljivostjo &latex;-a."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Powerdot: Powerdot is the follower of the packages <userinput>seminar</"
"userinput> and <userinput>HA-Prosper</userinput>. It does not have as many "
"options as Beamer, but it is easy to use and it can create really nice "
"presentations in PDF."
msgstr ""
"Powerdot: Powerdot je naslednik paketoma <userinput>seminar</userinput> in "
"<userinput>HA-Prosper</userinput>. Nima toliko možnosti kot Beamer, vendar "
"je enostaven za uporabo in lahko ustvari res lepe predstavitve v PDF formatu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Scrartcl, Scrbook, Scrreprt, Scrlttr2: the KOMA-Script document classes, "
"especially adapted to German typography. Use them whenever you write German "
"texts."
msgstr ""
"Scrartcl, Scrbook, Scrreprt, Scrlttr2: razredi z dokumenti KOMA-Script, "
"posebej prilagojeni nemški tipografiji. Uporabljajte jih, ko pišete nemška "
"besedila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Xelatex: a modified <userinput>Article</userinput> template to use with "
"<userinput>XeLaTeX</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Xelatex: predloga (template) za <userinput>Članke</userinput> za uporabo z "
"<userinput>XeLaTeX</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that all of these templates can be adjusted to the user's requirements."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da so vse te predloge prilagodljive uporabnikovim potrebam."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"New users need not worry: this list is just a brief description of the "
"available features, and a more detailed description can be found in <xref "
"linkend=\"quickstart\" role=\"select: title pageabbrv\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Novi uporabniki ne rabijo skrbeti: ta seznam je le kratek opis "
"razpoložljivih funkcij. Njihove podrobnejše opise lahko najdete v <xref "
"linkend=\"quickstart\" role=\"select: title pageabbrv\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Syntax Highlighting"
msgstr "Poudarjanje Sintakse"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:323
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kile; is similar to other programs that deal with source code and editing, "
"and will automatically highlight commands, options and items that are used "
"(and abused). &kile; makes it possible to easily spot problematic areas: for "
"example, if you see major areas of text turn green, it is likely that you "
"forgot to close a math environment somewhere."
msgstr ""
"&kile; je podoben drugim programom za izvorno kodo ter urejanje in bo "
"samodejno poudaril ukaze, možnosti in elemente, ki so uporabljeni (ali "
"napačno rabljeni). S &kile;-om boste z lahkoto opazili problematična "
"območja: npr. če se vam velik del besedila obarva zeleno, ste najbrž nekje "
"pozabili zapreti območje za matematiko."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid "Auto-Completion of Environments"
msgstr "Samodopolnjevanje Območij"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The auto-completion of environments means that, when you begin a new "
"environment by typing <userinput>\\begin{environment}</userinput>, &kile; "
"will automatically insert a matching <userinput>\\end{environment}</"
"userinput> command, with a line in between them for your text. You can of "
"course deactivate it if you want in <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure Kile...</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>LaTeX</"
"guimenuitem><guilabel>Environments</guilabel></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Samodopolnjevanje območij pomeni, da ko odprete novo območje v vpisom "
"<userinput>\\begin{environment}</userinput>, bo &kile; samodejno vstavil "
"ujemajoč ukaz <userinput>\\end{environment}</userinput> s prazno vrstico med "
"ukazoma za vaše besedilo. To možnost lahko seveda onemogočite v "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Nastavi Kile...</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>LaTeX</guimenuitem><guilabel>Environments</"
"guilabel></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid "Jump to Structure Element"
msgstr "Skoči na Element Strukture"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:347
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All documents are normally structured in a hierarchy of some type. &latex; "
"allows you to break up documents into the following hierarchy (part being "
"highest in the hierarchy, and subparagraph being lowest):"
msgstr ""
"Vsi dokumenti so ponavadi strukturirani v neke vrste hierarhiji. &latex; vam "
"omogoča, da dokument razdelite v skladu s sledečo hierarhijo (part je "
"najvišje v hierarhiji in subparagraph je najnižje):"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:352
#, no-c-format
msgid "\\part"
msgstr "\\part"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid "\\chapter"
msgstr "\\chapter"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:354
#, no-c-format
msgid "\\section"
msgstr "\\section"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:355
#, no-c-format
msgid "\\subsection"
msgstr "\\subsection"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid "\\subsubsection"
msgstr "\\subsubsection"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:357
#, no-c-format
msgid "\\paragraph"
msgstr "\\paragraph"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid "\\subparagraph"
msgstr "\\subparagraph"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:361
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When viewing a document in the <guilabel>Structure</guilabel> view, you can "
"jump between elements by clicking on the element you would like to view."
msgstr ""
"Ko gledate dokument v pogledu <guilabel>Struktura</guilabel>, lahko skačete "
"med elementi s klikom na element, ki ga želite videti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid "Inverse Search"
msgstr "Obratno Iskanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:370
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When creating your own &latex; files, inverse search can be very helpful. "
"Once you have created a &DVI; file (DeVice Independent File) or PDF file, "
"you can click the left mouse button while pressing &Shift; in the viewer and "
"&kile; will jump to the corresponding line in the &latex; source code."
msgstr ""
"Obratno iskanje je lahko zelo uporabno, ko ustvarjate svoje datoteke "
"&latex;. Ko ste enkrat že ustvarili &DVI; (DeVice Independent File) ali PDF "
"datoteko, lahko z držanjem tipke &Shift; in levim klikom na razdelek v oknu "
"s predogledom skočite na ustrezno vrstico &latex;-ove izvorne kode."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A &DVI; is a type of file containing a description of a formatted document, "
"along with other information including character font, and is besides PDF "
"the usual output of &tex; or &latex;. A number of utilities exist to view, "
"convert and print &DVI; files on various systems and devices."
msgstr ""
"&DVI; je vrsta datoteke, ki vsebuje opis formatiranega dokumenta poleg "
"drugih informacij kot npr. vrsta pisave, in je poleg PDF-ja običajen izhod "
"programov &tex; in &latex;. Obstaja veliko raznih pripomočkov za ogled, "
"pretvorbo in tiskanje datotek &DVI; na različnih sistemih in napravah."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid "Forward Search"
msgstr "Iskanje Naprej"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:387
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When using inverse search, the selection of items in the &DVI; or PDF file "
"is associated with the editor, so when you click on the &DVI; or PDF file, "
"the main window jumps to the corresponding section of &latex; code in the "
"editor. Forward search is the exact opposite of this. Forward search will "
"allow you to click on a specific section of text in the &latex; code, and "
"jump to the associated position in the viewer window."
msgstr ""
"Ko uporabljate obratno iskanje, je izbira elementov v &DVI; ali PDF datoteki "
"povezana z urejevalnikom, zato, ko kliknete na &DVI; ali PDF datoteko, bo "
"glavno okno skočilo na ustrezen razdelek &latex;-ove kode v urejevalniku. "
"Iskanje naprej je pravo nasprotje tega. Iskanje naprej vam omogoča, da "
"kliknete na določen razdelek besedila v &latex;-ovi kodi, in okno s "
"predogledom se bo premaknilo na ujemajočo se lokacijo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:399
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Toolbar"
msgstr "Orodna Vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>New</guibutton>: begin a new document."
msgstr "<guibutton>Nov</guibutton>: ustvari nov dokument."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:403
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Open</guibutton>: open a new document."
msgstr "<guibutton>Odpri</guibutton>: odpre nov dokument."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:404
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Close</guibutton>: close your document."
msgstr "<guibutton>Zapri</guibutton>: zapre vaš dokument."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Define document as master</guibutton>: this is used when working "
"with multiple files. Having a master document will let you work more easily "
"with other <literal role=\"extension\">.tex</literal> files included in your "
"document. If you are using projects, you can also set in "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Project</guimenu><guisubmenu>Project Options</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> a project-wide master document."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Določi dokument kot glavni</guibutton>: to se uporablja, ko se "
"dela z več datotekami. Če boste imeli glavni dokument, boste lažje delali z "
"ostalimi <literal role=\"extension\">.tex</literal> datotekami, ki so "
"vključene v vaš dokument. Če delate s projekti, lahko v "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Project</guimenu><guisubmenu>Project Options</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> nastavite tudi glavni dokument le za projekt."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:410
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Quickbuild</guibutton>: compiles your &latex; source code and "
"displays the results automatically unless there are errors contained in the "
"document."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Quickbuild</guibutton>: prevede vašo &latex;-ovo izvorno kodo in "
"samodejno prikaže rezultate, razen če pride do napak v dokumentu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:412
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Watch file mode</guibutton>: this mode will \"watch\" the &DVI; "
"file for changes, and will not launch a new session of &okular; after "
"<guibutton>Quickbuild</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Način ogleda datoteke</guibutton>: ta način bo \"opazoval\" "
"datoteko &DVI; za spremembe, in ne bo zagnal nove seje &okular;-ja po "
"<guibutton>Quickbuild</guibutton>-u."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>View logfile</guibutton>: views the <literal role=\"extension\">."
"log</literal> file, so you can spot errors."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Oglej si log datoteko</guibutton>: odpre pogled na <literal role="
"\"extension\">.log</literal> datoteko, da najdete napako."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:416
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Previous error</guibutton>: jumps backward through the <literal "
"role=\"extension\">.log</literal> file and highlights errors in the source."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Prejšnje napake</guibutton>: skoči nazaj skozi <literal role="
"\"extension\">.log</literal> datoteko in označi napake v viru."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:419
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Next error</guibutton>: jumps forward through the <literal role="
"\"extension\">.log</literal> file and highlights errors in the source."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Naslednja napaka</guibutton>: skoči naprej skozi<literal role="
"\"extension\">.log</literal> datoteko in označi napake v viru."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:422
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Stop</guibutton>: halts current tool."
msgstr "<guibutton>Ustavi</guibutton>: ustavi trenutno orodje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:423
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>LaTeX</guibutton>: runs &latex; on the active document."
msgstr "<guibutton>LaTeX</guibutton>: zažene &latex; na aktivnem dokumentu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:424
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>ViewDVI</guibutton>: launches &DVI; viewer."
msgstr "<guibutton>ViewDVI</guibutton>: odpre pogled za &DVI; datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:425
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>DVItoPS</guibutton>: converts a &DVI; to a &PostScript; (PS)."
msgstr "<guibutton>DVItoPS</guibutton>: pretvori &DVI; v &PostScript; (PS)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:426
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>ViewPS</guibutton>: launches &PostScript; (PS) viewer."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>ViewPS</guibutton>: odpre pogled za &PostScript; (PS) datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:427
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>PDFLaTeX</guibutton>: runs &pdflatex; on the active document."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>PDFLaTeX</guibutton>: zažene &pdflatex; na aktivnem dokumentu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:428
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>ViewPDF</guibutton>: launches the PDF viewer."
msgstr "<guibutton>ViewPDF</guibutton>: odpre pogled za PDF datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:429
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>DVItoPDF</guibutton>: converts a &DVI; to a PDF."
msgstr "<guibutton>DVItoPDF</guibutton>: pretvori &DVI; v PDF."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:430
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>PStoPDF</guibutton>: converts a PS to a PDF."
msgstr "<guibutton>PStoPDF</guibutton>: pretvori PS v PDF."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:431
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>ViewHTML</guibutton>: views &HTML; created."
msgstr "<guibutton>ViewHTML</guibutton>: za ogled ustvarjenih &HTML; datotek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>ForwardDVI</guibutton>: jump to the page of the &DVI; file that "
"corresponds to the current line in the editor."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>ForwardDVI</guibutton>: skoči na stran &DVI; datoteke, ki se "
"ujema s trenutno vrstico v urejevalniku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:433
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>ForwardPDF</guibutton>: jump to the page of the PDF file that "
"corresponds to the current line in the editor."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>ForwardPDF</guibutton>: skoči na stran PDF datoteke, ki se ujema "
"s trenutno vrstico v urejevalniku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:436
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you look at the <guilabel>Edit</guilabel> toolbar, you will notice three "
"large drop-down menus. The drop-down menus were designed for you to be able "
"to quickly add certain common features into your document. The first drop "
"down box is used for quickly dividing your document by parts, chapter, "
"sections and so on; the available commands to add segments to your &latex; "
"source code are:"
msgstr ""
"Če pogledate na orodno vrstico <guilabel>Uredi</guilabel> boste opazili tri "
"velike spustne menije. Ti meniji so bili zasnovani, da lahko hitro dodajate "
"nekatere navadne funkcije v svoj dokument. Prvi je namenjen, da lahko hitro "
"razdelite dokument na dele, poglavja, razdelke itd.; razpoložljivi ukazi za "
"dodajanje segmentov v vašo izvorno kodo so:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:443
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>part</guilabel>: highest level of sectioning for a document."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>part</guilabel>: (del) najvišja stopnja razdeljevanja dokumenta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:444
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>chapter</guilabel>: starts a new chapter."
msgstr "<guilabel>chapter</guilabel>: (poglavje) začne z novim poglavjem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:445
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>section</guilabel>: create a new section."
msgstr "<guilabel>section</guilabel>: (razdelek) ustvari nov razdelek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:446
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>subsection</guilabel>: create a new subsection."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>subsection</guilabel>: (podrazdelek) ustvari nov podrazdelek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>subsubsection</guilabel>: a secondary section between subsection "
"and paragraph."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>subsubsection</guilabel>: (podpodrazdelek) ustvari nov "
"podpodrazdelek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:449
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>paragraph</guilabel>: create a new paragraph."
msgstr "<guilabel>paragraph</guilabel>: (odstavek) ustvari nov odstavek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:450
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>subparagraph</guilabel>: create a new subparagraph."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>subparagraph</guilabel>: (pododstavek) ustvari nov pododstavek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:453
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The drop down box named <guilabel>Other</guilabel> is used to insert items "
"into your document such as indexes, footnotes, and references; the available "
"commands are:"
msgstr ""
"Spustni meni z imenom <guilabel>Ostalo</guilabel> je namenjena vstavljanju "
"elementov v vaš dokument, kot npr. kazala, opombe, reference; razpoložljivi "
"ukazi so:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:457
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>label</guilabel>: a command that produces a label for a chapter, a "
"figure or another element."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>label</guilabel>: (oznaka) ukaz, ki ustvari oznako za poglavje ali "
"kak drug element."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:459
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>index</guilabel>: creates an entry for the index."
msgstr "<guilabel>index</guilabel>: (kazalo) ustvari vnos v kazalo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:460
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>footnote</guilabel>: creates a footnote in your document."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>footnote</guilabel>: (opomba) ustvari opombo v vašem dokumentu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:461
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>ref</guilabel>: used to refer to a predefined label, which you can "
"choose from a drop-down list."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>ref</guilabel>: uporablja se za sklicevanje na vnaprej določeno "
"oznako, ki jo lahko izberete na spustnem seznamu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:463
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>pageref</guilabel>: just like <guilabel>ref</guilabel>, but refers "
"to a page instead of a structure element."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>pageref</guilabel>: tako kot <guilabel>ref</guilabel>, le da se "
"nanaša na stran namesto na element strukture."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>cite</guilabel>: create a reference with data from a bibliography."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>cite</guilabel>: ustvari referenco s podatki iz bibliografije."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:472
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The <guilabel>Other</guilabel> drop-down menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Spustni meni <guilabel>Ostalo</guilabel></screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:478
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The <guilabel>Other</guilabel> drop-down menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Spustni meni <guilabel>Ostalo</guilabel></phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:480
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>The <guilabel>Other</guilabel> drop-down menu</para>"
msgstr "<para>Spustni meni <guilabel>Ostalo</guilabel></para>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:485
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Selecting the label for a reference</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Izbira oznake za referenco</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Selecting the label for a reference</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Izbira oznake za referenco</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:493
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Selecting the label for a reference</para>"
msgstr "<para>Izbira oznake za referenco</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:497
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When using <guilabel>cite</guilabel>, you are presented with a drop-down "
"list of bibitems, but if you are using &bibtex; this will only work if the "
"file belongs to a Project. For editing &bibtex; files the usage of "
"specialized editors is recommended. The author has had good results with "
"&kbibtex;. Of course you can also write the &bibtex; files by hand inside "
"&kile;."
msgstr ""
"Ko uporabljate <guilabel>cite</guilabel>, se vam odpre spustni seznam "
"bibliotečnih elementov, če pa uporabljate &bibtex;, bo to delovalo le, če "
"vaša datoteka pripada k projektu. Za urejanje datotek &bibtex; je "
"priporočena uporaba specializiranih urejevalnikov. Avtor je imel dobre "
"izkušnje z &kbibtex;-om. Seveda lahko prav tako sami napišete &bibtex; "
"datoteko v &kile;-u."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:502
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The last drop down box labeled <guilabel>tiny</guilabel> is used to set the "
"size of the text. You can set the size of the main text, of footnotes, and "
"so on. The available commands are:"
msgstr ""
"Zadnji spustni meni, označen z <guilabel>tiny</guilabel> (majhen), se "
"uporablja za nastavitev velikosti besedila. Nastavite lahko velikost "
"glavnega besedila, opomb itd. Razpoložljivi ukazi so:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:506
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>tiny</guilabel>: smallest."
msgstr "<guilabel>tiny</guilabel>: najmanjše."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:507
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>scriptsize</guilabel>: very small."
msgstr "<guilabel>scriptsize</guilabel>: zelo majhno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:508
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>footnotesize</guilabel>: smaller."
msgstr "<guilabel>footnotesize</guilabel>: manjše."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:509
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>small</guilabel>: small."
msgstr "<guilabel>small</guilabel>: majhno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:510
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>normalsize</guilabel>: normal."
msgstr "<guilabel>normalsize</guilabel>: normalno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:511
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>large</guilabel>: large."
msgstr "<guilabel>large</guilabel>: veliko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:512
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Large</guilabel>: larger."
msgstr "<guilabel>Large</guilabel>: večje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:513
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>LARGE</guilabel>: even larger."
msgstr "<guilabel>LARGE</guilabel>: še večje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:514
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>huge</guilabel>: still larger."
msgstr "<guilabel>huge</guilabel>: še vedno večje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:515
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Huge</guilabel>: largest."
msgstr "<guilabel>Huge</guilabel>: največje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:523
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quickstart"
msgstr "Quickstart (Hitri začetek)"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:527
#, no-c-format
msgid "Writing a &latex; Document with &kile; for Beginners"
msgstr "Pisanje &latex;-ovega dokumenta s programom &kile; za Začetnike"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:529
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Users of &kile; have two choices when starting a new document: they can use "
"the <guimenu>Wizard</guimenu> to begin a new document, select the type of "
"document they would like to create and options such as font size, paper "
"size, and so on; otherwise, they can write the code by hand."
msgstr ""
"Kdor uporablja &kile;, ima dve možnosti, ko začenja nov dokument: lahko "
"uporabi funkcijo <guimenu>Wizard</guimenu>, da začne z novim dokumentom, "
"izbere vrsto dokumenta, ki bi ga rad ustvaril, in razne druge možnosti, kot "
"npr. velikost pisave, velikost papirja; v nasprotnem primeru lahko ročno "
"napiše kodo."

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:534
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\\documentclass[12pt]{article}\n"
"\\begin{document}\n"
"        Here is a bunch of text coded in \\LaTeX.\n"
"\\end{document}"
msgstr ""
"\\documentclass[12pt]{article}\n"
"\\begin{document}\n"
"        Here is a bunch of text coded in \\LaTeX.\n"
"\\end{document}"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:536
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Every document in &latex; begins with the command <userinput> "
"\\documentclass[optional argument]{class}</userinput>, where class specifies "
"the document type."
msgstr ""
"Vsak dokument v &latex;-u se začne z ukazom <userinput> "
"\\documentclass[neobvezni argument]{razred}</userinput>, kjer razred določa "
"vrsto dokumenta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:539
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Typing in the code example above from the text box gives you the following "
"output:"
msgstr ""
"Če vtipkate primer kode iz zgornjega okvirčka, boste dobili naslednji "
"rezultat:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:542
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Compiled text in &DVI; output</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Compiled text in &DVI; output</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:548
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Compiled text in &DVI; output</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Prevedeno besedilo v izhodu &DVI;</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:550
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Compiled text in &DVI; output</para>"
msgstr "<para>Prevedeno besedilo v izhodu &DVI;</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:554
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The brackets that come after the command <userinput>\\documentclass</"
"userinput> contain the options for the command. The option "
"<userinput>[12pt]</userinput> sets the size of the font for your article; if "
"you do not set the font size in the beginning, you can set it later in the "
"text."
msgstr ""
"Oklepaji takoj za ukazom <userinput>\\documentclass</userinput> vsebujejo "
"možnosti za ukaz. Možnost <userinput>[12pt]</userinput> nastavi velikost "
"pisave za vaš članek; če ne nastavite velikosti pisave na začetku, jo lahko "
"nastavite kasneje v besedilu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:559
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you have typed in the code example from the box above, you will need to "
"compile your &latex; source code. The easiest way for you to compile &latex; "
"is to use the <guimenu>Build</guimenu> menu, or using the "
"<guilabel>Quickbuild</guilabel> button."
msgstr ""
"Ko ste enkrat vpisali primer kode iz zgornjega okvirčka, morate prevesti "
"vašo &latex;-ovo izvorno kodo. Najlažji način, da prevedete &latex;, je da "
"uporabite meni <guimenu>Build</guimenu> ali pa da uporabite gumb "
"<guilabel>Quickbuild</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:563
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>2</keycap></keycombo> is the keyboard shortcut to "
"compile your source code."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>2</keycap></keycombo> je bližnjica za prevajanje "
"izvorne kode."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:566
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You have to save your source code before you can compile; &kile; will do "
"this automatically for you."
msgstr ""
"Izvorno kodo morate pred prevajanjem shraniti; &kile; vam to naredi "
"samodejno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:568
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If your document did not compile, check the log for errors. When using the "
"<guilabel>Quickbuild</guilabel> key, the &okular; viewer should be launched "
"automatically; if it does not, look at the log."
msgstr ""
"Če se vaš dokument ni prevedel, preverite okvirček za beleženje napak. Ko "
"uporabljate funkcijo <guilabel>Quickbuild</guilabel>, se bo pogled &okular; "
"zagnal samodejno; če se ne, poglejte okvirček za beleženje napak."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:574 index.docbook:1537
#, no-c-format
msgid "Environments"
msgstr "Območja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:576
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An environment is a segment of text that is managed differently from the "
"rest of the document. For example, you create a report with font size 12, "
"but you need to change your font size for a few sentences. The commands "
"<userinput>\\begin{environment}</userinput>, <userinput>\\huge</userinput> "
"and <userinput>\\end{environment}</userinput> will let you temporarily alter "
"the text inside the environment commands to be size huge."
msgstr ""
"Območje je del besedila, ki se ga obdela na drugačen način kot preostanek "
"dokumenta, npr. ustvarite lahko poročilo z velikostjo pisave 12, vendar "
"želite spremeniti velikost pri nekaterih stavkih. Z ukazi <userinput>"
"\\begin{environment}</userinput>, <userinput>\\huge</userinput> and "
"<userinput>\\end{environment}</userinput> boste spremenili besedilo v "
"območju, da bo veliko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:583
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Changes are only effective from <userinput>\\begin{environment}</userinput> "
"to <userinput>\\end{environment}</userinput>. There are no limits as to how "
"many changes you can make inside an environment."
msgstr ""
"Spremembe so učinkovite le od <userinput>\\begin{environment}</userinput> do "
"<userinput>\\end{environment}</userinput>. Ni omejitev, koliko sprememb "
"lahko naredite v enem območju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:587
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are many features you can add to your document that will make it more "
"readable and user-friendly. You can add features such as specific fonts, "
"bold, italics, underline &etc; to your document, and these commands will end "
"with either an <userinput>\\end</userinput> command, or at the end of your "
"environment."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja veliko funkcij, ki jih lahko uporabite v svojem dokumentu, da bo "
"bolj berljiv in uporabniku prijazen. Lahko dodate lastnosti kot so krepka, "
"ležeča, podčrtana pisava, določene oblike pisave, &etc;, in ti ukazi se bodo "
"končali z ukazom <userinput>\\end</userinput> ali pa s koncem vašega območja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:593
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>\\begin{emph}</userinput>: this command makes text italicized, "
"and is valid until the code comes across a <userinput>\\end{emph}</"
"userinput>, or another environment. To italicize one word in a sentence, you "
"can use the syntax: this is <userinput>\\emph{my}</userinput> sentence."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>\\begin{emph}</userinput>: ta ukaz naredi besedilo ležeče, in je "
"veljaven do ukaza <userinput>\\end{emph}</userinput> ali do drugega območja. "
"Da naredite ležečo le eno besedo v povedi lahko uporabite naslednjo "
"sintakso: to je <userinput>\\emph{my}</userinput> poved."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:597
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>\\textbf{I am making this text inside the brackets bold}</"
"userinput>: this command makes your text bold."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>\\textbf{To besedilo v oklepajih bo napisano krepko}</userinput>: "
"s tem ukazom naredite, da bo besedilo krepko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:599
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>\\quote</userinput>: to create a quote inside your document; "
"begin your quote with <userinput>\\begin{quote}</userinput> and end it with "
"<userinput>\\end{quote}</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>\\quote</userinput>: tako ustvarite citat v svojem dokumentu; "
"začnite vaš citat z <userinput>\\begin{quote}</userinput> in ga končajte z "
"<userinput>\\end{quote}</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:601
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>\\center</userinput>: centers the text."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>\\center</userinput>: uporabi sredinsko poravnavo na besedilu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:602
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>\\verse</userinput>: creates offset text for poems."
msgstr "<userinput>\\verse</userinput>: ustvari zamaknjeno besedilo za pesmi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:603
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>\\itemize</userinput>: makes an itemized list."
msgstr "<userinput>\\itemize</userinput>: ustvari seznam po alinejah."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:610
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &kile;"
msgstr "Uporaba &kile;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:612
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now that we have given you some background about how to write code using the "
"&latex; markup language, we will show you how to create a document using "
"&kile; step-by-step."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj ko smo vam predstavili nekaj osnov kako pisati &latex;-ovo kodo, vam "
"bomo pokazali kako s &kile;-om ustvariti dokument korak za korakom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:617
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start &kile;."
msgstr "Zaženite &kile;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:618
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <menuchoice><guimenu>Wizard</guimenu><guimenuitem>Quick Start</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, then choose a format, and set your preferences in "
"the wizard."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Wizard</guimenu><guimenuitem>Quick Start</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, nato izberite želeni format in nastavite svoje "
"preference."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:620
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once the wizard has entered text, do some customization to make the document "
"more readable, add a minimum of one quote, some bold text, italics, and a "
"verse to see the difference between the commands."
msgstr ""
"Ko je wizard vnesel besedilo, prilagodite svoje besedilo, da bo lažje "
"berljivo, dodajte vsaj en citat, nekaj krepkega in ležečega besedila ter "
"verz, da vidite razlike med ukazi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:623
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save your file, and give it the name <filename>intro.tex</filename>."
msgstr "Shranite datoteko in ji dajte ime <filename>intro.tex</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:624
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Build your document using <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>2</keycap></keycombo>, or "
"the button labeled <guilabel>LaTeX</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Zgradite svoj dokument z <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>2</keycap></keycombo> ali s "
"klikom na gumb <guilabel>LaTeX</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:626
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select <guibutton>ViewDVI</guibutton>."
msgstr "Izberite <guibutton>ViewDVI</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:627
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check out all your new text."
msgstr "Preverite vaše novo besedilo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:628
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you are done viewing your document, click the <guibutton>Editor View</"
"guibutton> button or press <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> to "
"return to the editor if you are using the embedded viewer, or close the "
"viewer window if you are using a separate viewer."
msgstr ""
"Ko ste končali z ogledovanjem dokumenta, kliknite na gumb <guibutton>Editor "
"View</guibutton> ali pritisnite <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></"
"keycombo>, da se vrnete v urejevalnik, če uporabljate vgrajen "
"pregledovalnik, ali pa le zaprite okno pregledovalnika, če uporabljate "
"ločeni pregledovalnik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:634
#, no-c-format
msgid "That's it! You have just created your first &latex; document!"
msgstr "To je to! Pravkar ste ustvarili svoj prvi &latex;-ov dokument!"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:636
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you have created your &DVI;, you will be able to print your document, "
"or change it into a &PostScript; or PDF file if you want. Experiment and "
"have fun!"
msgstr ""
"Ko enkrat ustvarite vaš &DVI;, boste lahko svoj dokument tudi natisnili ali "
"pa ga spremenili v datoteko &PostScript; ali PDF. Eksperimentirajte in "
"zabavajte se!"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:643
#, no-c-format
msgid "&DVI; Files"
msgstr "&DVI; Datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:645
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&DVI; stands for <emphasis>DeVice Independent</emphasis> file. These files "
"are produced by &tex; or &latex; to be read by a driver of some sort on your "
"computer. There are many different types of output that a <literal role="
"\"extension\">.dvi</literal> can be sent to, such as a printer, &PostScript; "
"or PDF file converter, or your computer screen."
msgstr ""
"&DVI; je kratica za datoteko neodvisno od naprave (<emphasis>DeVice "
"Independent</emphasis>). Te datoteke naredi &tex; ali &latex;, da jih "
"prebrere nekakšen gonilnik v vašem računalniku. Obstaja veliko različnih "
"vrst izhodov, na katere je možno poslati datoteko <literal role=\"extension"
"\">.dvi</literal>, kot na primer tiskalnik, pretvornik datotek &PostScript; "
"in PDF, ali zaslon vašega računalnika."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:651
#, no-c-format
msgid "Viewing a &DVI;"
msgstr "Ogled datoteke &DVI;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:653
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You have already seen how to view a &DVI; file on the screen by using the "
"<guibutton>ViewDVI</guibutton> button in the toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Do sedaj ste že videli, kako si ogledate datoteko &DVI; na zaslonu z uporabo "
"gumba <guibutton>ViewDVI</guibutton> iz orodne vrstice."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:659
#, no-c-format
msgid "Printing a &DVI;"
msgstr "Tiskanje datoteke &DVI;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:661
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To print a &DVI;, you can use the same process that you used to create your "
"document earlier (see <xref linkend=\"quick_using\" role=\"select: title "
"pageabbrv\"/>). At step 7, after clicking <guibutton>ViewDVI</guibutton>, "
"select <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Print</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> in the viewer, and if you have your printer properly configured, "
"you will be able to print the &DVI;."
msgstr ""
"Da natisnete &DVI;, lahko uporabite isti postopek, kot ste ga prej uporabili "
"za ustvarjanje vašega dokumenta (glej <xref linkend=\"quick_using\" role="
"\"select: title pageabbrv\"/>). Na koraku 7, potem ko ste kliknili "
"<guibutton>ViewDVI</guibutton>, izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Print</guimenuitem></menuchoice> v pregledovalniku, in "
"če imate pravilno nastavljen vaš tiskalnik, boste lahko natisnili &DVI;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:672
#, no-c-format
msgid "Converting &DVI; files"
msgstr "Pretvorba &DVI; datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:674
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The toolbar gives the options of Converting a &DVI; to other formats. Once "
"you have created a &DVI; from your &latex; source code, you will be able to "
"export it to a format of your choice using the toolbar buttons."
msgstr ""
"Orodna vrstica vam daje možnost, da pretvorite &DVI; v druge formate. Ko ste "
"ustvarili datoteko &DVI; iz vaše &latex;-ove izvorne kode, jo boste lahko "
"izvozili v druge formate z uporabo gumbov v orodni vrstici."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:684
#, no-c-format
msgid "Forward Search between &kile; and &okular;"
msgstr "Iskanje Naprej med &kile;-om in &okular;-jem"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:686
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The forward search functions allow you to jump from your editor directly to "
"the associated position of the &DVI; or PDF file."
msgstr ""
"Funkcije za iskanje naprej vam omogočajo, da iz vašega urejevalnika skočite "
"neposredno na ustrezen položaj v datoteki &DVI; ali PDF."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:689
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kile; offers a configuration with this option for all &latex; binaries. Go "
"to <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure Kile...</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Tools</guimenuitem><guilabel>Build</guilabel></"
"menuchoice> and always choose the <guilabel>Modern</guilabel> configuration."
msgstr ""
"&kile; ponuja konfiguracio s to možnostjo za vse &latex;-ove binarne "
"datoteke. Pojdite na <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Nastavi Kile...</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Tools</"
"guimenuitem><guilabel>Build</guilabel></menuchoice> in povsod izberite "
"konfiguracijo <guilabel>Modern</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:694
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To execute a forward search, position the cursor on a line of source code, "
"and click with the <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> mouse button while "
"pressing &Shift;, or click <guilabel>Forward DVI</guilabel>/"
"<guilabel>Forward PDF</guilabel> to jump to the associated position in the "
"&DVI; or PDF viewer window."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izvesti iskanje naprej, postavite kazalec na vrstico izvorne kode "
"in kliknite z <mousebutton>levim</mousebutton> gumbom miške, medtem ko "
"pritiskate &Shift;, ali kliknite <guilabel>Posreduj DVI</guilabel>/"
"<guilabel> Posreduj PDF</guilabel> za skok na povezan položaj v &DVI; ali "
"okno pregledovalnika PDF."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:701
#, no-c-format
msgid "Inverse Search between &kile; and &okular;"
msgstr "Iskanje nazaj med &kile;-om in &okular;-jem"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:703
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Inverse search is a very useful feature when you are writing a &latex; "
"document yourself. If everything is set up properly, you can click into "
"&okular;'s window with the <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> mouse button "
"while pressing &Shift;. After that &kile; loads the &latex; source file and "
"jumps to the proper paragraph. To use inverse search, you have to compile "
"your &latex; file with the <guilabel>Modern</guilabel> configuration."
msgstr ""
"Obratno iskanje je zelo uporabna funkcija, ko sami pišete &latex;-ov "
"dokument. Če je vse nastavljeno pravilno, lahko kliknete na okno &okular;-ja "
"z <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> gumbom miške, medtem ko držite &Shift;. "
"Nato bo &kile; naložil &latex;-ovo izvorno kodo in skočil na pravilen "
"odstavek. Da lahko uporabljate obratno iskanje, morate prevesti vašo &latex;-"
"ovo datoteko s konfiguracijo <guilabel>Modern</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:708
#, no-c-format
msgid "Inverse search cannot work unless:"
msgstr "Obratno iskanje ne bo delovalo, razen če:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:711
#, no-c-format
msgid "The source file has been compiled successfully."
msgstr "Je bila izvorna datoteka uspešno prevedena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:712
#, no-c-format
msgid "&okular; knows which editor you would like to use."
msgstr "&okular; ve, kateri urejevalnik želite uporabljati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:715
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With this feature of &okular;, a left mouse click while pressing &Shift; in "
"the &DVI; or PDF document will result in &kile; opening the corresponding "
"&latex; document and attempt to go to the corresponding line. Remember to "
"tell &okular; to use &kile; as a text editor, in &okular;'s menu item "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Okular...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (on the page <guimenuitem>Editor</guimenuitem>)."
msgstr ""
"S to funkcijo &okular;ja bo levi klik na &DVI; ali PDF med pritiskanjem "
"tipke &Shift; odprl ustrezen &latex;-ov dokument v &kile;-u in poskusil "
"poiskati ustrezno vrstico kode. Ne pozabite povedati &okular;-ju, naj kot "
"urejevalnik uporablja &kile;. To storite v meniju &okular;-ja "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Nastavi Okular...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (na strani <guimenuitem>Urejevalnik</guimenuitem>)."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:722
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Configuring &okular;</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Nastavljanje &okular;-ja</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:728
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Configuring &okular;</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Nastavljanje &okular;-ja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:730
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Configuring &okular;</para>"
msgstr "<para>Nastavljanje &okular;-ja</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:737
#, no-c-format
msgid "Resolving Errors"
msgstr "Razreševanje Napak"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:739
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are trying to use quickbuild, and the &DVI; viewer does not open, "
"chances are you have an error. If you have an error, it will be visible in "
"the log file / message area, and the summary of the error will be given."
msgstr ""
"Če poskušate uporabljati quickbuild in se vam &DVI; pregledovalnik ne odpre, "
"obstaja možnost, da imate napako. Če imate napako, bo to razvidno v okvirčku "
"za beleženje napak/sporočil. Podan bo tudi povzetek napake."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:743
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The log file will explain the source of the error in your code. In the "
"editor, you can use the buttons in the toolbar labeled <guibutton>Previous "
"LaTeX Error</guibutton> and <guibutton>Next LaTeX Error</guibutton> to jump "
"to and from errors. The log file always states in which line the error "
"occurred. To view the line where an error occurred, click on the error in "
"the log window, and &kile; will take you to the error's line."
msgstr ""
"V datoteki za beleženje bo pojasnjen izvor napake v vaši kodi. V "
"urejevalniku lahko uporabite gumbe orodne vrstice <guibutton>Previous LaTeX "
"Error</guibutton> and <guibutton>Next LaTeX Error</guibutton>, da skačete od "
"napake do napake. V datoteki za beleženje je vedno zabeleženo, v kateri "
"vrstici se je pojavila napaka. Da si ogledate to vrstico, kliknite na napako "
"v okvirčku za beleženje napak in &kile; vam bo prikazal vrstico s to napako."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:754
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starting a New Document"
msgstr "Začenjanje z Novim Dokumentom"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:756
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you click the button in the toolbar to begin a new document a dialog "
"appears, asking which type of template you would like to use to write your "
"document. The default choices are:"
msgstr ""
"Ko kliknete na gumb iz orodne vrstice, da začnete nov dokument, se prikaže "
"pogovorno okno, ki vas povpraša po vrsti predloge, ki bi jo želeli uporabiti "
"pri pisanju vašega dokumenta. Privzete izbire so:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:761
#, no-c-format
msgid "Empty document"
msgstr "Prazen dokument"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:762
#, no-c-format
msgid "Article"
msgstr "Članek (Article)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:763
#, no-c-format
msgid "Beamer"
msgstr "Beamer"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:764
#, no-c-format
msgid "Book"
msgstr "Knjiga (Book)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:765
#, no-c-format
msgid "HA-Prosper"
msgstr "HA-Prosper"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:766
#, no-c-format
msgid "Powerdot"
msgstr "Powerdot"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:767
#, no-c-format
msgid "Letter"
msgstr "Pismo (Letter)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:768
#, no-c-format
msgid "Report"
msgstr "Poročilo (Report)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:769
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scrartcl (from the KOMA-Script package)"
msgstr "Scrartcl (iz paketa KOMA-Script)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:770
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scrbook (from the KOMA-Script package)"
msgstr "Scrbook (iz paketa KOMA-Script)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:771
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scrlttr2 (from the KOMA-Script package)"
msgstr "Scrlttr2 (iz paketa KOMA-Script)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:772
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scrreprt (from the KOMA-Script package)"
msgstr "Scrreprt (iz paketa KOMA-Script)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:773
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>PDF</para>"
msgstr "<para>PDF</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:774
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>XeLaTeX</para>"
msgstr "<para>XeLaTeX</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:777
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you selected an <guilabel>Empty document</guilabel>, you can either start "
"writing a document from scratch, or you can use the wizard to quickly start "
"a new document (see <xref linkend=\"intro_docwizard\" role=\"select: title "
"pageabbrv\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"Če ste izbrali <guilabel>Prazen dokument</guilabel>, lahko začnete pisati "
"dokument od začetka, ali pa uporabite wizard, da hitreje začnete nov "
"dokument (glej <xref linkend=\"intro_docwizard\" role=\"select: title "
"pageabbrv\"/>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:784
#, no-c-format
msgid "Templates"
msgstr "Predloge"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:786
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Frequent users of &latex; typically use the same preamble for almost every "
"document they use. Templates can be created, saved and loaded within &kile; "
"to make it easier to start a new document."
msgstr ""
"Redni uporabniki &latex;-a ponavadi uporabljajo enake preambule za skoraj "
"vsak njihov dokument. Predloge se da ustvariti, shraniti in naložiti v "
"&kile;-u, in si tako olajšati začenjanje novih dokumentov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:791
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a New Template"
msgstr "Ustvari Novo Predlogo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:793
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a new template, you must first either open a &tex; / &latex; file, "
"or create a file of your own. &kile; can generate a template from an "
"existing document by opening the desired document and selecting "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Create Template from "
"Document</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Da ustvarite novo predlogo, morate najprej odpreti datoteko &tex; / &latex; "
"ali pa sami ustvariti datoteko. &kile; lahko ustvari predlogo iz obstoječega "
"dokumenta tako, da odprete želeni dokument in izberete "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Create Template from "
"Document</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:801
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring Automatic Substitutions"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje Samodejnih Zamenjav"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:803
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When creating a new document by selecting a template from "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>, certain character combinations will be replaced by data such as "
"your name, or the character encoding you are using. These variables can be "
"configured in <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure "
"Kile...</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Settings</guimenuitem><guilabel>General</"
"guilabel></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Ko ustvarjate nov dokument s pomočjo predloge in "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Nov</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>, bodo določene kombinacije znakov zamenjane s podatki, kot so "
"vaše ime ali kodiranje znakov, ki ga uporabljate. Te spremenljivke se lahko "
"nastavi v <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Nastavi "
"Kile...</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Nastavitve</guimenuitem><guilabel>Splošno</"
"guilabel></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:810
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When designing your own template, it is useful to know which character "
"combinations are replaced by which template variables:"
msgstr ""
"Ko oblikujete svojo predlogo, je uporabno vedeti, katere kombinacije znakov "
"se zamenjajo s katerimi spremenljivkami:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:814
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>$$AUTHOR$$</userinput>: This string will be replaced by the "
"author variable."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>$$AUTHOR$$</userinput>: Ta niz se bo zamenjal s spremenljivko "
"avtor."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:816
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>$$DOCUMENTCLASSOPTIONS$$</userinput>: This string will be "
"replaced by the documentclass options variable. Typically this is used as "
"follows: <userinput>\\documentclass[$$DOCUMENTCLASSOPTIONS$$]{article}</"
"userinput>."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>$$DOCUMENTCLASSOPTIONS$$</userinput>: Ta niz se bo zamenjal s "
"spremenljivko možnosti vrste dokumenta. To se ponavadi uporablja tako: "
"<userinput>\\documentclass[$$DOCUMENTCLASSOPTIONS$$]{article}</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:819
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>$$INPUTENCODING$$</userinput>: If the inputencoding variable is "
"set to, say, <userinput>latin1</userinput> this string is replaced by "
"<userinput>\\input[latin1]{inputenc}</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>$$INPUTENCODING$$</userinput>: Če je spremenljivka kodiranja "
"vnosa nastavljena na recimo <userinput>latin1</userinput>, se bo ta niz "
"zamenjal z <userinput>\\input[latin1]{inputenc}</userinput>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:828
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a Template from the Wizard"
msgstr "Ustvari Predlogo s pomočjo Wizarda"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:830
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The easiest way to create a new template is to start the wizard, and then "
"add commands in the editor. Once you have your document set up the way you "
"like:"
msgstr ""
"Novo predlogo se najlažje ustvari tako, da začnete wizard in nato dodate "
"ukaze v urejevalnik. Ko ste ustvarili vaš dokument tako kot želite:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:835
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save your file;"
msgstr "Shranite datoteko;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:836
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to <guimenu>File</guimenu>;"
msgstr "Pojdite na <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu>;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:837
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choose <guimenuitem>Create Template from Document</guimenuitem>;"
msgstr "Izberite <guimenuitem>Create Template from Document</guimenuitem>;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:838
#, no-c-format
msgid "Make any corrections necessary to the template;"
msgstr "Napravite zadnje popravke na predlogi;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:839
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter a name for your new template;"
msgstr "Vnesite ime za vašo novo predlogo;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:840
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click <guibutton>OK</guibutton> to add your template to the menu."
msgstr "Kliknite <guibutton>OK</guibutton>, da dodate vašo predlogo v meni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:843
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Next time you start up a new document, you will be able to choose your "
"customized template instead of the default ones."
msgstr ""
"Ko boste naslednjič začenjali z novim dokumentom, boste lahko izbrali svojo "
"prilagojeno predlogo namesto privzetih."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:850
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating a Template from any File"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje Predloge iz katerekoli Datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:852
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A template can be created from any &latex; file. If you are looking for an "
"easy way to configure a template, go find one you like on the Internet and "
"follow the same steps as listed in <xref linkend=\"templ_wiz\" role="
"\"select: title pageabbrv\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Predlogo se da ustvariti iz katerekoli &latex;-ove datoteke. Če iščete "
"enostaven način, da nastavite predlogo, poiščite tisto, ki vam je všeč, na "
"Internetu in sledite istim korakom, ki so navedeni v <xref linkend="
"\"templ_wiz\" role=\"select: title pageabbrv\"/>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:856
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For instance, you may want to create a full-fledged A0 poster. These posters "
"are usually seen at scientific conferences, and &latex; will help you make "
"an attractive, catchy poster. Remember that you will need the "
"<filename>a0poster</filename> package, which is normally not included in "
"standard &tex; distributions. Download it from <ulink url=\"http://www.ctan."
"org/tex-archive/macros/latex/contrib/a0poster/\">here</ulink> and place it "
"in the same folder as your &latex; file."
msgstr ""
"Na primer, morda bi želeli ustvariti vsebine poln plakat A0. Take plakate "
"običajno vidimo na znanstvenih konferencah, in &latex; vam bo pomagal "
"narediti privlačen in poglede vzbujajoč plakat. Ne pozabite, da boste "
"potrebovali paket <filename>a0poster</filename>, ki običajno ni vključen v "
"standardne &tex; distribucije. Prenesete ga <ulink url=\"http://www.ctan.org/"
"tex-archive/macros/latex/contrib/a0poster/\">tukaj</ulink> in ga postavitev "
"isto mapo kot vašo mapo &latex;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:864
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removing a Template"
msgstr "Odstranjevanje Predloge"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:866
#, no-c-format
msgid "To remove a template from &kile;, do as follows:"
msgstr "Če želite odstraniti predlogo iz &kile;-a, storite naslednje:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:869
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go to <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Remove Template...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>;"
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Remove "
"Template...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:871
#, no-c-format
msgid "A dialog box will appear with all templates listed: select a template;"
msgstr ""
"Odprlo se bo pogovorno okno s seznamom vseh predlog: izberite predlogo;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:872
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click <guilabel>OK</guilabel>, and your template will be removed."
msgstr "Kliknite <guilabel>OK</guilabel> in predloga bo odstranjena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:875
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Templates marked with an asterisk (*) cannot be removed without the proper "
"permission."
msgstr ""
"Predlog označenih z zvezdico (*) ni mogoče odstraniti brez posebnega "
"dovoljenja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:884
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing &latex; Documents"
msgstr "Urejanje &latex;-ovih Dokumentov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:886
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The internal editor that &kile; uses is &kate;. &kate; is a text editor "
"created for programmers, which incorporates the ability to read and "
"highlight many different types of text files, among which are &latex; and "
"&bibtex;; you can access many options for &kate; directly from &kile;'s "
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Notranji urejevalnik, ki ga uporablja &kile;, je &kate;. &kate; je "
"urejevalnik besedil ustvarjen za programerje, ki vključuje zmožnost branja "
"in označevanja veliko različnih vrst besedilnih datotek, med katerimi so "
"tudi &latex; in &bibtex;; do veliko možnosti za nastavljanje &kate;-a lahko "
"dostopate neposredno iz &kile;-ovega menija <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:891
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To learn more about &kate; and its capabilities, see the <ulink url=\"help:/"
"kate\">&kate; Handbook</ulink>. &kile; users can start reading from the "
"chapter <quote>Working with the &kate; Editor</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Če se želite podrobneje spoznati s programom &kate; in njegovimi "
"zmogljivostmi, glejte <ulink url=\"help:/kate\">&kate;-ov Priročnik</ulink>. "
"Uporabniki &kile;-a lahko začnejo z branjem pri poglavju <quote>Delo z "
"Urejevalnikom &kate;</quote>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:896
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &latex; Reference"
msgstr "&latex;-ova referenčni priročnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:898
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kile; features a very practical &latex; tag reference, which you can access "
"by choosing <menuchoice><guimenu>Help</guimenu><guimenuitem>LaTeX Reference</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. It contains a thorough description of almost all "
"the commands that you may use in &latex; and their syntax."
msgstr ""
"&kile; vključuje zelo praktično referenco &latex;-ovih značk, ki je dostopna "
"preko <menuchoice><guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu><guimenuitem>LaTeX Reference</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Vsebuje temeljit opis skoraj vseh ukazov, ki jih "
"boste morda uporabljali v &latex;-u, in njihovo sintakso."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:907
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cursor Movements"
msgstr "Premiki Kazalca Miške"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:909
#, no-c-format
msgid "To select text, you have the following options:"
msgstr "Da izberete besedilo, imate naslednje možnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:912
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hold left mouse button, and drag mouse to highlight text."
msgstr "Držite levi gumb miške in povlecite miško, da označite besedilo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:913
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click once on a word to move the cursor to a new area."
msgstr "Kliknite enkrat na besedo, da premaknete kazalec v novo območje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:914
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click twice on a word to select the whole word."
msgstr "Kliknite dvakrat na besedo, da izberete celo besedo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:915
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click twice on a word and pressing <keycombo>&Ctrl;</keycombo> to select the "
"whole &tex; word. This means clicking in this way on <userinput>\\par</"
"userinput> from <userinput>\\par\\bigskip</userinput> only select \\par."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite dvakrat na besedo in pritisnite <keycombo>&Ctrl;</keycombo>, da "
"izberete celo &tex; besedo. Če boste kliknili na ta način na <userinput>"
"\\par</userinput> v nizu <userinput>\\par\\bigskip</userinput>, boste "
"izbrali le \\par."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:917
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click three times to select the whole sentence."
msgstr "Kliknite trikrat, da izberete celo poved."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:920
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Holding the left mouse button, and dragging the text you want to select, "
"automatically copies the selected text to the clipboard."
msgstr ""
"Če držite levi gumb miške in vlečete besedilo, ki ste ga izbrali, se bo to "
"besedilo samodejno kopiralo v odložišče."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:923
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Holding &Shift; and using the arrow keys allows you to select portions of "
"the source code in the editor window."
msgstr ""
"Z držanjem tipke &Shift; in uporabljanjem puščic na tipkovnici lahko "
"izberete dele izvorne kode v oknu urejevalnika."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:930
#, no-c-format
msgid "Brackets"
msgstr "Oklepaji"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:932
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Bracket completion is a visual tool that the editor view uses to indicate to "
"you which bracket matches which. If you open any <literal role=\"extension"
"\">.tex</literal> file, and select any bracket, whether it be a parenthesis "
"(), square brackets [] or braces {}, the editor will highlight the bracket "
"and its match in yellow (this default color can be changed). So, for "
"example, if you position the cursor on the braces in <userinput>"
"\\section{Introduction}</userinput>, you would see <userinput>"
"\\section{Introduction}</userinput> in the default yellow highlight, showing "
"you the location of the beginning and ending brackets."
msgstr ""
"Dokončanje oklepaja je vizualno orodje, ki ga urejevalnik uporablja za "
"prikaz, kateri oklepaj se ujema s katerim. Če odprete katerokoli datoteko "
"<literal role=\"extension\">.tex</literal> in izberete katerikoli oklepaj, "
"ne glede na to, ali je to navadni oklepaj (), oglati oklepaj [] ali zaviti "
"oklepaj {}, bo urejevalnik označil oklepaj in njegov par z rumeno (to barvo "
"lahko poljubno nastavite). Na primer če postavite kazalec miške na zaviti "
"oklepaj v nizu <userinput>\\section{Introduction}</userinput>, boste videli "
"<userinput>\\section{Introduction}</userinput> v privzeti rumeni barvi, ki "
"vam označuje lokacijo začetnega in končnega oklepaja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:945
#, no-c-format
msgid "Highlighting"
msgstr "Poudarjanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:947
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kile; has the ability to look for and highlight different types of code. "
"For example, &latex; commands are distinguished from normal text, and math "
"formulas are also highlighted in a different color."
msgstr ""
"&kile; ima zmožnost iskanja in poudarjanja različnih vrst kode, npr. da se "
"&latex;-ove ukaze lažje razloči od normalnega besedila, pa tudi matematične "
"formule so označene z drugo barvo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:954
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Bullets</title>"
msgstr "<title>Naboji</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:956
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many wizards can insert optional bullets, a special kind of bookmark within "
"the text. The menu entries <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Bullets</guisubmenu></menuchoice> or the corresponding "
"keyboard shortcuts will allow you to jump to the next or last bullet. This "
"will also highlight this bullet so that it will be deleted automatically, "
"when you enter your first letter."
msgstr ""
"Veliko čarovnikov (wizard) lahko vstavlja tako imenovane naboje (bullets). "
"To so posebni zaznamki znotraj besedila. Z menijem "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guisubmenu>Bullets</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice> ali z ustrezno bližnjico na tipkovnici lahko skočite na "
"naslednji ali zadnji naboj. To dejanje prav tako označi ta naboj, da bo "
"izbrisan samodejno, ko vnesete prvo črko."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:963 index.docbook:3930 index.docbook:3954 index.docbook:3970
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Bullets</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Naboji</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:969 index.docbook:3936 index.docbook:3960 index.docbook:3976
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Bullets</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Naboji</phrase>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:976
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>Right</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Next Bullet</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>Desno</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Naslednji Naboj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:979
#, no-c-format
msgid "Jump to the next bullet in the text if there is one."
msgstr "Skoči na naslednji naboj v besedilu, če ta obstaja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:982
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>Left</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Last Bullet</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>Levo</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Zadnji Naboj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:985
#, no-c-format
msgid "Jump to the previous bullet in the text if there is one."
msgstr "Skoči na prejšnji naboj, če ta obstaja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:994
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select"
msgstr "Izberi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:996
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Editing is of course one of the main aspects when you use a program like "
"&kile;. Although &kate; already has great capabilities, &kile; adds some "
"important features, which are especially needed to write &latex; source. "
"&latex; always needs a lot of environments and groups, so &kile; supports "
"very special commands to select them. Under <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Select</guisubmenu></menuchoice> you will find the "
"following commands to select text."
msgstr ""
"Urejanje je seveda eden glavnih vidikov, ko uporabljate program kot je "
"&kile;. Čeprav ima tudi &kate; dobre zmožnosti, doda &kile; nekaj pomembnih "
"funkcij, ki so še posebej potrebne pri pisanju &latex;-ove kode. Pri &latex;-"
"u je vedno potrebnih veliko območij in skupin, zato &kile; podpira zelo "
"posebne ukaze, da jih lahko izberete. Pod <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Izberi</guisubmenu></menuchoice> boste našli naslednje "
"ukaze za izbiro besedila."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1004
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Edit->Select items</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Uredi->Izbirni elementi</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1010
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Edit->Select items</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Uredi->Izbirni elementi</phrase>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1016
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,E</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Environment (inside)</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,E</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Območje (notranjost)</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1020
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select an environment without the surrounding tags. If this command is "
"called, when an environment is already selected, &kile; will expand the "
"selection to the next surrounding environment."
msgstr ""
"Izberi območje brez njegovih oklepajočih značk. Če je poklican ta ukaz, "
"medtem ko je območje že izbrano, bo &kile; razširil izbiro na naslednje "
"območje, v katerem je trenutno vsebovano."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1026
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,F</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Environment (outside)</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,F</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Območje (zunaj)</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1030
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select an environment including the surrounding tags. This selection can "
"also be expanded with a second call of this command."
msgstr ""
"Izberi območje vključno z njegovimi oklepajočimi značkami. Ta izbira je prav "
"tako lahko razširjena s ponovnim klicem tega ukaza."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1035
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,T</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>TeX Group (inside)</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,T</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>TeX Skupina "
"(notranjost)</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1039
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select a &tex; group inside the surrounding braces."
msgstr "Izberi &tex; skupino znotraj zavitih oklepajev."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1043
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,U</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>TeX Group (outside)</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,U</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>TeX Skupina (zunaj)</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1047
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select a &tex; group including the surrounding braces."
msgstr "Izberi &tex; skupino vključno z zavitimi oklepaji."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1051
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,M</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Math Group</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,M</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Matematična skupina</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1055
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select the current math group including the math commands."
msgstr "Izberi trenutno matematično skupino, vključno z matematičnimi ukazi."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1058
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,P</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Paragraph</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,P</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Odstavek</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1062
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select a whole paragraph, &ie; a group of text lines separated on both sides "
"by empty lines. A paragraph does not mean just continuous lines of text, as "
"it is in other text editors. This extended meaning also includes tables, "
"&latex; commands and all other lines of source. The only important thing for "
"&kile; is that this kind of paragraph is separated by two empty lines."
msgstr ""
"Izberi celoten odstavek, &ie; skupino vrstic besedila, ki je na obeh straneh "
"ločena z praznimi vrsticami. Odstavek ne pomeni le neprekinjenih vrstic "
"besedila, kot npr. pri drugih urejevalnikih. Ta razširjen pomen označuje "
"tudi tabele, &latex;-ove ukaze in vse druge vrstice izvorne kode. Edina "
"pomembna lastnost odstavka pri &kile;-u je, da je ločen z dvema praznima "
"vrsticama."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1070
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,L</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Line</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,L</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Vrstica</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1074
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select the text line of the current cursor position."
msgstr "Izberi vrstico besedila glede na trenuten položaj kazalca."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1078
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,W</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>TeX Word</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,W</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>TeX Beseda</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1082
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the word under the current cursor position. This selection has also "
"en extended meaning, because this command can also select &latex; commands, "
"which begin with a backslash and may also have an optional star at the end."
msgstr ""
"Izberi besedo na kateri se trenutno nahaja kazalec. Ta izbira ima tudi "
"razširjen pomen, saj lahko s tem ukazom prav tako izberemo &latex;-ove "
"ukaze, ki se začenjajo z poševnico nazaj in imajo lahko tudi zvezdico na "
"koncu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1093
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select &latex; commands"
msgstr "Izberi &latex;-ove ukaze"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1095
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kile; has an extended feature to select &latex; commands. If you for "
"example have typed"
msgstr ""
"&kile; ima razširjeno funkcijo za izbiro &latex;.ovih ukazov. Če ste na "
"primer vtipkali"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:1098
#, no-c-format
msgid "text \\bfseries\\itshape more text"
msgstr "besedilo \\bfseries\\itshape več besedila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"and double click on one of the &latex; commands, both will be selected. But "
"often you only want to select one of two or more commands. This can be done "
"using the <keycombo>&Ctrl;</keycombo> key. You only have to press the "
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;</keycombo> key and a double click will only select the "
"desired command."
msgstr ""
"in dvojno kliknili na eno od teh ukazov, bosta izbrana oba. Vendar pogosto "
"želite izbrati eno od dveh ali več ukazov. To lahko storite z uporabo tipke "
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;</keycombo>. Le pritisniti morate tipko <keycombo>&Ctrl;</"
"keycombo> in dvojni klik bo izbral le zaželen ukaz."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1111
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete"
msgstr "Izbriši"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To delete some parts of a document you can of course select them, and then "
"use the <keycombo><keycap>Delete</keycap></keycombo> key. &kate; also offers "
"the command <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>K</keycap></keycombo> which deletes the "
"whole line. But &kile; offers a faster way with its own delete commands. "
"Under <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guisubmenu>Delete</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice> you will find the following commands to delete text."
msgstr ""
"Da izbrišete nekatere dele dokumenta, jih lahko seveda najprej izberete in "
"nato uporabite tipko <keycombo><keycap>Delete</keycap></keycombo>. Poleg "
"tega &kate; ponuja ukaz <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>K</keycap></keycombo>, ki "
"izbriše celotno vrstico. &kile; pa ponuja še hitrejši način s svojimi ukazi "
"za izbris. Pod <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guisubmenu>Izbriši</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> boste našli naslednje ukaze za izbris besedila."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1121
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Edit->Delete items</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Uredi->Elementi za izbris</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1127
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Edit->Delete items</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Uredi->Elementi za izbris</phrase>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,E</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Environment (inside)</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,E</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Območje (notranjost)</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1137
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete an environment without the surrounding tags."
msgstr "Izbriše notranjost območja brez njegovih oklepajočih značk."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,F</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Environment (outside)</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,F</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Območje (zunaj)</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1144
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete an environment including the surrounding tags."
msgstr "Izbriše območje vključno z njegovimi oklepajočimi značkami."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,T</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>TeX Group (inside)</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,T</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>TeX Skupina "
"(notranjost)</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1151
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete a &tex; group inside the surrounding braces."
msgstr "Izbriše &tex; skupino znotraj zavitih oklepajev."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1154
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,U</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>TeX Group (outside)</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,U</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>TeX Skupina (zunaj)</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1158
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete a &tex; group including the surrounding braces."
msgstr "Izbriše &tex; skupino, vključno z zavitimi oklepaji."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,M</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Math Group</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,M</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Matematična Skupina</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1165
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete the current math group including the math commands."
msgstr "Izbriše trenutno matematično skupino vključno z matematičnimi ukazi."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,P</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Paragraph</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,P</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Odstavek</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1172
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Delete a whole paragraph. Look at the <menuchoice><guisubmenu>Select</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Paragraph</guimenuitem></menuchoice> command, how a "
"paragraph is defined in &kile;."
msgstr ""
"Izbriše celoten odstavek. Glej ukaz <menuchoice><guisubmenu>Izberi</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Odstavek</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, kako je "
"definiran v &kile;-u."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,I</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>To End of Line</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,I</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Do Konca Vrstice</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1183
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Delete the text from the current cursor position to the end of the line."
msgstr "Izbriše besedilo od trenutnega položaja kazalca do konca vrstice."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,W</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>TeX Word</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,W</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>TeX Beseda</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1191
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete the word or &latex; command under the current cursor position."
msgstr "Izbriše besedo ali &latex;-ov ukaz, na katerem se nahaja kazalec."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1201
#, no-c-format
msgid "Environment"
msgstr "Območje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It has already been mentioned that environments are a central point in "
"&latex;. So &kile; offers five other commands to make the work with &latex; "
"as easy as possible under submenus <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Environment</guisubmenu></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Omenjali smo že, da so območja osrednje bistvo &latex;-a. Zato &kile; ponuja "
"še pet drugih ukazov, ki se nahajajo pod <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Območje</guisubmenu></menuchoice>, da je delo z &latex;-"
"om kar se da enostavno."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1208
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Edit->Environment items</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Uredi->Elementi za območje</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1214
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Edit->Environment items</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Uredi->Elementi za območje</phrase>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1221
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>E</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,B</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Go to Begin</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>E</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,B</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Pojdi na Begin</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command will jump to the beginning of the current environment, wherever "
"your current position is. The cursor will be placed directly in front of the "
"opening environment tag."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz bo povzročil skok na začetek trenutnega območja, v katerem je vaš "
"kazalec (\\begin{}). Kazalec se bo postavil točno pred značko za začetek "
"območja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1230
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>E</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,E</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Go to End</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>E</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,E</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Pojdi na End</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command will jump to the end of the current environment, wherever your "
"current position is. The cursor will be placed directly behind the closing "
"environment tag."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz povzroči skok na konec trenutnega območja (\\end{}). Kazalec se bo "
"postavil točno za značko za konec območja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>E</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,M</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Match</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>E</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,M</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Najdi ujemajočo</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1243
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When your cursor is placed in front of or above the <userinput>"
"\\begin{environment}</userinput> tag, it will be moved to the opposite end "
"of the environment and vice versa."
msgstr ""
"Ko je kazalec postavljen pred ali na značko <userinput>\\begin{environment}</"
"userinput>, bo s tem ukazom premaknjen na nasproten konec območja in obratno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1248
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>E</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,C</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Close</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>E</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,C</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Zaključi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Typing a lot of nested environment tags, you may lose control of all those "
"environments. This command will close the last opened environment, so that "
"the nested structure of environments will not be broken."
msgstr ""
"Če uporabljate veliko vgnezdenih značk za območja, lahko izgubite pregled "
"nad vsemi temi območji. Ta ukaz bo zaprl zadnjo odprto območje, tako da "
"vgnezdena struktura območij ne bo pokvarjena."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>E</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,A</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Close All</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>E</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,A</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Zaključi Vse</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This closes all open environments, not only the last opened environment."
msgstr "Ta ukaz zapre vsa odprta območja, ne le zadnjega odprtega."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1271
#, no-c-format
msgid "&tex; Group"
msgstr "&tex; Skupina"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1273
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kile; also offers some special commands for &latex; groups, which are "
"determined by braces <userinput>{...}</userinput>. In submenu "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guisubmenu>TeX Group</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice> you will find some important commands, which correspond to those "
"from <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guisubmenu>Environment</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"&kile; prav tako ponuja nekaj posebnih ukazov za &latex;-ove skupine, ki so "
"določene z zavitimi oklepaji <userinput>{...}</userinput>. V podmeniju "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guisubmenu>TeX Skupina</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice> boste našli nekaj pomembnih ukazov, ki ustrezajo tistim iz "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guisubmenu>Območje</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1281
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Edit->TeX Group</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Uredi->TeX Skupina</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1287
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Edit->TeX Group</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Uredi->TeX Skupina</phrase>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1293
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>G</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,B</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Go to Begin</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>G</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,B</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Pojdi na Begin</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1297
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command will jump to the beginning of the current group, wherever your "
"current position is. The cursor will be placed directly in front of the "
"opening brace."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz bo skočil na začetek trenutne skupine, glede na to, kje je vaš "
"kazalec. Kazalec bo postavljen točno pred odpiralnim oklepajem."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1302
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>G</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,E</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Go to End</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>G</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,E</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Pojdi na End</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1306
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command will jump to the end of the current group, wherever your "
"current position is. The cursor will be placed directly behind the closing "
"brace."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz bo skočil na konec trenutne skupine. Kazalec bo postavljen točno za "
"zavitim zaklepajem."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1311
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>G</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,M</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Match</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>G</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,M</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Najdi ujemajoče</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1315
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When your cursor is placed in front of or behind an opening brace of a &tex; "
"group, it will be moved to the opposite end of the group and vice versa."
msgstr ""
"Ko je kazalec postavljen pred ali za odpiralnim oklepajem &tex; skupine, se "
"bo s tem ukazom premaknil na nasprotni konec skupine in obratno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1320
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>G</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,C</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Close</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>G</keycap></"
"keycombo> <keycap>,C</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Zaključi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Typing a lot of nested group braces may be hard work. This command will "
"close the last opened group, so that the nested structure of &tex; groups "
"will not be broken."
msgstr ""
"Vpisovanje veliko vgnezdenih oklepajev skupin je lahko naporno. S tem ukazom "
"zaprete zadnjo odprto skupino, da vgnezdena struktura ni pokvarjena."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1335
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Double Quotes</title>"
msgstr "<title>Dvojni Narekovaji</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1337
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In &latex;, two single quotes are used as double quotes. To help you insert "
"these efficiently, &kile; allows you to press <keycap>\"</keycap> to insert "
"two opening single quotes. Furthermore, if you want to close a quotation, "
"you also have to press <keycap>\"</keycap>. &kile; will be smart enough to "
"recognize this situation and inserts two closing quotes for &latex;."
msgstr ""
"V &latex;-u sta dva enojna narekovaja uporabljena kot dvojni narekovaj. Da "
"jih vstavite učinkovito, vam &kile; omogoča, da pritisnete <keycap>\"</"
"keycap>, da vstavite dva odpiralna enojna narekovaja. Če v nadaljevanju "
"želite zapreti citat, morate prav tako pritisniti <keycap>\"</keycap>. "
"&kile; je dovolj pameten, da tako situacijo prepozna in vstavi dva zapiralna "
"narekovaja za &latex;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1345
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To get a literal double quote on the other side, press <keycap>\"</keycap> "
"twice."
msgstr ""
"Če pa želite natanko dvojni narekovaj, potem pritisnite <keycap>\"</keycap> "
"dvakrat."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1348
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can enable or disable this auto insertion of opening and closing double "
"quotes in section <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure Kile...</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>LaTeX</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Samodejno vstavljanje odpiralnih in zapiralnih dvojnih narekovajev lahko "
"omogočite ali onemogočite v <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Nastavi Kile...</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>LaTeX</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1354
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Double Quotes</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Dvojni Narekovaji</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1360
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Double Quotes</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Dvojni Narekovaji</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1365
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you also include language-specific options like <userinput>ngerman</"
"userinput> or <userinput>french</userinput>, you will also be able to use "
"German or French double quotes. Many more languages are available."
msgstr ""
"Če poleg tega vključujete jezikovnospecifične možnosti, kot "
"<userinput>ngerman</userinput> ali <userinput>french</userinput>, boste "
"lahko uporabljali nemške ali francoske dvojne narekovaje. Na voljo je še "
"veliko več jezikov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1374
#, no-c-format
msgid "Smart Newline"
msgstr "Pametna Nova Vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1376
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you press <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Return</keycap></keycombo>, &kile; "
"inserts an intelligent newline. If your current position is inside a list "
"environment, like <userinput>enumerate</userinput> or <userinput>itemize</"
"userinput>, &kile; will not only insert a newline, but also add a <userinput>"
"\\item</userinput> command."
msgstr ""
"Če pritisnete <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Enter</keycap></keycombo>, bo &kile; "
"vstavil inteligentno novo vrstico. Če je vaš trenutni položaj znotraj "
"seznamskega območja, kot recimo <userinput>enumerate</userinput> ali "
"<userinput>itemize</userinput>, bo &kile; vstavil novo vrstico in bo pri tem "
"še dodal ukaz <userinput>\\item</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1382
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are inside a tabular environment, &kile; will finish the current line "
"with <userinput>\\\\</userinput>, followed by the newline."
msgstr ""
"Če ste znotraj tabelarnega območja, bo &kile; zaključil trenutno vrstico z "
"<userinput>\\\\</userinput>, nato pa naredil novo vrstico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1385
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are inside a &latex; comment, &kile; will start the next line with a "
"<userinput>%</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Če ste v &latex;-ovem komentarju, bo &kile; začel naslednjo vrstico z "
"<userinput>%</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1388
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Even better, &kile; is smart enough to support predefined &latex; and user "
"defined environments, which can be added in section "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure Kile...</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>LaTeX</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Še bolje, &kile; je dovolj pameten, da podpira vnaprej definirana &latex;-"
"ova območja in območja, ki jih je definiral uporabnik. Te se lahko doda pod "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Nastavi Kile...</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>LaTeX</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1397
#, no-c-format
msgid "Smart Tabulator"
msgstr "Pametni Tabulator"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1399
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some users like to arrange columns in tabular environments and put all "
"ampersand characters <keycap>&amp;</keycap> beneath each other. &kile; tries "
"to support this. If you press <keycombo>&Alt;&Shift;<keycap>&amp;</keycap></"
"keycombo>, &kile; will look for the next tab in the row above. Although this "
"tab may not be the corresponding tab, &kile; will add some spaces to adjust "
"the column position with the current tab."
msgstr ""
"Nekateri uporabniki si radi uredijo stolpce v tabelarnih območjih in "
"poravnajo vse znake za in <keycap>&amp;</keycap> enega pod drugim. &kile; "
"poskuša to podpirati. Če pritisnete <keycombo>&Alt;&Shift;<keycap>&amp;</"
"keycap></keycombo>, bo &kile; poiskal naslednji zavihek v zgornji vrstici. "
"Čeprav ta zavihek morda ne bo ustrezen, bo &kile; dodal nekaj presledkov, da "
"poravna položaj stolpca s trenutnim zavihkom."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1412
#, no-c-format
msgid "Code Completion"
msgstr "Dopolnjevanje Kode"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1414
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Although &kate; already offers a good completion mode, &kile; extends code "
"completion to support some special methods especially for &latex;. Five "
"different modes are integrated. Three of them work on demand, the other two "
"are autocompletion modes. All modes can be configured to work very "
"differently at <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure "
"Kile...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav &kate; že ponuja dober način za dopolnjevanje, &kile; razširi "
"dopolnjevanje kode, da podpira nekaj posebnih metod izključno za &latex;. "
"Vgrajenih je pet različnih načinov. Tri od teh jih deluje na zahtevo, druga "
"dva pa sta načina samodejnega dopolnjevanja. Vse načine se da skonfigurirati "
"pod <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Nastavi Kile...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, da delujejo na precej drugačen način."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1422
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatic Environment Completion"
msgstr "Samodejno Dopolnjevanje Območij"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1424
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you begin a new environment, typing <userinput>\\begin{environment}</"
"userinput>, &kile; will automatically add an <userinput>\\end{environment}</"
"userinput> command, with a line in between for your text."
msgstr ""
"Ko začnete novo območje, se bo z vtipkanjem ukaza <userinput>"
"\\begin{environment}</userinput> samodejno dodal ukaz <userinput>"
"\\end{environment}</userinput> z vrstico vmes za vaše besedilo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1428
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Autocompletion can be turned off in the &latex; section of "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure Kile...</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>LaTeX</guimenuitem><guilabel>Environments</"
"guilabel></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Samodopolnjevanje se da izključiti v &latex;-ovem razdelku "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Nastavi Kile...</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>LaTeX</guimenuitem><guilabel>O</guilabel></"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1433 index.docbook:1647
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Completing an Equation Environment</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Dopolnjevanje Območja z Enačbo</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1439 index.docbook:1653
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Completing an Equation Environment</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Dopolnjevanje Območja z Enačbo</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1441
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Completing an Equation Environment</para>"
msgstr "<para>Dopolnjevanje Območja z Enačbo</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1449 index.docbook:1633
#, no-c-format
msgid "&latex; Commands"
msgstr "&latex;-ovi Ukazi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1451
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you type some letters, you can activate this completion mode for "
"&latex; commands and normal words with <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Complete</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>(La)TeX Command</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> or the keyboard shortcut <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;"
"<keycap>Space</keycap></keycombo>. &kile; first reads the letters from the "
"current cursor position to the left and stops at the first non-letter "
"character or a backslash. If this pattern begins with a backslash, &kile; "
"will enter completion mode for &tex; or &latex; commands. Otherwise it "
"enters normal dictionary mode, where you will not find any &latex; commands. "
"Depending on the chosen mode, a completion box will be opened. You will see "
"all commands or words whose beginning matches the current pattern. You can "
"navigate with the cursor keys through this list and select one entry with "
"&Enter; or a double click with the mouse."
msgstr ""
"Ko vtipkate nekaj črk, lahko aktivirate ta način dopolnitve za &latex;-ove "
"ukaze in normalne besede z <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Dopolni</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>(La)TeX Ukaz</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali z bližnjico <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Shift;"
"<keycap>Space</keycap></keycombo>. &kile; najprej prebere črke od trenutnega "
"položaja kazalca na levo in se ustavi pri prvem nečrkovnem znaku ali "
"poševnico nazaj. Če se ta vzorec začenja s poševnico nazaj, bo &kile; "
"vstopil v način dopolnjevanja za ukaze &tex; ali &latex;. Odvisno od "
"izbranega načina se bo prikazal dopolnjevalni okvirček. Videli boste vse "
"ukaze ali besede, katerih začetek se ujema s trenutnim vzorcem. S puščicami "
"lahko greste skozi seznam in s tipko &Enter; izberete en element ali pa "
"dvojno kliknete nanj."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1464 index.docbook:1490 index.docbook:1551 index.docbook:1567
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Completing a LaTeX Command</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Dopolnjevanje Ukaza LaTeX</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1470 index.docbook:1496 index.docbook:1557 index.docbook:1573
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Completing a LaTeX Command</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Dopolnjevanje Ukaza LaTeX</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1475
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you push the &Backspace; key, the last letter of your pattern will be "
"deleted, and the completion list may grow. On the other hand, if you type "
"another letter it will expand the pattern and the visible word list may "
"shrink."
msgstr ""
"Ko pritisnete tipko &Backspace; bo izbrisana zadnja črka vašega vzorca in "
"seznam za dopolnjevanje se bo morda povečal. Po drugi strani, če vtipkate še "
"kakšno črko, se bo vzorec povečal in seznam se bo morda skrajšal."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1480
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you decide not to select any of the suggestions, you can leave this "
"dialog with &Esc;."
msgstr ""
"Če se odločite, da ne boste izbrali nobenega od predlogov, lahko zapustite "
"to pogovorno okno z &Esc;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1483
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You will see that all commands are written with a short description of their "
"parameters. These descriptions are of course stripped when you select a "
"command. Optionally you can let &kile; insert bullets at these places, so "
"that you can easily jump to these positions with <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Bullets</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Next Bullet</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> and insert the parameter you want."
msgstr ""
"Videli boste, da so vsi ukazi napisani s kratkim opisom njihovih parametrov. "
"Ti opisi seveda izginejo, ko izberete ukaz. Po želji lahko dovolite &kile;-"
"u, da vstavlja naboje (bullets) na ta mesta, da lahko enostavno skačete na "
"te položaje z <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guisubmenu>Naboji</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Naslednji Naboj</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in "
"vstavite želen parameter."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1501
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go to <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure Kile...</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Kile</guimenuitem><guilabel>Complete</guilabel></"
"menuchoice> to configure one or more of these lists. You can choose "
"different word lists for &tex; and &latex; commands and dictionary mode for "
"normal words."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Nastavi "
"Kile...</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Kile</guimenuitem><guilabel>Complete</"
"guilabel></menuchoice>, da konfigurirate enega ali več teh seznamov. "
"Izberete lahko različne sezname besed za ukaze &tex; in &latex; in način "
"slovarja za normalne besede."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1507
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you choose the option <guimenuitem>Show Latex commands</guimenuitem>, the "
"entries of all chosen compressed word list (cwl) files for &latex; command "
"completion are shown in a separate view of &kile;'s sidebar. You will see "
"which commands are available and what parameters and options must or can be "
"given for a completion. You can also simply select one entry with a mouse "
"click and it will be inserted into the document, with all named parameters "
"and options stripped."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete možnost <guimenuitem>Prikaži Latex-ove ukaze</guimenuitem>, bodo "
"vnosi za vse izbrane datoteke stisnjenih besednih seznamov (cwl - compressed "
"word list) za &latex;-ovo dopolnjevanje ukazov prikazani v ločenem pogledu "
"&kile;-ove stranske orodne vrstice. Videli boste, kateri ukazi so na voljo "
"in katere parametre in možnosti morajo ali so lahko podane za kompletiranje. "
"Prav tako lahko enostavno izberete en vnos z klikom miške in ta bo vstavljen "
"v dokument brez parametrov in brez možnosti."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1516
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>LaTeX commands in the sidebar</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>LaTeX-ovi ukazi v stranski orodni vrstici</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1522
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>LaTeX commands in the sidebar</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>LaTeX-ovi ukazi v stranski orodni vrstici</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1527
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As each chosen word list will be shown in a separate view of its own, there "
"could be too many views, so that &kile;'s main window may be larger than a "
"small screen allows. As this looks very ugly, &kile; works with a maximum "
"number of allowed views, which by default is set to 10. If this value is too "
"big for your screen, you should reduce it."
msgstr ""
"Ker je vsak izbran seznam besed prikazan v svojem ločenem pogledu, lahko "
"pride do prevelikega števila pogledov, tako da je &kile;-ovo glavno okno "
"morda celo večje, kot to dopušča majhen zaslon. Ker to izgleda precej grdo, "
"ima &kile; določeno maksimalno število dovoljenih pogledov. Privzeto je to "
"nastavljeno na 10, če pa je to število preveliko za vaš zaslon, ga "
"zmanjšajte."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1539
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <emphasis>command mode</emphasis> is not useful for code completion of "
"environments. You always have to type some letters of <userinput>\\begin</"
"userinput>, and invoking the completion mode will result in a huge list of "
"environment tags. On the other hand, environments are so often used that "
"&kile; offers a special mode for code completion of environments. Forget the "
"opening tag and write, for example, <userinput>al</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Način ukazov</emphasis> ni kaj dosti uporaben za dopolnjevanje "
"kode za območja. Vedno morate vtipkati nekaj črk niza <userinput>\\begin</"
"userinput>, kar pa bo tudi prineslo ogromen seznam značk za območja. Po "
"drugi strani so območja uporabljena tako pogosto, da &kile; ponuja poseben "
"način za dopolnjevanje kode območij. Brez začetne značke vtipkajte npr. "
"<userinput>al</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1545
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you call the completion mode with <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Complete</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Environment</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> or keyboard shortcut <keycombo>&Alt;&Shift;"
"<keycap>Space</keycap></keycombo>, the opening tag is automatically added "
"and you will see <userinput>\\begin{al}</userinput>. After this change, the "
"completion list is much less cluttered."
msgstr ""
"Ko pokličete način dopolnjevanja z <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Dopolni</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Območje</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> ali bližnjico na tipkovnici <keycombo>&Alt;&Shift;<keycap>Space</"
"keycap></keycombo>, bo začetna značka samodejno dodana in videli boste "
"<userinput>\\begin{al}</userinput>. Po tej spremembi bo seznam za "
"dopolnjevanje veliko bolj urejen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1562
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now select an environment, and you will see that it is also automatically "
"closed. Even more, if &kile; recognizes it as a list environment, it will "
"also insert a first <userinput>\\item</userinput> tag."
msgstr ""
"Sedaj izberite območje in videli boste, da se tudi samodejno zapre. Še več, "
"če ga &kile; prepozna kot seznamsko območje, bo vstavil tudi prvo značko "
"<userinput>\\item</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1578
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go to <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure Kile...</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Kile</guimenuitem><guilabel>Complete</guilabel></"
"menuchoice> to configure one or more of these lists. This mode uses the same "
"word lists as the completion mode for &tex; and &latex; commands."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite pod <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Nastavi "
"Kile...</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Kile</guimenuitem><guilabel>Complete</"
"guilabel></menuchoice>, da konfigurirate enega ali več teh seznamov. Ta "
"način uporablja iste sezname besed kot način dopolnjevanja za ukaze &tex; in "
"&latex;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1588 index.docbook:1617
#, no-c-format
msgid "Abbreviations"
msgstr "Okrajšave"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1590
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kile; supports user defined lists of abbreviations, which are replaced on "
"demand by longer text strings. Look at <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure Kile...</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Kile</"
"guimenuitem><guilabel>Complete</guilabel></menuchoice> to configure one or "
"more of these lists. For the example given here, the abbreviation list in "
"<filename>example.cwl</filename> must be chosen. In this file you will find, "
"for example, the entry <userinput>L=\\LaTeX</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"&kile; omogoča, da si uporabnik ustvari seznam okrajšav, ki so kasneje "
"zamenjane z daljšimi nizi znakov. Glej <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Nastavi Kile...</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Kile</"
"guimenuitem><guilabel>Complete</guilabel></menuchoice> za konfiguracijo "
"enega ali več teh seznamov. Za primer, ki je naveden tukaj, mora biti izbran "
"seznam okrajšav v <filename>example.cwl</filename>. V tej datoteki boste "
"našli npr. vnos <userinput>L=\\LaTeX</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1598
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For example, type only the letter <userinput>L</userinput>. Now invoke the "
"abbreviation mode of word completion with <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Complete</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Abbreviation</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> or keyboard shortcut <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Alt;"
"<keycap>Space</keycap></keycombo>, and the letter <userinput>L</userinput> "
"is replaced by the string <userinput>\\LaTeX</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Za primer vtipkajte le črko <userinput>L</userinput>. Zdaj prikličite način "
"okrajšav za dopolnjevanje besed z <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Dopolni</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Okrajšava</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali pa z bližnjico na tipkovnici <keycombo>&Ctrl;"
"&Alt;<keycap>Space</keycap></keycombo> in črka <userinput>L</userinput> bo "
"nadomeščena z nizom <userinput>\\LaTeX</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1604
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Abbreviation completion also supports newline <userinput>%n</userinput> and "
"<userinput>%C</userinput> to place the cursor, if these characters are "
"present in the expansion text. So if you have the entry"
msgstr ""
"Dopolnjevanje okrajšav podpira tudi novo vrstico <userinput>%n</userinput> "
"in <userinput>%C</userinput> za postavitev kazalca, če so ti znaki prisotni "
"v razširitvenem besedilu. Torej, če imate vnos"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:1608
#, no-c-format
msgid "en1=\\begin{enumerate}%n\\item %C%n\\end{enumerate}%n"
msgstr "en1=\\begin{enumerate}%n\\item %C%n\\end{enumerate}%n"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1610
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"in the completion file, and invoke the abbreviation completion, the "
"expansion looks as below, where <userinput>x</userinput> shows the final "
"cursor position."
msgstr ""
"v datoteki z dopolnitvami in sprožite način dopolnjevanja okrajšav, se bo "
"okrajšava razširila v spodnje besedilo, kjer <userinput>x</userinput> "
"predstavlja končno pozicijo kazalca."

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:1613
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\\begin{enumerate}\n"
"        \\item x\n"
"\\end{enumerate}"
msgstr ""
"\\begin{enumerate}\n"
"        \\item x\n"
"\\end{enumerate}"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1619
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you choose <guimenuitem>Show abbreviations</guimenuitem>, all possible "
"abbreviations are shown in a view of the sidebar. So you will have a good "
"survey of all possible abbreviations."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete <guimenuitem>Pokaži okrajšave</guimenuitem>, bodo v stranski "
"orodni vrstici prikazane vse možne okrajšave. Tako boste imeli dober pregled "
"nad vsemi možnimi okrajšavami."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1629
#, no-c-format
msgid "Autocompletion Modes"
msgstr "Načini za Samodejno Dopolnjevanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1635
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also enable an autocompletion mode for &latex; commands. When a "
"given threshold of letters (default: 3) is entered, a popup window opens "
"with a list of all matching &latex; commands. You can select one of these "
"commands, or ignore this window and type further letters. The entries of the "
"completion box will always change and match your currently typed word."
msgstr ""
"Omogočite lahko tudi način samodopolnjevanja za &latex;-ove ukaze. Ko je "
"število vnešenih črk večje od nastavljenega praga (privzeta vrednost: 3), se "
"bo samoprikazal okvirček s seznamom vseh ujemajočih &latex;-ovih ukazov. "
"Lahko katerega izberete ali pa le prezrete priporočila in nadaljujete z "
"vpisovanjem črk. Vsebina okvirčka za dopolnjevanje se bo spreminjala sproti, "
"da se bo ujemala z besedo, ki je trenutno vpisana."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1641
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go to <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure Kile...</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Kile</guimenuitem><guilabel>Complete</guilabel></"
"menuchoice> to enable or disable this mode or to change the threshold."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Nastavi "
"Kile...</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Kile</guimenuitem><guilabel>Complete</"
"guilabel></menuchoice>, da omogočite ali pa onemogočite za način, lahko pa "
"tudi spremenite prag."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1662
#, no-c-format
msgid "Document Words"
msgstr "Besede iz Dokumenta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1664
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Large dictionaries are not useful in autocompletion mode. But, we have seen "
"that a lot of words in a document are typed more than once. So &kile; offers "
"a completion for all words from the document that the user has already "
"typed. You can manually invoke this completion, if you press <keycombo>&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>Space</keycap></keycombo>. Note that this mode is different from the "
"completion mode for &latex; commands."
msgstr ""
"Veliki slovarji niso pretirano uporabni za način samodopolnjevanja, smo pa "
"ugotovili, da je veliko različnih besed napisanih več kot enkrat v "
"dokumentu. Zato &kile; ponuja dopolnjevanje vseh besed, ki so bile v "
"dokumentu že napisane. To dopolnjevanje lahko prikličete ročno s pritiskom "
"na <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Space</keycap></keycombo>. Upoštevajte, da je ta "
"način drugačen od tistega, ki dopolnjuje &latex;-ove ukaze."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1671
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to turn this mode on or off, go to "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure Kile...</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Editor</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Editing</"
"guimenuitem><guilabel>Auto Completion</guilabel></menuchoice>. In this "
"dialog you can configure if completion mode for document words should be "
"enabled. There is also an additional autocompletion mode, where a completion "
"box pops up, when a certain threshold is reached."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ta način izklopiti ali vklopiti, pojdite na "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Nastavi Kile...</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Urejevalnik</guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Urejanje</"
"guimenuitem><guilabel>Auto Completion</guilabel></menuchoice>. V tem "
"pogovornem oknu lahko nastavite, ali naj bo način dopolnjevanja za besede iz "
"dokumenta omogočen. Obstaja tudi dodaten način za samodopolnjevanje, pri "
"katerem se okvirček za dopolnjevanje prikaže, ko število črk doseže določen "
"prag."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1684
#, no-c-format
msgid "Writing Own Completion Files"
msgstr "Kako Napisati Svojo Datoteko za Dopolnjevanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1686
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The latest specification of the completion file format can found in the "
"<ulink url=\"https://commits.kde.org/kile?path=README.cwl\"> CWL file format "
"specification</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Najnovejše specifikacije za format dopolnjevalne datoteke je dostopen v "
"<ulink url=\"https://commits.kde.org/kile?path=README.cwl\">Specifikacija za "
"format datoteke CWL</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1691
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Completion files can be installed in a user's home folder under the "
"<filename>~/.kde/share/apps/kile/complete/&lt;mode&gt;/</filename> "
"subdirectory, where <parameter>&lt;mode&gt;</parameter> either stands for "
"<constant>abbreviation</constant>, <constant>dictionary</constant> or "
"<constant>tex</constant>."
msgstr ""
"Dopolnitvene datoteke se da namestiti v domačo mapo uporabnika v podimeniku "
"<filename>~/.kde/share/apps/kile/complete/&lt;mode&gt;/</filename>, kjer "
"<parameter>&lt;mode&gt;</parameter> pomeni <constant>abbreviation</"
"constant>, <constant>dictionary</constant> ali <constant>tex</constant>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1701
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wizards and Dialogs"
msgstr "Čarovniki in Pogovorna okna"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1707
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This wizard has already been described in the section <xref linkend="
"\"intro_docwizard\" role=\"select: title pageabbrv\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Ta čarovnik (wizard) je že opisan v razdelku <xref linkend=\"intro_docwizard"
"\" role=\"select: title pageabbrv\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1713
#, no-c-format
msgid "Include Graphics"
msgstr "Vključevanje Grafik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1715
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Include Graphics</guilabel> dialog makes insertion of graphics "
"as easy as possible. You can reach it via the menubar with "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>LaTeX</guimenu><guimenuitem>Image Insertion</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Please take a look at <xref linkend="
"\"build_graphics\" role=\"select: title pageabbrv\"/> and <xref linkend="
"\"build_epsgraphics\" role=\"select: title pageabbrv\"/> to get an overview "
"of some basic facts concerning graphic formats."
msgstr ""
"Pogovorno okno <guilabel>Vključi Grafiko</guilabel> olajša vstavljanje "
"grafik kolikor se le da. Do njega dostopate preko menija z "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>LaTeX</guimenu><guimenuitem>Image Insertion</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Prosimo, oglejte si <xref linkend=\"build_graphics"
"\" role=\"select: title pageabbrv\"/> in <xref linkend=\"build_epsgraphics\" "
"role=\"select: title pageabbrv\"/>, da dobite pregled o osnovnih dejstvih o "
"grafičnih formatih."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1722
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Including a graphics element</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Vstavljanje grafičnega elementa</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1728
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Including a graphics element</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Vstavljanje grafičnega elementa</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1734
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose a graphics file. This can be a JPEG, PNG, PDF, EPS or even a zipped "
"or gzipped EPS file. If you have installed <ulink url=\"http://www."
"imagemagick.org/\">&imagemagick;</ulink> and also configured &kile; to use "
"it (<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure Kile...</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>LaTeX</guimenuitem><guilabel>Graphics</guilabel></"
"menuchoice>), the width and the height of the graphic is automatically "
"shown. If &imagemagick; can determine a resolution, the size of the graphics "
"is also shown in centimeters."
msgstr ""
"Izberite datoteko z grafiko. To je lahko JPEG, PNG, PDF, EPS ali celo "
"zippana ali gzippana EPS datoteka. Če ste inštalirali <ulink url=\"http://"
"www.imagemagick.org/\">&imagemagick;</ulink> in nastavili &kile; tako, da ga "
"lahko uporablja (<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Nastavi Kile...</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>LaTeX</"
"guimenuitem><guilabel>Graphics</guilabel></menuchoice>), bosta višina in "
"širina slike samodejno prikazani. Če &imagemagick; lahko določi resolucijo, "
"je velikost grafike navedena še v centimetrih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1744
#, no-c-format
msgid "Decide whether your image shall be centered on the page."
msgstr "Odločite se, ali naj bo vaša slika poravnana na sredini strani."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1746
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose whether you want the <userinput>\\graphicspath</userinput> notation "
"for your graphics file."
msgstr ""
"Izberite, ali želite notacijo <userinput>\\graphicspath</userinput> za vašo "
"grafično datoteko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1749
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default graphics files have to be in the same folder as your master "
"document. However, it is possible to put them in other folders to make "
"things tidier. Without a <userinput>\\graphicspath</userinput> command, "
"&kile; would include the path for the graphics file. But if you use "
"<userinput>\\graphicspath</userinput> in your preamble like this:"
msgstr ""
"Privzeto morajo biti datoteke z grafikami v isti mapi kot vaš master "
"dokument. Kljub temu pa jih je možno prestaviti tudi v druge mape, da imate "
"stvari bolj urejene. Brez ukaza <userinput>\\graphicspath</userinput> bi "
"&kile; vključil pot za grafično datoteko. Če pa uporabljate <userinput>"
"\\graphicspath</userinput> v vaši preambuli tako:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:1757
#, no-c-format
msgid "\\graphicspath{{/path/to/my/graphics}{other/path/to/more/graphics}}"
msgstr "\\graphicspath{{/pot/do/moje/grafike}{druga/pot/do/grafik}}"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1759
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"and check this option, &kile; will only use the base name of the graphics "
"file."
msgstr ""
"in obkljukate to možnost, bo &kile; uporabljal le ime grafične datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1762
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another example: if you set <userinput>\\graphicspath</userinput> command "
"like:"
msgstr ""
"Drug primer: če nastavite ukaz <userinput>\\graphicspath</userinput> tako:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:1765
#, no-c-format
msgid "\\graphicspath{{./}{camera/}{images/}}"
msgstr "\\graphicspath{{./}{camera/}{images/}}"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1767
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&latex; will search in the current folder, then in <filename>camera</"
"filename> and finally in <filename>images</filename> to find your graphics "
"file."
msgstr ""
"bo &latex; iskal v trenutni datoteki, nato v <filename>camera</filename> in "
"nazadnje v <filename>images</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1771
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you choose either a width or a height, the whole graphics will be "
"proportionally scaled. If you set two values for width and height at the "
"same time, width and height may be scaled with different factors, and this "
"could not be what you want. See also the information near the top of the "
"dialog to know the original size of the graphics."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete višino ali širino, bo celotna grafika sorazmerno spremenila "
"dimenzije. Če hkrati nastavite dve vrednosti za višino in širino, se zna "
"zgoditi, da se širina in višina ne bosta spremenili za isti faktor in "
"grafika se bo morda nekoliko popačila, kar ni nekaj, kar bi si želeli. "
"Poglejte še informacije blizu vrha pogovornega okna, da izveste originalno "
"velikost grafike."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1777
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert an angle by which to rotate the graphics counterclockwise."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite kot, za kolikor želite zarotirati grafiko v smeri urinega kazalca."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1779
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The bounding-box information is set automatically when you choose a graphics "
"file. This information is only needed when you work with traditional &latex; "
"and bitmapped graphics. See the discussion of <link linkend="
"\"build_epsgraphics\">EPS graphics</link>."
msgstr ""
"Informacije o mejnem okvirju (bounding-box) se nastavijo samodejno, ko "
"izberete datoteko z grafiko. Te informacije so uporabne le, ko delate z "
"tradicionalnim &latex;-om in z bitnimi (bitmapped) slikami. Glejte razpravo "
"o <link linkend=\"build_epsgraphics\">EPS grafiki</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1785
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If &latex; needs a bounding box and you do not want to generate a bb file, "
"&kile; supports this option. On the other hand, &pdflatex; will give a "
"warning when you want to include a png or jpg graphics with this option. "
"This checkbox enables or disables the bounding-box option."
msgstr ""
"Če &latex; potrebuje mejni okvir, vi pa nočete generirati datoteke bb, "
"&kile; podpira tudi to možnost. Po drugi strani vam bo &pdflatex; dal "
"opozorilo, če boste želeli vključiti grafiko png ali jpg na ta način. Ta "
"potrditveni okvirček omogoči ali pa onemogoči možnost z mejnim okvirjem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1790
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Scale the image by the desired scale factor. &eg;, 0.5 to reduce by half, or "
"2 to double. When you use this option, you do not have to set a width or "
"height for the image."
msgstr ""
"Povečajte sliko za želeni faktor, &eg; 0.5 da jo pomanjšate za pol ali 2 da "
"jo dvakrat povečate. Ko uporabljate to možnost, vam ni treba nastavljati "
"višine ali širine slike."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1794
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Trim Image</guilabel> tab you can crop your image in all "
"four directions."
msgstr ""
"V zavihku <guilabel>Obreži Sliko</guilabel> lahko obrežete vašo sliko iz "
"vseh štirih strani."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1798
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Finally, you have to specify whether you want to embed this image into a "
"figure environment. When you want the text to wrap around the figure, use "
"the wrapfigure environment instead."
msgstr ""
"Nazadnje morate še navesti, ali želite to sliko vdelati v okolje figure "
"(figure environment). Ko želite, da besedilo objema sliko, uporabite raje "
"objemajoče okolje (wrapfigure environment)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1802
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you choose the wrapfigure environment, you need to include the wrapfig "
"package in your preamble."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete objemajoče območje (wrapfigure environment), morate v vaši "
"preambuli vključiti paket wrapfig."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1804
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In either case you can insert a caption and a label for your image. "
"Generally, it is a good idea to add a different prefix to each kind of "
"label. It is common to use the prefix <userinput>fig:</userinput> for images."
msgstr ""
"V vsakem primeru lahko vstavite napis in oznako za vašo sliko. V splošnem je "
"pametno dodati različne predpone za vsako vrsto oznake. Pogosto se uporablja "
"predpona <userinput>fig:</userinput> za slike."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1810
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you pick the figure environment, you can choose where &latex; should "
"preferably position the figure."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete figurno okolje (figure environment), lahko izberete, kam naj "
"&latex; poskusi postaviti figuro."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1813
#, no-c-format
msgid "In the wrapfigure environment you can:"
msgstr "V objemajočem okolju lahko:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1815
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pick a placement rule for the figure and decide whether the figure should "
"float or not. In a two-sided document you can define whether the figure "
"should be on the inside or outside edge of the page."
msgstr ""
"Izberite pravilo za postavitev slike in se odločite, ali naj figura lebdi "
"ali ne. V dvostranskem dokumentu lahko določite, ali naj bo figura na "
"notranjem ali zunanjem robu strani."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1819
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Define how many shortened lines of the text are set alongside the figure. If "
"you leave this empty, &latex; will determine this itself as well as is "
"possible."
msgstr ""
"Definirajte, koliko skrajšanih vrstic besedila naj bo postavljenih vzdolž "
"figure. Če pustite to vrednost prazno, jo bo &latex; poskusil določiti sam "
"kar se da dobro."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1823
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Define an overhang to the chosen side. This is especially useful when you "
"have columns in your document and you want a figure to span over more than "
"just one column or you want shortened text on both sides of the figure."
msgstr ""
"Določite prekrivanje na izbrano stran. To je še posebej uporabno, če imate v "
"dokumentu stolpce in želite, da se figura razteza čez več kot le en stolpec, "
"ali želite skrajšano besedilo na obeh straneh figure."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1827
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose a width for the figure. This should be a bit bigger than the actual "
"image width, so there will be some empty space between the figure and the "
"text."
msgstr ""
"Izberite širino za figuro. Ta naj bo nekoliko večja od dejanske širine "
"slike, da pustite nekaj praznega prostora med sliko in besedilom."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1839
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arrays and tabulars"
msgstr "Polja in tabularji"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1841
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"One of the most boring jobs one can do in &latex; is to write a matrix or a "
"tabular environment. One has to keep track of all the elements, ensure that "
"the environment is well formed, and that all things are where they are "
"supposed to be. Good indentation helps, but there is a simpler way: using "
"&kile;'s <menuchoice><guimenu>Wizard</guimenu><guimenuitem>Array</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> or <menuchoice><guimenu>Wizard</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Tabular</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu entries. You "
"will then have a matrix-style input form that you can easily fill in with "
"your entries. This dialog also offers some options to typeset the tabular "
"material."
msgstr ""
"Ena najbolj dolgočasnih stvari, ki jih lahko nekdo počne v &latex;-u je "
"pisanje matrik ali tabelarnih okolij. Pri tem je potrebno spremljati vse "
"elemente, zagotoviti, da je okolje dobro oblikovano, in da so vse stvari na "
"svojem mestu. Zamikanje vrstic lahko pomaga, vendar obstaja enostavnejši "
"način: uporaba &kile;-ovih elementov menija <menuchoice><guimenu>Wizard</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Array</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Wizard</guimenu><guimenuitem>Tabular</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. Tako boste imeli na voljo vnašanje v tabelo, ki jo lahko lažje "
"in bolj pregledno izpolnite. To pogovorno okno prav tako ponuja nekaj "
"možnosti za oblikovanje materiala tabele."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1851
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Inserting a tabular environment</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Vstavljanje tabelarnega območja</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1857
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Inserting a tabular environment</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Vstavljanje tabelarnega območja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1862
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the toolbar on top of the dialog you can set the <userinput>align</"
"userinput> of a cell, define a certain <userinput>font style</userinput>, "
"<userinput>join</userinput> and <userinput>split</userinput> cells, choose a "
"<userinput>border</userinput>, and specify background and font "
"<userinput>colors</userinput>. On the extreme right there is a "
"<guilabel>Paste</guilabel> button. With this button you can insert a table "
"from the clipboard into the dialog, which allows you to copy and paste "
"tables from a spreadsheet program, for example."
msgstr ""
"Z uporabo orodne vrstice na vrhu pogovornega okna lahko nastavite "
"<userinput>poravnavo</userinput> celice, definirate določene "
"<userinput>sloge pisave</userinput>, <userinput>združite</userinput> in "
"<userinput>razdelite</userinput> celice, izberete <userinput>meje</"
"userinput> celic in navedete <userinput>barve</userinput> ozadja in pisave. "
"Na skrajni desni je gumb <guilabel>Prilepi</guilabel>. S tem gumbom lahko "
"vstavljate tabele iz odložišča v pogovorno okno, kar vam omogoča, da "
"kopirate in prilepite tabele iz npr. programov za preglednice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1870
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Below you can choose how many rows and columns you want, and you can tweak "
"some more details about your array:"
msgstr ""
"Spodaj lahko izberete, koliko vrstic in stolpcev želite, in prilagajate še "
"nekaj dodatnih podrobnosti o vaši tabeli:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1875
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With the <guilabel>Name</guilabel> option you can select which environment "
"should be used for your array or tabular material."
msgstr ""
"Z možnostjo <guilabel>Ime</guilabel> lahko izberete, katero območje naj se "
"uporabi za vašo tabelo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1878
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can select the vertical cell alignment with the <guilabel>Parameter</"
"guilabel> option. This is only enabled for environments which support that "
"feature."
msgstr ""
"Z možnostjo <guilabel>Parameter</guilabel> lahko izberete navpično poravnavo "
"celic. To je omogočeno le za območja, ki podpirajo to možnost."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1882
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If it exists for the selected environment, you can select <guilabel>use "
"starred version</guilabel>. When you select this option, you also have to "
"specify a <guilabel>table width</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko možnost <guilabel>use starred version</guilabel>, če ta "
"obstaja za izbrano območje. Ko izberete to možnost, morate navesti še "
"<guilabel>širino tabele</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1886
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tables sometimes look nicer when you select the <guilabel>use booktabs "
"package</guilabel> option."
msgstr ""
"Tabele včasih izgledajo lepše, če izberete možnost <guilabel>use booktabs "
"package</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1889
#, no-c-format
msgid "Of course, you can also <guilabel>Center</guilabel> your whole array."
msgstr ""
"Seveda lahko tudi postavite celotno tabelo <guilabel>na Sredino</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1892
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Inserting bullets</guilabel> helps you when you want to fill in "
"your content in the editor. With this option checked, &kile; will insert "
"bullet placeholders for each element of your array."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Vstavljanje točk navajanja</guilabel> vam pomaga, ko želite "
"napolniti svojo vsebino v urejevalniku. S to možnostjo obkljukano, bo &kile; "
"vstavil točko za vsak element polja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1898
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <menuchoice><guimenu>Wizard</guimenu><guimenuitem>Tabbing</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> option will display a simpler dialog to quickly set up a tabbing "
"environment. It allows you to easily specify the number of rows or columns "
"and the required spacing."
msgstr ""
"Možnost <menuchoice><guimenu>Wizard</guimenu><guimenuitem>Tabbing</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> bo prikazala poenostavljeno pogovorno okno za "
"hitrejše postavljanje tabelarnega območja. Omogoča, da enostavno navedete "
"število vrstic, stolpcev in potreben razmik."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1904
#, no-c-format
msgid "Inserting floating elements"
msgstr "Vstavljanje lebdečih elementov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1906
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kile; helps you with inserting your floating elements. With the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Wizard</guimenu><guimenuitem>Floats</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> wizard it is very simple to create a new figure or table "
"environment."
msgstr ""
"&kile; vam pomaga z vstavljanjem lebdečih elementov. S čarovnikom "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Wizard</guimenu><guimenuitem>Floats</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> je zelo lahko ustvariti novo figuro ali tabelarno območje."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1912
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Inserting a floating element</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Vstavljanje lebdečega elementa</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1918
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Inserting a floating element</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Vstavljanje lebdečega elementa</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1923
#, no-c-format
msgid "To insert a new floating environment just follow these steps:"
msgstr "Da vstavite novo lebdeče območje, sledite tem preprostim korakom:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1929
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choose whether you want to insert a figure or a table."
msgstr "Izberite, ali želite vstaviti figuro ali tabelo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1934
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select the desired positioning rules."
msgstr "Izberite želena pravila za postavitev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1939
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter a caption for your floating element."
msgstr "Vnesite napis za vaš lebdeči element."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1944
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type in a label for your new floating element. &kile; will automatically "
"suggest an appropriate prefix , &eg; \"fig:\" for figures and \"tab:\" for "
"tables."
msgstr ""
"Vtipkajte oznako vašega lebdečega elementa. &kile; bo samodejno predlagal "
"primerno predpono, &eg; \"fig:\" za figure in \"tab:\" za tabele."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1953
#, no-c-format
msgid "Inserting Math environments"
msgstr "Vstavljanje Matematičnih okolij"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1955
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Remembering how all the different math elements work can be really annoying. "
"Of course &kile; can do the magic for you here: <menuchoice><guimenu>Wizard</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Math</guimenuitem></menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"To, da se moramo sproti spominjati, kako delujejo različni matematični "
"elementi, zna biti precej nadležno. Seveda lahko &kile; opravi to delo "
"namesto vas: <menuchoice><guimenu>Wizard</guimenu><guimenuitem>Math</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1959
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Inserting a math element</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Vstavljanje matematičnega elementa</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1965
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Inserting a math element</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Vstavljanje matematičnega elementa</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1970
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options:"
msgstr "Možnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1974
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Name:</guilabel> Choose the type of math element you want to "
"create."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Ime:</guilabel> Izberite vrsto matematičnega območja, ki ga želite "
"ustvariti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1975
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Without numbering:</guilabel> This can switch numbering off for "
"numbered elements like equations or aligns."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Brez številčenja:</guilabel> Ta možnost izklopi številčenje za "
"oštevilčene elemente kot so enačbe ali poravnave."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1977
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Space command to separate groups:</guilabel> In an environment "
"which supports several groups like alignat, you can define a space separator "
"when you have more than one group. You can enter any space command here, "
"which exists in mathmode, &eg; \\quad."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Ukaz za presledek za ločevanje skupin:</guilabel> V okolju, ki "
"podpira več skupin (kot npr. alignat), lahko definirate ločilo, ko imate več "
"kot eno skupino. Tu lahko vnesete ukaz za ločevanje, ki obstaja v "
"matematičnem načinu, &eg; \\quad."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1980
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Standard tabulator:</guilabel> Select the tabulator which should "
"be used. &kile; should automatically pick the right one for you here."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Standard tabulator:</guilabel> Izberite tabulator, ki naj bo "
"uporabljen. &kile; bo samodejno izbral pravega za vas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1982
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Displaymath mode:</guilabel> For environments like matrices or "
"arrays you can choose which math environment your mathematical text should "
"be displayed with."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Displaymath mode:</guilabel> Za območja kot so matrike ali tabele "
"lahko izberete, s katerim matematičnim območjem naj bo vaše matematično "
"besedilo prikazano."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1984
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Use bullets:</guilabel> With this option checked, &kile; will "
"insert bullet placeholders for each element of your mathematical text."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Use bullets:</guilabel> S to možnostjo obkljukano bo &kile; "
"vstavil naboje na vsako mesto, kjer naj bi vnesli svoje matematično besedilo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1991
#, no-c-format
msgid "&PostScript; Utilities"
msgstr "&PostScript; Pripomočki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1993
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"PS files are not so popular as PDF files, but are an excellent base for "
"manipulations and rearrangements of pages. If you need PDF output, you can "
"rearrange pages with some &PostScript; utilities and then convert it to PDF "
"with <command>ps2pdf</command>."
msgstr ""
"Datoteke PS niso tako popularne kot datoteke PDF, vendar so odlična osnova "
"za prilagajanje in preureditve strani. Če potrebujete končni izdelek v PDF "
"obliki, lahko preuredite strani z &PostScript;-om in ga nato pretvorite v "
"PDF z <command>ps2pdf</command>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1998
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <emphasis>&PostScript; Wizard</emphasis> under "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Wizard</guimenu><guimenuitem>Postscript Tools</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> will suggest the most popular rearrangement. The "
"conversion is done by the programs <command>pstops</command> and "
"<command>psselect</command>, which can be found in most distributions in the "
"package <userinput>psutils</userinput>. If one of these programs is not "
"available, the corresponding item will not be visible."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>&PostScript; Wizard</emphasis> pod <menuchoice><guimenu>Wizard</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Postscript Tools</guimenuitem></menuchoice> vam bo "
"predlagal najbolj priljubljeno preureditev. Pretvorba se izvede s programoma "
"<command>pstops</command> in <command>psselect</command>, ki jih v večini "
"distribucijah lahko najdete v paketu <userinput>psutils</userinput>. Če eden "
"od teh programov ni na voljo, potem pripadajoč element ne bo viden."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:2007
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Dialog PSTools</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pogovorno Okno PSTools</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2013
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Dialog PSTools</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno Okno PSTools</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2018
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First choose your input file. If &kile; finds a PS file corresponding to "
"your current master document, it is already filled in as the input file, but "
"you are also free to choose another file. Then choose an output file, and "
"select one of the tasks. Finally, you have to decide whether you want to do "
"the conversion only, or also invoke &okular; to view the result."
msgstr ""
"Najprej izberite vašo vhodno datoteko. Če &kile; sam najde datoteko PS, ki "
"se ujema z vašim master dokumentom, bo ta datoteka že izbrana kot vhodna "
"datoteka, lahko pa tudi izberete kakšno drugo datoteko. Nato izberite "
"izhodno datoteko in izberite eno od nalog. Nazadnje se še odločite, ali "
"želite le napraviti pretvorbo, ali pa želite ob tem še odpreti pogled v "
"&okular;-ju, da prikažete rezultat."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2027
#, no-c-format
msgid "1 A5 page + empty page --> A4"
msgstr "1 A5 stran + prazna stran --> A4"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2028
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Combine one A5 page together with one empty page on one A4 page. Whenever "
"two A5 pages are combined together, they are rotated 90 degrees and will be "
"arranged on an A4 page in landscape mode."
msgstr ""
"Združi eno A5 stran z eno prazno stranjo skupaj v eno A4 stran. Ko sta dve "
"A5 strani združeni skupaj, sta zarotirani za 90 stopinj in bosta na strani "
"A4 prikazani v ležečem načinu."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:2033 index.docbook:2301
