#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2231
#, no-c-format
msgid "pstops: choose parameter"
msgstr "pstops: izberite parameter"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are many options for &PostScript; utilities <command>pstops</command> "
"and <command>psselect</command>. If you need a very special one, you can "
"invoke <command>pstops</command> with an option of your choice. Please read "
"the manual for all possible options."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja veliko možnosti za &PostScript;-ova pripomočka <command>pstops</"
"command> in <command>psselect</command>. Če potrebujete zelo posebnega, "
"lahko prikličete <command>pstops</command> z možnostjo, ki jo izberete sami. "
"Preberite priročnik za vse možne možnosti."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2240
#, no-c-format
msgid "psselect: choose parameter"
msgstr "psselect: izberite parameter"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2241
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can invoke <command>psselect</command> with an option of your choice. "
"Please read the manual for all possible options."
msgstr ""
"Prikličete lahko <command>psselect</command> z možnostjo, ki jo izberete "
"sami. Preberite priročnik za vse možne možnosti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2252
#, no-c-format
msgid "PDF Utilities"
msgstr "PDF Pripomočki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2254
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many people think of PDFs as frozen files, which cannot be modified. But "
"this is not true, as there exist excellent tools"
msgstr ""
"Veliko ljudi misli, da so PDFji zamrznjene datoteke, ki se jih ne da "
"spreminjati. Vendar to ni res, saj obstaja veliko odličnih orodij"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2257
#, no-c-format
msgid "for manipulations and rearrangements of pages"
msgstr "za prirejanje in preurejanje strani"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2258
#, no-c-format
msgid "to read and update document info"
msgstr "za branje in posodabljanje informacij dokumenta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2259
#, no-c-format
msgid "to read, set or change some permissions"
msgstr "za branje, nastavljanje ali spreminjanje nekaterih dovoljenj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2262
#, no-c-format
msgid "of an existing PDF document."
msgstr "obstoječega PDF dokumenta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kile;'s <emphasis>PDF wizard</emphasis> under <menuchoice><guimenu>Wizard</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>PDF Tools</guimenuitem></menuchoice> uses two different "
"methods to manipulate and rearrange PDF documents:"
msgstr ""
"&kile;-ov <emphasis>PDF wizard</emphasis> pod <menuchoice><guimenu>Wizard</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>PDF Tools</guimenuitem></menuchoice> uporablja dve "
"različni metodi za prirejanje in preurejanje PDF dokumentov:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&latex; package <command>pdfpages</command>, which is part of each &latex; "
"distribution. <command>pdfpages</command> doesn't work with encrypted pages."
msgstr ""
"&latex;-ov paket <command>pdfpages</command>, ki je del vsake &latex;-ove "
"distribucije. <command>pdfpages</command> ne deluje z zašifriranimi stranmi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2268
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>pdftk</command>, which is an excellent command line tool for doing "
"everyday things with PDF documents (see <ulink url=\"http://www.pdflabs.com/"
"tools/pdftk-the-pdf-toolkit\">The PDF Toolkit</ulink>)."
msgstr ""
"<command>pdftk</command>, ki je odlično orodje ukazne vrstice za opravljanje "
"vsakdanjih opravil s PDF dokumenti (glej <ulink url=\"http://www.pdflabs.com/"
"tools/pdftk-the-pdf-toolkit\">The PDF Toolkit</ulink>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If one of these helpers, <command>pdfpages</command> or <command>pdftk</"
"command>, is not present in your system, the corresponding items will not be "
"visible. Furthermore, remember that only <command>pdftk</command> can work "
"with encrypted files."
msgstr ""
"Če kateri od teh pomočnikov, <command>pdfpages</command> ali <command>pdftk</"
"command>, ni prisoten na vašem sistemu, pripadajoči elementi ne bodo vidni. "
"V nadaljnem ne pozabite, da samo <command>pdftk</command> lahko dela z "
"zašifriranimi datotekami."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2275
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rearrangements"
msgstr "Preureditve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2277
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If &kile;'s PDF wizard is called, it starts with the "
"<userinput>Rearrangements</userinput> register card."
msgstr ""
"Ko je poklican &kile;-ov PDF wizard, se zažene z registersko kartico "
"<userinput>Rearrangements</userinput>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:2280
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Dialog PDF Tools</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pogovorno okno PDF Orodja</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2286
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Dialog PDF Tools</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno PDF Orodja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2291
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First choose your input file. If &kile; finds a PDF file corresponding to "
"your current master document, it will already be filled in as the input "
"file, but you are also free to choose another file. Then choose an output "
"file or overwrite the existing PDF file, and select one of the tasks. "
"Finally, you have to decide whether you want to do the conversion only, or "
"also invoke the viewer (&eg; &okular;) to show the resulting document."
msgstr ""
"Najprej izberite vašo vhodno datoteko. Če &kile; najde PDF datoteko, ki se "
"ujema z vašim trenutnim master dokumentom, bo ta datoteka že navedena kot "
"vaša vhodna datoteka, seveda pa lahko izberete tudi drugo datoteko. Nato "
"izberite izhodno datoteko ali prepišite vašo obstoječo PDF datoteko in "
"izberite eno od nalog. Nazadnje se morate odločiti, ali želite izvesti le "
"pretvorbo, ali želite priklicati še pregledovalnik (&eg; &okular;), da "
"prikažete rezultat pretvorbe."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2293
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the PDF file is encrypted, only <command>pdftk</command> will work and "
"you have to give the password of this document to execute tasks."
msgstr ""
"Če je PDF datoteka zašifrirana, bo deloval le <command>pdftk</command> in "
"pri tem morate podati še geslo tega dokumenta, da izvedete nalogo."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2298
#, no-c-format
msgid "1 page + empty page --> A4"
msgstr "1 stran + prazna stran --> A4"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2299
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Combine one page together with an empty page on one A4 page. Whenever two A5 "
"pages are combined together, they are rotated by 90 degrees and arranged on "
"an A4 page in landscape mode."
msgstr ""
"Združi eno stran skupaj s prazno stranjo na eni A4 strani. Ko sta dve A5 "
"strani združeni skupaj, sta zarotirani za 90 stopinj in razporejeni na A4 "
"strani v ležečem načinu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2311 index.docbook:2369
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whenever two A4 pages are combined together, they are scaled, rotated by 90 "
"degrees and arranged on an A4 page in landscape mode."
msgstr ""
"Ko sta dve A4 strani združeni skupaj, sta primerno povečani/pomanjšani, "
"zarotirani za 90 stopinj in razporejeni na A4 strani v ležečem načinu."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:2313
#, no-c-format
msgid "A4 + empty page --> A4"
msgstr "A4 + prazna stran --> A4"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2319
#, no-c-format
msgid "A4 + empty page"
msgstr "A4 + prazna stran"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2327
#, no-c-format
msgid "1 page + duplicate --> A4"
msgstr "1 stran + duplikat --> A4"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2328
#, no-c-format
msgid "Put one page and a duplicate together on one A4 page."
msgstr "Združi eno stran in duplikat skupaj na eni A4 strani."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:2330 index.docbook:2342
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Duplicate a page</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Podvoji stran</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2336 index.docbook:2348
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Duplicate a page</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Podvoji stran</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2340
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the page to be duplicated has A4 size, it will be scaled to fit on the "
"page."
msgstr ""
"Če je stran, ki jo podvajate, velikosti A4, bo pomanjšana, da se bo "
"prilegala na eno stran."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2356
#, no-c-format
msgid "2 pages --> A4"
msgstr "2 strani --> A4"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2357
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Combine two consecutive pages together on one A4 page. Whenever two A5 pages "
"are combined together, they are rotated by 90 degrees and arranged on an A4 "
"page in landscape mode."
msgstr ""
"Združi dve zaporedni strani skupaj na eno A4 stran. Ko sta dve A5 strani "
"kombinirani skupaj, sta zarotirani za 90 stopinj in razporejeni na A4 strani "
"v ležečem načinu."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2385
#, no-c-format
msgid "2 pages (landscape) --> A4"
msgstr "2 strani (ležeče) --> A4"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2386
#, no-c-format
msgid "Put two consecutive pages in landscape mode together on one A4 page."
msgstr "Združi dve zaporedni strani v ležečem načinu skupaj na eno A4 stran."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:2388
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Combine two pages (in landscape mode)</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Združi dve strani (v ležečem načinu)</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2394
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Combine two pages (in landscape mode)</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Združi dve strani (v ležečem načinu)</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2402
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>4 pages --> A4</term>"
msgstr "<term>4 strani --> A4 </term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2403
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Combine four consecutive pages together on one A4 page. The pages have to be "
"scaled to fit on the page."
msgstr ""
"Združi štiri zaporedne strani skupaj na eno A4 stran. Strani morajo biti "
"pomanjšane, da se lahko prilegajo strani."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:2406
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>4 pages --> A4</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>4 strani --> A4</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2412
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>4 pages --> A4</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>4 strani --> A4</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2420
#, no-c-format
msgid "4 pages (landscape) --> A4"
msgstr "4 strani (ležeče) --> A4"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2421
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Combine four consecutive pages in landscape mode together on one A4 page. "
"The pages have to be scaled to fit on the page."
msgstr ""
"Združi štiri zaporedne strani v ležečem načinu skupaj na eno A4 stran. "
"Strani morajo biti pomanjšane, da se lahko prilegajo strani."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:2423
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Combine four pages (in landscape mode)</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Združi štiri strani  (v ležečem načinu)</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2429
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Combine four pages (in landscape mode)</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Združi štiri strani  (v ležečem načinu)</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2462
#, no-c-format
msgid "decrypt a file"
msgstr "dešifriraj datoteko"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2463
#, no-c-format
msgid "If the PDF file is encrypted, you can decrypt it."
msgstr "Če je PDF datoteka šifrirana, jo lahko dešifrirate."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2467
#, no-c-format
msgid "select pages"
msgstr "izberi strani"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2468
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add a comma separated list of pages or page ranges, &eg; 1,4-7,9. Only these "
"pages will appear in the resulting PDF file."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte z vejico ločen seznam strani ali obsegov strani, &eg; 1,4-7,9. Samo "
"te strani se bodo prikazale v končni PDF datoteki."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2472
#, no-c-format
msgid "delete pages"
msgstr "izbriši strani"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2473
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add a comma separated list of pages or page ranges, which should be removed "
"from the chosen PDF file."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte z vejico ločen seznam strani ali obsegov strani, ki naj bodo "
"odstranjeni iz izbrane PDF datoteke."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2477
#, no-c-format
msgid "apply a background watermark"
msgstr "uporabite vodni žig za ozadje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2478
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Applies a PDF watermark to the background of a single input PDF. The wizard "
"only uses the first page from the background PDF and applies it to every "
"page of the input PDF. This page is scaled and rotated as needed to fit the "
"input page."
msgstr ""
"Uporabi vodni žig PDF za ozadje enega vhodnega PDF-ja. Čarovnik uporabi samo "
"prvo stran PDF-ja v ozadju in jo uporabi za vsako stran vhodnega PDF-ja. Ta "
"stran je po potrebi prilagojena in obrnjena, da se prilega vhodni strani."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2482
#, no-c-format
msgid "apply a background color"
msgstr "uporabi barvo ozadja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2483
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Applies a background color to all pages of the current document. This can "
"only be done once, as the second color will be put behind the first color "
"and will not then be visible."
msgstr ""
"Uporabi barvo za ozadje na vseh straneh trenutnega dokumenta. To je lahko "
"izvedeno le enkrat, saj se druga barva postavi za prvo barvo in druga barva "
"nebo vidna."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2487
#, no-c-format
msgid "apply a foreground stamp"
msgstr "uporabite žig v ospredju"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2488
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Applies a foreground stamp on top of the input PDF document's pages. The "
"wizard uses only the first page from the stamp PDF and applies it to every "
"page of the input PDF. This page is scaled and rotated as needed to fit the "
"input page. This works best if the stamp PDF page has a transparent "
"background."
msgstr ""
"Uporabi žig v ospredju na vrhu strani vhodnega dokumenta PDF. Čarovnik "
"uporabi samo prvo stran PDF-ja z žigom in jo uporabi za vsako stran vhodnega "
"PDF-ja. Ta stran je po potrebi prilagojena in obrnjena, da se prilega vhodni "
"strani. To najbolje deluje, če ima stran PDF z žigom prosojno ozadje."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2492
#, no-c-format
msgid "pdftk: choose parameter"
msgstr "pdftk: izberi parameter"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2493
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can invoke <command>pdftk</command> with an option of your choice. "
"Please read the manual for all possible options."
msgstr ""
"Prikličete lahko <command>pdftk</command> z možnostjo vaše izbire. Preberite "
"si priročnik za vse možne možnosti."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2497
#, no-c-format
msgid "pdfpages: choose parameter"
msgstr "pdfpages: izberite parameter"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2498
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can invoke <command>pdfpages</command> with an option of your choice. "
"Please read the manual for all possible options."
msgstr ""
"Prikličete lahko <command>pdfpages</command> z možnostjo po vaši izbiri. "
"Preberite si priročnik za vse možne možnosti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2507
#, no-c-format
msgid "Properties"
msgstr "Lastnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2509
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The setting, changing and removing of properties will only be possible if "
"<command>pdftk</command> is installed and if additionally &kile; was "
"compiled with the <userinput>libpoppler</userinput> library."
msgstr ""
"Nastavljanje, spreminjanje in odstranjevanje lastnosti je izvedljivo le, če "
"je nameščen <command>pdftk</command> in če je bil &kile; dodatno preveden s "
"knjižnico <userinput>libpoppler</userinput>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:2512
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Dialog PDF Properties</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pogovorno okno PDF Lastnosti</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2518
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Dialog PDF Properties</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno PDF Lastnosti</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2523
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Traditional PDF metadata includes the document's title, author, subject, "
"keywords, creator, producer and the dates of creation and last modification."
msgstr ""
"Tradicionalni metapodatki PDF-ja vključujejo naslov dokumenta, avtorja, "
"temo, ključne besede, ustvarjalce, producenta in datume nastanka in sprememb."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2529
#, no-c-format
msgid "Permissions"
msgstr "Dovoljenja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2531
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Also, the setting, changing and removing of permissions will be only "
"possible if <command>pdftk</command> is installed."
msgstr ""
"Tudi nastavljanje, spreminjanje in odstranjevanje dovoljenj je mogoče le, če "
"je nameščen <command>pdftk</command>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:2534
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Dialog PDF Permissions</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pogovorno okno PDF Dovoljenja</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2540
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Dialog PDF Permissions</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno PDF Dovoljenja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2545
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A password is necessary to set or change these document settings. "
"Additionally, PDF encryption is done to lock the file's content behind this "
"password or to enforce lighter restrictions imposed by the author. So the "
"author can allow or restrict:"
msgstr ""
"Geslo je nujno potrebno za nastavljanje ali spreminjanje nastavitev teh "
"dokumentov. Poleg tega je šifriranje PDF-ja namenjeno zaklepanju vsebine "
"datoteke s tem geslom ali da se uveljavijo lažje omejitve, ki jih določi "
"avtor. Tako lahko lahko avtor odobri ali omeji:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2548
#, no-c-format
msgid "printing pages"
msgstr "tiskanje strani"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2549
#, no-c-format
msgid "modifying pages"
msgstr "spreminjanje strani"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2550
#, no-c-format
msgid "copying text and graphics from pages"
msgstr "kopiranje besedila in grafik iz strani"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2551
#, no-c-format
msgid "changing or adding annotations"
msgstr "spreminjanje ali dodajanje opomb"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2552
#, no-c-format
msgid "filling form fields with data."
msgstr "zapolnjevanje polj obrazcev s podatki."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2555
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Changing permissions always forces encryption associated with 128-bit "
"security of <userinput>Acrobat</userinput> 5 and 6, and also needs a "
"password."
msgstr ""
"Spreminjanje dovoljenj vedno prisili šifriranje povezano z 128-bitno "
"varnostjo <userinput>Acrobat-a</userinput> 5 in 6, in prav tako zahteva "
"geslo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2557
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"But always remember: encryption and a password do not provide any real PDF "
"security. The content is encrypted, but the key is known. You should see it "
"more as a polite but firm request to respect the author's wishes."
msgstr ""
"Vendar ne pozabite: šifriranje in geslo ne zagotavljata prave varnosti PDF-"
"ja. Vsebina je šifrirana, vendar je ključ znan. Na to bi morali gledati bolj "
"kot na vljudno, a trdno zahtevo po spoštovanju avtorjevih želja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2564
#, no-c-format
msgid "Document Statistics"
msgstr "Statistika Dokumenta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2566
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The statistics dialog in <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Statistics</guimenuitem></menuchoice> gives you a "
"statistical overview for a selection, a document or a whole project. It "
"includes the number of words, &latex; commands/environments and also "
"includes the number of characters for each type."
msgstr ""
"Pogovorno okno statistike pod <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Statistics</guimenuitem></menuchoice> vam ponuja "
"statistični pregled za neko izbiro, dokument ali celoten projekt. Vključuje "
"število besed, &latex;-ovih ukazov/območij in vključuje tudi število znakov "
"za vsako vrsto."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2571
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The statistics obtained can be copied as text or as a nicely formatted "
"&latex; table to the clipboard."
msgstr ""
"Te pridobljene statistične podatke je mogoče kopirati v odložišče kot "
"besedilo ali lepo formatirano &latex;-ovo tabelo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2573
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you select a text and open the statistics dialog, you get the "
"statistics for the currently selected text. If you open the dialog without "
"any text selected, the statistics for all opened files are shown. If you "
"want to get statistics for the whole project, you can use "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Project</guimenu><guisubmenu>Open All Project Files</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> for an easy and quick way to open all source files "
"of your project."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete besedilo in odprete pogovorno okno statistike, dobite statistiko "
"za trenutno izbrano besedilo. Če isto pogovorno okno odprete, brez da bi "
"izbrali kakršno koli besedilo, se bo prikazala statistika za vse odprte "
"datoteke. Če želite statistiko za celoten projekt, lahko uporabite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Project</guimenu><guisubmenu>Open All Project Files</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> kot lahek in hiter način, da odprete vse izvorne "
"datoteke vašega projekta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2579
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A note of caution has to be sounded about the accuracy of the numbers. We "
"have included some logic to get a good estimate, &eg; K\\\"uhler gives one "
"word and one command, with six and two characters respectively. But there "
"are other combinations in which parts of commands are counted as words and "
"vice versa. Please note that the algorithm was developed and tested for "
"languages similar to English or German. So don't take the numbers for "
"granted. If you write a report whose length has to be of a certain numbers "
"of words or characters, please make some tests first in order to check "
"whether &kile;'s accuracy satisfies your needs."
msgstr ""
"Opozoriti vas moramo še glede natančnosti teh številk. Dodali smo nekaj "
"logike za dobro oceno &eg; program šteje K\\\"uhler kot eno besedo in en "
"ukaz s šestimi in dvema znakoma. So pa še druge kombinacije, v katerih so "
"deli ukazov šteti kot besede in obratno. Prosimo upoštevajte, da je bil ta "
"algoritem razvit in testiran za jezike podobne angleščini in nemščini. Zato "
"ne jemljite teh števil za stoodstotno točne. Če pišete poročilo, ki mora "
"obsegati neko določeno število besed ali znakov, raje najprej opravite nekaj "
"testov, da preverite, ali &kile;-ova natančnost zadostuje vašim potrebam."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2593
#, no-c-format
msgid "Special Tags in &latex;"
msgstr "Posebne Značke v programu &latex;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2596
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the &latex; Tag Library"
msgstr "Uporaba &latex;-ove Knjižnice Značk"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2598
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&latex; has thousands of tags for symbols and special characters. The "
"easiest way to insert these tags is to use the sidebar menu, to the left of "
"the editor window."
msgstr ""
"&latex; vsebuje tisoče značk za simbole in posebne znake. Najlažji način, da "
"jih vstavite, je s pomočjo stranske orodne vrstice na levi strani okna "
"urejevalnika."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:2603
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Sidebar Menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Stranska Orodna Vrstica</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2609
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Sidebar Menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Stranska Orodna Vrstica</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2611
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>The Sidebar Menu</para>"
msgstr "<para>Stranska Orodna Vrstica</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2614
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following types are available:"
msgstr "Na voljo so naslednje vrste:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2617
#, no-c-format
msgid "Most Frequently Used"
msgstr "Najpogosteje Uporabljeno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2618
#, no-c-format
msgid "Relation"
msgstr "Relacije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2619
#, no-c-format
msgid "Operators"
msgstr "Operatorji"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2620
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arrows"
msgstr "Puščice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2621
#, no-c-format
msgid "Miscellaneous Math"
msgstr "Matematika Razno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2622
#, no-c-format
msgid "Miscellaneous Text"
msgstr "Besedilo Razno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2623
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delimiters"
msgstr "Ločila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2624
#, no-c-format
msgid "Greek"
msgstr "Grško"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2625
#, no-c-format
msgid "Special Characters"
msgstr "Posebni Znaki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2626
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cyrillic Characters"
msgstr "Znaki Cirilice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2627
#, no-c-format
msgid "User Defined"
msgstr "Definirano od Uporabnika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2629
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The tooltips of the icons show the &latex; commands and additionally needed "
"packages."
msgstr "Opisi ikon prikazujejo &latex;-ov ukaz in dodatno potreben paket."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2630
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pressing <keycombo>&Shift;</keycombo> and clicking a symbol will result in "
"<userinput>$\\symbolcmd$</userinput> being inserted. Similarly, pressing "
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;</keycombo> inserts it in curly brackets."
msgstr ""
"S pritiskom na <keycombo>&Shift;</keycombo> in klikom na simbol se bo ukaz "
"vstavil med znaka $: <userinput>$\\ukazsimbola$</userinput>. Podobno se bo s "
"pritiskom na <keycombo>&Ctrl;</keycombo> ukaz vstavil med zavite oklepaje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2633
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you insert a command which requires a package which is not included in "
"your &latex; document, you will see a warning message in the logview window."
msgstr ""
"Če vstavite ukaz, ki zahteva paket, ki ni vključen v vašem &latex;-ovem "
"dokumentu, se vam bo v okvirčku za beleženje napak prikazalo opozorilo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2635
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first list of symbols holds the <guilabel>Most Frequently Used</"
"guilabel> symbols. Inserted symbols will be added to this list, for quick "
"and easy reference. The ordering of the symbols will not be changed upon "
"addition of new symbols, instead a reference counter is incremented. If the "
"number of items exceeds 30 items, the item with the lowest count is removed."
msgstr ""
"Prvi seznam simbolov vključuje <guilabel>Najpogosteje Uporabljene</guilabel> "
"simbole. Vstavljeni simboli bodo dodani na ta seznam za hitro in lahko "
"ponovno dodajanje. Urejenost seznama se ne bo spremenila ob dodajanju novega "
"simbola. Namesto tega bo povečan števec za simbol. Če število elementov na "
"seznamu preseže 30 elementov, bo odstranjen simbol z najmanjšim števcem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2639
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>User Defined</guilabel> symbol list can hold your own symbols. "
"To create your own symbols you need the program gesymb and the file "
"<filename>definitions.tex</filename> from the kile source package. "
"Additionally you need a &latex; compiler (what a surprise) and <ulink url="
"\"http://www.dvipng.sourceforge.net\">&dvipng;</ulink> (version 1.7 or "
"later). The procedure is that you create a &latex; file with <userinput>"
"\\input{definitions}</userinput>, which makes the commands listed below "
"available, and let <userinput>gesymb mysymbols.tex user</userinput> (which "
"calls &latex; and &dvipng;) create the icons. After copying them to "
"<userinput>$HOME/.kde/share/apps/kile/mathsymbols/user/</userinput> and "
"restarting kile you can use your own symbols."
msgstr ""
"Seznam simbolov <guilabel>Uporabniško definirano</guilabel> vključuje vaše "
"lastne simbole. Da ustvarite svoj simbol, potrebujete program gesymb in "
"datoteko <filename>definitions.tex</filename> iz izvornega paketa kile-a. "
"Dodatno potrebujete &latex;-ov prevajalnik (kako presenetljivo) in <ulink "
"url=\"http://www.dvipng.sourceforge.net\">&dvipng;</ulink> (verzija 1.7 ali "
"kasnejšo). Ustvariti morate &latex;-ovo datoteko z <userinput>"
"\\input{definitions}</userinput>, kar omogoči spodaj navedene ukaze, in "
"omogočiti <userinput>uporabniku gesymb mysymbols.tex</userinput> (ki kliče "
"&latex; in &dvipng;), da ustvarja ikone. Potem ko jih kopirate v <userinput>"
"$HOME/.kde/share/apps/kile/mathsymbols/user/</userinput> in ponovno zaženete "
"kile, lahko uporabljate svoje lastne simbole."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2648
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following commands are defined in <filename>definitions.tex</filename>:"
msgstr "Naslednji ukazi so definirani v <filename>definitions.tex</filename>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2652
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>\\command[\\optarg]{\\symbol}</userinput>: Include the symbol "
"<userinput>\\symbol</userinput> in the symbol list, the optional argument "
"<userinput>\\optarg</userinput> specifies the command which kile should "
"insert. If it is not given the command in the mandatory argument is used."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>\\command[\\optarg]{\\symbol}</userinput>: Vključi simbol "
"<userinput>\\symbol</userinput> v seznam simbolov, neobvezni argument "
"<userinput>\\optarg</userinput> določa ukaz, ki naj bi ga kile vstavil. Če "
"ni podan, bo uporabljen ukaz v obveznem argumentu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2659
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>\\mathcommand[\\optarg]{\\symbol}</userinput>: Same as above, "
"except that the command in the mandatory argument is inserted in math mode."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>\\mathcommand[\\optarg]{\\symbol}</userinput>: Isto kot zgoraj, "
"le da je ukaz v obveznem argumentu vstavljen v matematičnem načinu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2665
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>\\pkgs[arg]{pkg}</userinput>: Declare that the command given in "
"this line needs the &latex; package <userinput>pkg</userinput> with the "
"optional argument <userinput>arg</userinput>. This command has to be in "
"front of the <userinput>\\command</userinput> command and overrides any "
"package specification by the neededpkgs enviroment."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>\\pkgs[arg]{pkg}</userinput>: Deklarira, da ukaz, ki je podan v "
"tej vrstici potrebuje &latex;-ov paket <userinput>pkg</userinput> z "
"neobveznim argumentom <userinput>arg</userinput>. Ta ukaz mora biti pred "
"ukazom <userinput>\\command</userinput>in preglasi katere koli specifikacije "
"paketov iz okolje neededpkgs."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2673
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>\\begin{neededpkgs}[pkgs-args]{pkgs} ... \\end{neededpkgs}</"
"userinput>: Has the same effect as above, but for all enclosed commands."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>\\begin{neededpkgs}[pkgs-args]{pkgs} ... \\end{neededpkgs}</"
"userinput>: Ima isti učinek kot zgoraj,le da je za vse priložene ukaze."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2680
#, no-c-format
msgid "An example for completeness is given here:"
msgstr "Primer za dopolnitev je podan tukaj:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:2682
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\\documentclass[a4paper,10pt]{article}\n"
"\\usepackage{amssymb}\n"
"\\input{definitions}\n"
"%\n"
"\\begin{document}\n"
"\\pagestyle{empty}\n"
"%\n"
"\\begin{neededpkgs}{amssymb}\n"
"\\mathcommand{\\surd}\n"
"\\pkgs{amsmath}\\mathcommand[\\ddddot{}]{\\ddddot{a}}\n"
"\\mathcommand{\\angle}\n"
"\\end{neededpkgs}\n"
"\\command{\\\"A}\n"
"\\mathcommand{\\exists}\n"
"\\mathcommand[\\stackrel{}{}]{\\stackrel{abc}{=}}\n"
"\n"
"%\\begin{neededpkgs}[russian,koi8-r,T2C,]{babel,inputenc,fontenc,mathtext}\n"
"%\n"
"%   \\end{neededpkgs}\n"
"% this would need to include the packages\n"
"% \\usepackage{mathtext}\n"
"% \\usepackage[T2C]{fontenc}\n"
"% \\usepackage[russian]{babel}\n"
"% \\usepackage[koi8-r]{inputenc}\n"
"%  just to explain the format\n"
"\\end{document}"
msgstr ""
"\\documentclass[a4paper,10pt]{article}\n"
"\\usepackage{amssymb}\n"
"\\input{definitions}\n"
"%\n"
"\\begin{document}\n"
"\\pagestyle{empty}\n"
"%\n"
"\\begin{neededpkgs}{amssymb}\n"
"\\mathcommand{\\surd}\n"
"\\pkgs{amsmath}\\mathcommand[\\ddddot{}]{\\ddddot{a}}\n"
"\\mathcommand{\\angle}\n"
"\\end{neededpkgs}\n"
"\\command{\\\"A}\n"
"\\mathcommand{\\exists}\n"
"\\mathcommand[\\stackrel{}{}]{\\stackrel{abc}{=}}\n"
"\n"
"%\\begin{neededpkgs}[russian,koi8-r,T2C,]{babel,inputenc,fontenc,mathtext}\n"
"%\n"
"%   \\end{neededpkgs}\n"
"% to bi moralo vkljčevati pakete\n"
"% \\usepackage{mathtext}\n"
"% \\usepackage[T2C]{fontenc}\n"
"% \\usepackage[russian]{babel}\n"
"% \\usepackage[koi8-r]{inputenc}\n"
"%  le da se razloži format\n"
"\\end{document}"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2688
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Bibitems"
msgstr "Uporaba Bibitems"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2690
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>\\bibitem</userinput> is a command used to enter a reference in a "
"<userinput>thebibliography</userinput> environment in your document. The "
"syntax for using <userinput>\\bibitem</userinput> is <userinput>"
"\\bibitem[label]{key}</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>\\bibitem</userinput> je ukaz, ki se ga uporablja za vnos "
"reference v območju <userinput>thebibliography</userinput> v vašem "
"dokumentu. Sintaksa za uporabo <userinput>\\bibitem</userinput> je "
"<userinput>\\bibitem[label]{key}</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2694
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The optional <userinput>[label]</userinput> is for you to add your own "
"labeling system for the bibliography entry. If no label is set, the entries "
"will be set in numerical order: [1], [2], [3], &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Neobvezen <userinput>[label]</userinput> je zato, da lahko sami dodate vaš "
"sistem označevanja za bibliografske vnose. Če ni nastavljena nobena oznaka, "
"bodo vnosi postavljeni v številskem vrstnem redu: [1], [2], [3], &etc;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2698
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The argument <userinput>{key}</userinput> is used to reference and link the "
"commands <userinput>\\bibitem</userinput> and <userinput>\\cite</userinput> "
"to each other and the information they contain. The command <userinput>"
"\\cite</userinput> contains the label associated with the intended "
"<userinput>\\bibitem</userinput>, which is located inside a "
"<userinput>thebibliography</userinput> environment, and contains the "
"reference data. Both corresponding <userinput>\\bibitem</userinput> and "
"<userinput>\\cite</userinput> must have the same <userinput>{key}</"
"userinput>; the easiest way to organize keys is by the author's last name. "
"The secondary braces in the <userinput>thebibliography</userinput> "
"environment denote the longest bibliography label you expect to have. So, "
"inserting <userinput>{<replaceable>foo</replaceable>}</userinput> means you "
"can have any label shorter or as large as the expression "
"<userinput><replaceable>foo</replaceable></userinput>. Failure to set this "
"parameter correctly may result in a not so attractive indentation of your "
"bibliography."
msgstr ""
"Argument <userinput>{key}</userinput> za naslavljanje in povezovanje ukazov "
"<userinput>\\bibitem</userinput> in <userinput>\\cite</userinput> druga z "
"drugo in z informacijami, ki jih vsebujeta. Ukaz <userinput>\\cite</"
"userinput> vsebuje oznako povezano z namenjeno <userinput>\\bibitem</"
"userinput>, ki se nahaja znotraj območja <userinput>thebibliography</"
"userinput>, in vsebuje ustrezne podatke. Oba ustrezna <userinput>\\bibitem</"
"userinput> in <userinput>\\cite</userinput> morata imeti isti "
"<userinput>{key}</userinput>; najlažji način za organizacijo ključev je po "
"priimkih avtorja. Drugi zaviti oklepaji v območju "
"<userinput>thebibliography</userinput> označujejo najdaljšo bibliografsko "
"oznako, ki jo pričakujete, da jo boste imeli. Tako vstavljanje "
"<userinput>{<replaceable>foo</replaceable>}</userinput> pomeni, da imate "
"lahko katero koli oznako krajšo ali enako kot izraz "
"<userinput><replaceable>foo</replaceable></userinput>. Napaka pri korektni "
"nastavitvi tega parametra se lahko prikaže kot ne preveč privlačen zamik "
"vaše bibliografije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2712
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The bibliography is a section apart from your main document, and an example "
"of code for the bibliography would look like the following:"
msgstr ""
"Bibliografija je razdelek, ločen od vašega glavnega dokumenta. Primer kode "
"za bibliografijo bi izgledal nekako tako:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:2715
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\\begin{thebibliography}{50}\n"
"        \\bibitem{Simpson} Homer J. Simpson. \\textsl{Mmmmm...donuts}. "
"Evergreen Terrace Printing Co.,\n"
"                          Springfield, SomewhereUSA, 1998\n"
"\\end{thebibliography}"
msgstr ""
"\\begin{thebibliography}{50}\n"
"        \\bibitem{Simpson} Homer J. Simpson. \\textsl{Mmmmm...donuts}. "
"Evergreen Terrace Printing Co.,\n"
"                          Springfield, SomewhereUSA, 1998\n"
"\\end{thebibliography}"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2717
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Then, your main source code would contain the location of the information "
"relating to the <userinput>\\bibitem</userinput> using <userinput>\\cite</"
"userinput>. That source code would look similar to this:"
msgstr ""
"Nato naj vaša glavna izvorna koda vsebuje lokacijo informacij, povezanih z "
"<userinput>\\bibitem</userinput> z uporabo <userinput>\\cite</userinput>. Ta "
"izvorna koda bi izgledala nekako tako:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:2720
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"My thesis, about the philosophy of The Simpsons\\copyright comes from my "
"favorite book \\cite{Simpson}."
msgstr ""
"Moja teza o filozofiji Simpsonovih\\copyright prihaja iz moje najljubše "
"knjige \\cite{Simpson}."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2722
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As it is often difficult to remember the exact citation key once you have "
"many references, &kile; provides an easy way to insert a citation. Using "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>LaTeX </guimenu><guimenuitem>References</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Cite</guimenuitem></menuchoice> a list with all the "
"citation keys pops up. Select the correct reference and a citation will be "
"inserted into your document. To update the list of keys, either save the "
"file, or <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Refresh Structure</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, or press <keycap>F12</keycap>. With code "
"completion enabled, &kile; will show you a list of all the "
"<userinput>bibitem</userinput>-labels as soon as you open up a <userinput>"
"\\cite</userinput> command."
msgstr ""
"Ker si je velikokrat težko zapomniti točen ključ citata, ko imate enkrat "
"veliko sklicev, ponuja &kile; enostaven način za vstavljanje citatov. Z "
"klikom na <menuchoice><guimenu>LaTeX </guimenu><guimenuitem>References</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Cite</guimenuitem></menuchoice> se bo prikazal "
"seznam z vsemi ključi citatov. Izberite pravilen sklic in citat bo vstavljen "
"v vaš dokument. Da posodobite seznam ključev, lahko shranite datoteko, "
"kliknete <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Refresh Structure</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, ali pa pritisnete <keycap>F12</keycap>. Z "
"omogočenim dopolnjevanjem kode bo &kile; prikazal seznam vseh "
"<userinput>bibitem</userinput> oznak takoj, ko odprete ukaz <userinput>"
"\\cite</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2732
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The final result in your document's bibliography would then look like this:"
msgstr "Končni rezultat v bibliografiji vašega dokumenta bo izgledal tako:"

#. Tag: computeroutput
#: index.docbook:2734
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"[1] Homer J. Simpson. Mmmmm...donuts. Evergreen Terrace Printing Co., "
"Springfield, SomewhereUSA, 1998."
msgstr ""
"[1] Homer J. Simpson. Mmmmm...donuts. Evergreen Terrace Printing Co., "
"Springfield, SomewhereUSA, 1998."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2737
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kile; can also work together with &bibtex; editors, such as &kbibtex; to "
"make it easier to enter citations. When a &bibtex; file is added to the "
"project, &kile; will help you complete citation commands, just as described "
"above."
msgstr ""
"&kile; lahko sodeluje tudi z urejevalniki &bibtex;-a, kot je &kbibtex; za "
"lažji vnos citatov. Ko je &bibtex; datoteka dodana v projekt, vam bo &kile; "
"pomagal dopolniti ukaze citatov, kot je opisano zgoraj."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2749
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Build Tools"
msgstr "Orodja za Grajenje"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2753
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compiling, converting and viewing"
msgstr "Prevajanje, pretvarjanje in ogledovanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2755
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To view the result of your work, you first need to compile the source. All "
"the build tools are grouped closely together in the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Build</guimenu><guisubmenu>Compile</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice>, <menuchoice><guimenu>Build</guimenu><guisubmenu>Convert</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice>, and <menuchoice><guimenu>Build</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>View</guisubmenu></menuchoice> menus."
msgstr ""
"Da si ogledate rezultat vašega dela, morate najprej prevesti izvorno kodo. "
"Vsa orodja za grajenje se nahajajo blizu skupaj v menijih "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Build</guimenu><guisubmenu>Compile</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice>, <menuchoice><guimenu>Build</guimenu><guisubmenu>Convert</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> in <menuchoice><guimenu>Build</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>View</guisubmenu></menuchoice> menus."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2762
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To compile your source code for screen viewers like &okular; or further "
"conversion, you can use the shortcut <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>2</keycap></"
"keycombo>. Then you can view the &DVI; file using your default viewer with "
"<keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>3</keycap></keycombo>, convert the &DVI; to a PS file "
"with <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>4</keycap></keycombo>, and view the PS file with "
"<keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>5</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Da prevedete vašo izvorno kodo za vaše pregledovalnike kot je &okular; ali "
"za nadaljnjo pretvorbo, lahko uporabite bližnjico <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>2</"
"keycap></keycombo>. Nato si lahko ogledate &DVI; datoteko z uporabo "
"privzetega pregledovalnika z <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>3</keycap></keycombo>, "
"pretvorite &DVI; v PS datoteko z <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>4</keycap></"
"keycombo> in ogledate PS datoteko z <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>5</keycap></"
"keycombo>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2771
#, no-c-format
msgid "&bibtex;"
msgstr "&bibtex;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2773
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are using <ulink url=\"http://www.ecst.csuchico.edu/~jacobsd/bib/"
"formats/bibtex.html\">&bibtex;</ulink> for your bibliography entries, you "
"usually have to follow a special compiling scheme. This means calling "
"&latex; and then &bibtex; and then &latex; twice again. Fortunately &kile; "
"is clever enough to detect automatically if it is necessary to call "
"additional tools like &bibtex;, &makeidx; and &asymptote;. This logic is "
"turned on by default and can be changed in <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure Kile...</guisubmenu><guisubmenu>Tools</"
"guisubmenu><guilabel>Build</guilabel></menuchoice> in the <guilabel>General</"
"guilabel> tab in the &latex; and &pdflatex; tools."
msgstr ""
"Če uporabljate <ulink url=\"http://www.ecst.csuchico.edu/~jacobsd/bib/"
"formats/bibtex.html\">&bibtex;</ulink> za vaše vnose bibliografije, morate "
"ponavadi slediti posebni shemi za prevajanje. To pomeni, da kličete &latex;, "
"nato &bibtex; in nato spet drugič &latex;. Na srečo je &kile; dovolj "
"pameten, da samodejno zazna, če je potrebno uporabiti dodana orodja kot so "
"&bibtex;, &makeidx; in &asymptote;. Ta logika je privzeto vključena in se jo "
"da spremeniti v <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Nastavi "
"Kile...</guisubmenu><guisubmenu>Tools</guisubmenu><guilabel>Build</"
"guilabel></menuchoice> v zavihku <guilabel>General</guilabel> v orodjih "
"&latex; in &pdflatex;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2796
#, no-c-format
msgid "MetaPost and &asymptote;"
msgstr "MetaPost in &asymptote;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2798
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to compile your document with <application>MetaPost</"
"application> or <application>&asymptote;</application>, picture drawing "
"programs, you can do it with <menuchoice><guimenu>Build</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Compile</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Metapost</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>, or <menuchoice><guimenu>Build</guimenu><guisubmenu>Compile</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>&asymptote;</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite prevesti svoj dokument z aplikacijo <application>MetaPost</"
"application> ali <application>&asymptote;</application>, za risanje slik, "
"lahko to storite z <menuchoice><guimenu>Build</guimenu><guisubmenu>Compile</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Metapost</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, ali "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Build</guimenu><guisubmenu>Compile</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>&asymptote;</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2806
#, no-c-format
msgid "&pdflatex;"
msgstr "&pdflatex;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2808
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is also another way to compile your document, if you want a PDF: you "
"can run &pdflatex;, that will compile the source directly into a PDF file, "
"with <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>6</keycap></keycombo>: you can then view the "
"compiled file by pressing <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>7</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja tudi drug način za prevajanje vašega dokumenta, če želite PDF: "
"zaženete lahko &pdflatex;, ki bo prevedel izvorno kodo neposredno v PDF "
"datoteko, z <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>6</keycap></keycombo>: nato si lahko "
"ogledate prevedeno datoteko s pritiskom na <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>7</"
"keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2813
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can convert a PS into a PDF with <keycombo>&Alt;"
"<keycap>8</keycap></keycombo>, or a &DVI; directly into a PDF with "
"<keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>9</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Alternativno lahko pretvorite PS v PDF z <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>8</keycap></"
"keycombo> ali pa &DVI; neposredno v PDF z <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>9</keycap></"
"keycombo>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2817
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using &pdflatex; instead of &latex; may be just a matter of simplicity or "
"habit, but sometimes the behavior of the two programs can differ."
msgstr ""
"Uporabljanje &pdflatex; namesto &latex; je lahko le stvar preprostosti ali "
"navade, vendar se lahko v nekaterih primerih vedenje teh dveh programov "
"razlikuje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2824
#, no-c-format
msgid "&latex; to Web"
msgstr "&latex; v Splet"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2826
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Finally, you may want to publish your work on the web and not just on paper. "
"You may then use the <application>latex2html</application> program, that can "
"be called from &kile;'s menu <menuchoice><guimenu>Build</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Convert</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>LaTeX to Web</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. The result will be placed in a subfolder of the "
"work folder, and you will be able to see the result of the conversion "
"choosing the menu item <menuchoice><guimenu>Build</guimenu><guisubmenu>View</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>View &HTML;</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Na koncu se zna zgoditi, da boste želeli svoje delo objaviti na spletu, ne "
"le na papirju. V tem primeru lahko uporabite program "
"<application>latex2html</application>, ki se ga da poklicati iz &kile;-ovega "
"menija <menuchoice><guimenu>Build</guimenu><guisubmenu>Convert</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>LaTeX to Web</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Rezultat se "
"bo nahajal v podmapi delovne datoteke, vi pa ga boste lahko videli z izbiro "
"elementa seznama <menuchoice><guimenu>Build</guimenu><guisubmenu>View</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>View &HTML;</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2838
#, no-c-format
msgid "Passing Command Line Parameters"
msgstr "Posredovanje Parametrov Ukazne Vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2840
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to pass some specific command line parameters to the compile, "
"convert or view tools, you can configure their call in "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Configure Kile...</"
"guisubmenu><guisubmenu>Tools</guisubmenu><guilabel>Build</guilabel></"
"menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite posredovati nekaj določenih parametrov ukazne vrstice orodjem za "
"prevajanje, pretvarjanje in ogledovanje, lahko konfigurirate njihov klic v "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj Kile...</"
"guisubmenu><guisubmenu>Orodja</guisubmenu><guilabel>Izgradi</guilabel></"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2849
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Quick Preview</title>"
msgstr "<title>Hitri predogled</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2851
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You will always need some time to view the result, when working with "
"&latex;. &latex; has to compile the source and the viewer has to be called. "
"This can be annoying if you only changed some letters in an equation "
"difficult to typeset. &kile; offers a <emphasis>Quick Preview</emphasis> "
"mode, where you can compile only a part of a document and save a lot of "
"time. It supports four different modes, which can be combined with seven "
"configurations."
msgstr ""
"Ko delate z &latex;-om, boste za ogled rezultata vedno morali počakati nekaj "
"časa. &latex; mora prevesti izvorno kodo in priklicati je treba "
"pregledovalnik. To je lahko neprijetno, če želite le spremeniti nekaj črk v "
"enačbi. &kile; ponuja način <emphasis>Hitrega Predogleda</emphasis>, s "
"katerim lahko prevedete le del dokumenta in s tem prihranite veliko časa. "
"Podpira štiri različne načine, ki se jih da kombinirati s sedmimi "
"konfiguracijami."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:2859
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Quick Preview</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Hitri Predogled</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2865
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Quick Preview</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Hitri Predogled</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2870
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All settings must be done in <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure Kile...</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Tools</"
"guimenuitem><guilabel>Preview</guilabel></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Vse nastavitve se nastavi v <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Nastavi Kile...</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Tools</"
"guimenuitem><guilabel>Preview</guilabel></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:2875
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Quick Preview Configuration</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Nastavitve Hitrega predogleda</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2881
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Quick Preview Configuration</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Nastavitve Hitrega predogleda</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2888
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selection Mode"
msgstr "Način izbire"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2890
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The user has to select a part of the document. Menu entry "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Build</guimenu><guisubmenu>QuickPreview</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Selection</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or the keyboard "
"shortcut <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo>,"
"<keycap>S</keycap> will start the selected programs. &kile; takes the "
"preamble of the original text, so that all packages and user defined "
"commands are included. The user can choose one of eight predefined "
"configurations:"
msgstr ""
"Uporabnik mora izbrati del dokumenta. Vnos menija "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Build</guimenu><guisubmenu>QuickPreview</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Selection</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali bližnjica "
"na tipkovnici <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>P</keycap></"
"keycombo>,<keycap>S</keycap> bo zagnala izbrane programe. &kile; vzame "
"preambulo originalnega besedila, da so vsi paketi in uporabnikovi na novo "
"definirani ukazi vključeni. Uporabnik lahko izbira enega od osmih vnaprej "
"definiranih konfiguracij:"

#. Tag: application
#: index.docbook:2897
#, no-c-format
msgid "LaTeX+&DVI; (embedded viewer)"
msgstr "LaTeX+&DVI; (vgrajeni pregledovalnik)"

#. Tag: application
#: index.docbook:2898
#, no-c-format
msgid "LaTeX+&DVI; (&okular;)"
msgstr "LaTeX+&DVI; (&okular;)"

#. Tag: application
#: index.docbook:2899
#, no-c-format
msgid "LaTeX+PS (embedded viewer)"
msgstr "LaTeX+PS (vgrajeni pregledovalnik)"

#. Tag: application
#: index.docbook:2900
#, no-c-format
msgid "LaTeX+PS (&okular;)"
msgstr "LaTeX+PS (&okular;)"

#. Tag: application
#: index.docbook:2901
#, no-c-format
msgid "PDFLaTeX+PDF (embedded viewer)"
msgstr "PDFLaTeX+PDF (vgrajeni pregledovalnik)"

#. Tag: application
#: index.docbook:2902
#, no-c-format
msgid "PDFLaTeX+PDF (&okular;)"
msgstr "PDFLaTeX+PDF (&okular;)"

#. Tag: application
#: index.docbook:2903
#, no-c-format
msgid "XeLaTeX+PDF (embedded viewer)"
msgstr "XeLaTeX+PDF (vgrajeni pregledovalnik)"

#. Tag: application
#: index.docbook:2904
#, no-c-format
msgid "XeLaTeX+PDF (&okular;)"
msgstr "XeLaTeX+PDF (&okular;)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2907
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This should be sufficient for all situations for which a quick preview is "
"needed."
msgstr ""
"To bi moralo zadostovati za vse situacije, za katere je hitri predogled "
"potreben."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2913
#, no-c-format
msgid "Environment Mode"
msgstr "Način Območja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2915
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Very often you want to preview the current environment, and especially "
"mathematical environments, which sometimes may be difficult to write. &kile; "
"offers a very fast way to do this. No selection is needed, just choose "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Build</guimenu><guisubmenu>QuickPreview</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Environment</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or the "
"keyboard shortcut <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>P</keycap></"
"keycombo>,<keycap>E</keycap> and the current environment will be compiled "
"and shown."
msgstr ""
"Zelo pogosto želite predogled trenutnega območja, še posebno v matematičnih "
"območjih, ki jih je včasih težko napisati. &kile; ponuja zelo hiter način za "
"to. Označevanje kode ni potrebno, le izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Build</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>QuickPreview</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Environment</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali uporabite bližnjico na tipkovnici <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo>,<keycap>E</keycap> "
"in trenutno območje bo prevedeno in prikazano."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2926
#, no-c-format
msgid "Subdocument Mode"
msgstr "Način Poddokumenta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2928
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have a large project with a lot of documents, compiling the whole "
"project is not a great idea, if you have made changes only in one single "
"document. &kile; is able to compile and show a preview of the current "
"subdocument. It takes the preamble from the master document and only "
"compiles the current part when you choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Build</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>QuickPreview</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Subdocument</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> or the keyboard shortcut <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo>,<keycap>D</keycap>."
msgstr ""
"Če imate velik projekt z veliko dokumenti, potem prevajanje celega dokumenta "
"res ni najboljša ideja, če ste spremenili le enega od dokumentov. &kile; "
"lahko prevede in prikaže predogled trenutnega poddokumenta. Vzame preambulo "
"iz master dokumenta in prevede le trenuten del. Izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Build</guimenu><guisubmenu>QuickPreview</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Subdocument</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali bližnjico "
"na tipkovnici <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>P</keycap></"
"keycombo>,<keycap>D</keycap>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2939
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mathgroup Mode"
msgstr "Način Matematičnih Skupin"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2941
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The mathgroup preview mode allows you to preview the mathgroup you are "
"currently editing. &kile; takes the preamble from the master document and "
"only compiles the mathgroup the cursor is currently in when you choose "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Build</guimenu><guisubmenu>QuickPreview</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Mathgroup</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or the keyboard "
"shortcut <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo>,"
"<keycap>M</keycap>."
msgstr ""
"Način predogleda matematičnih skupin vam omogoča, da si predogledate "
"matematično skupino, ki jo trenutno urejate. &kile; vzame preambulo iz "
"master dokumenta in prevede le matematično skupino, na kateri se trenutno "
"nahaja kazalec, ko izberete <menuchoice><guimenu>Build</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>QuickPreview</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Mathgroup</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali bližnjico <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"&Alt;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo>,<keycap>M</keycap>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2950
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quick Preview in Bottom Bar"
msgstr "Hitri Predogled v Spodnji Vrstici"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2952
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Instead of showing the preview in a new document &kile; can also be "
"configured to use the bottom bar for preview compilations. You can activate "
"this feature in the quick preview configuration panel."
msgstr ""
"Namesto da se predogled kaže v novem dokumentu, se da &kile; nastaviti tudi "
"tako, da uporablja spodnjo vrstico za predoglede prevodov. To funkcijo lahko "
"aktivirate v nastavitvah hitrega predogleda."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2961
#, no-c-format
msgid "Graphic File Formats"
msgstr "Formati Grafičnih Datotek"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2965
#, no-c-format
msgid "&latex; and &pdflatex;"
msgstr "&latex; in &pdflatex;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2967
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&pdflatex;, when used with <userinput>graphics</userinput> or "
"<userinput>graphicx</userinput> packages, can correctly compile PNG and JPG "
"files into &DVI; or PDF, but is not able to handle EPS files. Conversely, "
"the process of compiling with &latex; to &DVI; and converting to PS and "
"eventually PDF does support EPS, but does not support PNG and JPG."
msgstr ""
"Ko je &pdflatex; uporabljen skupaj s paketi <userinput>graphics</userinput> "
"ali <userinput>graphicx</userinput>, lahko pravilno prevede PNG in JPG "
"datoteke v &DVI; ali PDF, ni pa zmožen tega z EPS datotekami. Nasprotno "
"proces prevajanja &latex;-a v &DVI; in pretvarjanje v PS in nazadnje v PDF "
"podpira EPS, ne podpira pa PNG in JPG."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2973
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A lot of users want to create PDF documents, but also want to use the "
"excellent <application>Pstricks</application> package to create &PostScript; "
"graphics, or they want to use the &PostScript; output of mathematical and "
"scientific software like <application>Mathematica</application>, "
"<application>Maple</application> or <application>MuPAD</application>. These "
"&latex; users have to compile first in &PostScript;, even if they want to "
"create PDF documents, because these programs produce &PostScript; code which "
"cannot be managed by &pdflatex;. However, it is not so hard as it may sound, "
"because &kile; will help."
msgstr ""
"Veliko uporabnikov želi ustvariti PDF dokumente, pa tudi uporabljati odličen "
"paket <application>Pstricks</application> za ustvarjanje &PostScript; "
"grafik, ali pa želijo uporabiti izhode &PostScript;-a za matematično in "
"znanstveno programsko opremo kot so <application>Mathematica</application>, "
"<application>Maple</application> ali <application>MuPAD</application>. Ti "
"uporabniki &latex;-a morajo prevesti najprej v &PostScript;, tudi če želijo "
"ustvariti PDF dokumente, saj ti programi proizvedejo &PostScript; kodo, ki "
"se je ne da upravljati z &pdflatex;. Kakor koli to ni tako zahtevno kot se "
"sliši, saj pri tem pomaga &kile;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2985
#, no-c-format
msgid "Graphics Conversion"
msgstr "Pretvorba Grafike"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2987
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To overcome this frustrating loop, when you want to include both "
"&PostScript; code and PNG or JPG files, you have a number of workarounds:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite premagati to frustrirajočo zanko, ko želite vključiti oboje, "
"&PostScript; kodo in datoteke PNG ali JPG, imate številne rešitve:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2991
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you need a file in PS format, but have JPG or PNG graphics, you can also "
"simply use &pdflatex; with &DVI; output first, and then run "
"<application>dvips</application> to create the PS file. You see that "
"&pdflatex; is a very good choice, if your source contains no &PostScript; "
"code at all."
msgstr ""
"Če potrebujete datoteko v formatu PS, imate pa JPG ali PNG grafiko, lahko "
"najprej uporabite tudi &pdflatex; z izhodom &DVI; in nato poženete "
"<application>dvips</application>, da ustvarite datoteko PS. Tako lahko "
"vidite, da je &pdflatex; zelo dobra izbira, če vaš vir ne vsebuje nobene "
"&PostScript; kode."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2996
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can convert EPS files to PNG or other formats with utilities as the "
"<ulink url=\"http://www.gimp.org/\"><application>Gimp</application></ulink> "
"or <ulink url=\"http://www.imagemagick.org/\">&imagemagick;</ulink> and use "
"&pdflatex;."
msgstr ""
"EPS datoteke lahko pretvorite v PNG ali druge formate s pripomočki kot so "
"<ulink url=\"http://www.gimp.org/\"><application>Gimp</application></ulink> "
"ali <ulink url=\"http://www.imagemagick.org/\">&imagemagick;</ulink> in "
"uporabite &pdflatex;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3001
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A preferred way is to convert EPS graphics to PDF graphics with "
"<command>epstopdf</command>, which comes with every &tex; distribution and "
"then use &pdflatex;. It produces high quality graphics, and you can even "
"control the result with some of the following options:"
msgstr ""
"Priporočen način, da pretvorite grafiko EPS v PDF, je z <command>epstopdf</"
"command>, ki je vključen v vsaki &tex; distribuciji, in nato uporabite "
"&pdflatex;. Proizvede grafiko visoke kvalitete, rezultate pa lahko celo "
"kontrolirate z naslednjimi možnostmi:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:3007
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"-dAutoFilterColorImages=false\n"
"        -dAutoFilterGrayImages=false\n"
"        -sColorImageFilter=FlateEncode\n"
"        -sGrayImageFilter=FlateEncode\n"
"        -dPDFSETTINGS=/prepress\n"
"        -dUseFlateCompression=true"
msgstr ""
"-dAutoFilterColorImages=false\n"
"        -dAutoFilterGrayImages=false\n"
"        -sColorImageFilter=FlateEncode\n"
"        -sGrayImageFilter=FlateEncode\n"
"        -dPDFSETTINGS=/prepress\n"
"        -dUseFlateCompression=true"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3010
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Even better: if your system allows <userinput>shell-escape</userinput>, "
"conversion can be done on the fly. All you have to do is to include the "
"<application>epstopdf</application> package, which is part of all &tex; "
"distributions, with the command <userinput>\\usepackage{epstopdf}</"
"userinput>. Assuming that your code is: <programlisting>\n"
"        \\includegraphics[width=5cm]{test.eps}\n"
"</programlisting> When you call &pdflatex; with option <option>--shell-"
"escape</option>, graphics <filename>test.eps</filename> is automatically "
"converted into <filename>test.pdf</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Še bolje: če vaš sistem dovoljuje <userinput>shell-escape</userinput>, je "
"mogoče pretvorbo izvesti sproti. Le vključiti morate paket "
"<application>epstopdf</application>, ki je vključen v vseh &tex; "
"distribucijah, z ukazom <userinput>\\usepackage{epstopdf}</userinput>. Ob "
"predpostavki, da je vaša koda: <programlisting>\n"
"        \\includegraphics[width=5cm]{test.eps}\n"
"</programlisting> Ko pokličete &pdflatex; z možnostjo <option>--shell-"
"escape</option>, bo grafika <filename>test.eps</filename> samodejno "
"pretvorjena v <filename>test.pdf</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3020
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This conversion will take place each time you run &pdflatex;. If your "
"graphics command is given implicitly: <programlisting>\n"
"        \\includegraphics[width=5cm]{test}\n"
"</programlisting> <application>epstopdf</application> checks whether "
"<filename>test.pdf</filename> is already available, so that the conversion "
"step can be skipped."
msgstr ""
"Ta pretvorba se bo zgodila vsakič ko zaženete &pdflatex;. Če je vaš grafični "
"ukaz podan implicitno: <programlisting>\n"
"        \\includegraphics[width=5cm]{test}\n"
"</programlisting> <application>epstopdf</application> preveri, ali je "
"<filename>test.pdf</filename> že dostopen, da se lahko pretvorbi izognemo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3028
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can convert the other way around, and use &latex; and PS-PDF conversion. "
"This is not always a good idea, since EPS encapsulation of JPG or PNG can "
"yield larger files, that in turn yield unnecessarily large documents. This "
"is however <emphasis>highly</emphasis> dependent on the graphic utility that "
"you use, since EPS can encapsulate other graphics, but not all applications "
"support this perfectly. Some might actually try to build your JPG image with "
"vectors and various scripting, which will result in gigantic files. "
"Conversion of all graphics formats to EPS can be done by <ulink url=\"http://"
"www.imagemagick.org/\">&imagemagick;</ulink>. Another simple program that "
"does this process correctly is <ulink url=\"http://www.tex.uniyar.ac.ru/"
"win32/tools/jpg2ps/\"><application>jpg2ps</application></ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Prevedete lahko tudi v drugo smer in uporabite &latex; in PS-PDF pretvorbo. "
"To ni vedno dobra ideja, saj EPS-jeva enkapsulacija JPG ali PNG datoteke "
"lahko privede do precej večjih datotek, kar potem privede do nepotrebno "
"velikih dokumentov. Vendar pa je to <emphasis>močno</emphasis> odvisno od "
"grafičnega pripomočka, ki ga uporabljate, saj EPS lahko enkapsulira druge "
"grafike, vendar tega ne podpirajo vse aplikacije popolno. Nekatere bodo "
"morda celo poskušale zgraditi JPG sliko z vektorji in različnimi skriptami, "
"kar privede do ogromnih datotek. Pretvorbo vseh grafičnih formatov v EPS je "
"mogoče narediti z <ulink url=\"http://www.imagemagick.org/\">&imagemagick;-"
"om</ulink>. Še en enostaven program, ki opravi to nalogo pravilno, je <ulink "
"url=\"http://www.tex.uniyar.ac.ru/win32/tools/jpg2ps/\"><application>jpg2ps</"
"application></ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3040
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also use an automatic conversion. All graphics files are converted "
"on the fly to EPS, and inserted into the PS document. This is a comfortable "
"way, but you have to set up your system properly. This is discussed in the "
"section <link linkend=\"build_epsgraphics\">EPS Graphics</link>."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite lahko tudi samodejno pretvorbo. Vse grafične datoteke bodo "
"pretvorjene v EPS sproti in bodo vstavljene v PS dokument. To je udoben "
"način, vendar ga je potrebno pravilno nastaviti. To je opisano v razdelku "
"<link linkend=\"build_epsgraphics\">EPS Grafike</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3051
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use the right File for the right Graphic"
msgstr "Uporabite pravo Datoteko za pravo Grafiko"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3054
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"EPS is sort of a graphic vector scripting language, describing all the lines "
"and dots the graphic is made of; it looks good even when magnified beyond "
"its default size, and suits best diagrams and vectorial graphics natively "
"produced in EPS, which look very clear and sharp while maintaining a very "
"small byte size."
msgstr ""
"EPS je neke vrste grafični vektorski skriptni jezik, ki opisuje vse črte in "
"pike, iz katerih je sestavljena grafika; izgleda dobro, tudi če je povečana "
"preko privzete velikosti, in najbolje ustreza diagramom in vektorskim "
"grafikam, izvirno izdelanim v EPS, ki so videti zelo jasne in ostre, hkrati "
"pa ohranjajo zelo majhno velikost v bajtih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3058
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"PNG (or the deprecated &GIF;) is a <emphasis>non-lossy</emphasis> file "
"format, with good compression and quality. It is very good for diagrams, "
"scans of drawings, or anything whose sharpness you do want to retain. It is "
"sometimes overkill when used for photos."
msgstr ""
"PNG (ali zastarel &GIF;) je <emphasis>neizguben</emphasis> format datoteke z "
"dobro kompresijo in kvaliteto. Dober je za diagrame, skenirane risbe ali "
"katero koli stvar, pri kateri želite ohraniti ostrino. Včasih je to "
"pretirano za fotografije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3062
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"JPG is a <emphasis>lossy</emphasis> format, that compresses files better "
"than PNG at the price of some loss in the picture detail. This is usually "
"irrelevant for photos, but may cause bad quality for diagrams, drawings, and "
"may make some thin lines disappear outright; in those cases use EPS or PNG."
msgstr ""
"JPG je <emphasis>izguben</emphasis> format, ki kompresira datoteke bolje kot "
"PNG v zameno za nekaj izgub pri podrobnostih slike. To je ponavadi "
"nepomembno pri fotografijah, lahko pa povzroči slabšo kvaliteto pri "
"diagramih in risbah, saj pri tem lahko izginejo nekatere tanke črte; v teh "
"primerih uporabite raje EPS ali PNG."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3068
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"But always remember: garbage in, garbage out! No conversion will make a bad "
"picture good."
msgstr ""
"Vendar ne pozabite: smeti noter, smeti ven! Nobena pretvorba ne bo polepšale "
"slabe slike."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3076
#, no-c-format
msgid "EPS Graphics"
msgstr "EPS Grafike"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3078
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"EPS graphics files are the traditional way to insert graphics files into "
"&latex; documents. As mailing lists are full with questions concerning EPS "
"graphics, we will discuss some important aspects and demonstrate how &kile; "
"supports them."
msgstr ""
"EPS grafične datoteke so tradicionalen način vstavljanja grafik v &latex;-"
"ove dokumente. Ker so e-poštni seznami polni vprašanj v zvezi z EPS "
"grafikami, bomo nekaj pomembnejših vidikov opisali tukaj in demonstrirali, "
"kako jih &kile; podpira."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3085
#, no-c-format
msgid "&latex; and EPS Graphics"
msgstr "&latex; in EPS Grafike"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3087
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you decided to use the traditional &latex; to produce PS or PDF output, "
"you will probably run into some problems with graphics. You have to use EPS "
"graphics (Encapsulated &PostScript;); no JPEG or PNG files. This should be "
"no problem, as there are a lot of <link linkend=\"build_graphics_conversion"
"\">converters</link> like <command>convert</command> from the excellent "
"<ulink url=\"http://www.imagemagick.org/\">&imagemagick;</ulink> package. "
"But, it needs some time of course."
msgstr ""
"Če se odločite, da boste uporabljali tradicionalni &latex; za proizvajanje "
"PS ali PDF datotek, boste najbrž naleteli na nekaj problemov z grafikami. "
"Uporabiti morate EPS grafike (Encapsulated &PostScript;); in ne JPEG ali PNG "
"datotek. Tukaj ne bi smelo biti problemov, saj obstaja veliko <link linkend="
"\"build_graphics_conversion\">pretvornikov</link> kot <command>convert</"
"command> iz odličnega paketa <ulink url=\"http://www.imagemagick.org/"
"\">&imagemagick;</ulink>. Je pa seveda za to potrebno nekaj časa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3096
#, no-c-format
msgid "The EPS files are used by both &latex; and the &DVI;-PS converter:"
msgstr "EPS datoteke so uporabljene v obeh, &latex;-u in &DVI;-PS pretvorniku:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3099
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&latex; scans the EPS file for the bounding-box line, which tells &latex; "
"how much space to reserve for the graphics."
msgstr ""
"&latex; skenira EPS datoteko za črto zunanje obrobe, ki pove &latex;-u, "
"koliko prostora naj prihrani za grafiko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &DVI;-PS converter then reads the EPS file and inserts the graphics in "
"the PS file."
msgstr ""
"Nato &DVI;-PS pretvornik prebere EPS datoteko in vstavi grafiko v PS "
"datoteko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3107
#, no-c-format
msgid "This has some implications:"
msgstr "To ima nekaj implikacij:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&latex; never reads the EPS file if the bounding-box parameters are "
"specified in the graphics insertion command."
msgstr ""
"&latex; nikoli ne prebere EPS datoteke, če so parametri za zunanjo obrobo "
"določeni z ukazom vstavitve grafike."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Since &latex; cannot read non-ASCII files, it cannot read the bounding-box "
"information from compressed or non-EPS graphics files."
msgstr ""
"Ker &latex; ne more brati datotek, ki niso zapisane z znaki ASCII, ne more "
"prebrati informacij o zunanji obrobi iz stisnjene datoteke ali iz grafike, "
"ki ni v formatu EPS."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The EPS graphics are not included in the &DVI; file. Since the EPS files "
"must be present when the &DVI; file is converted to PS, the EPS files must "
"accompany the &DVI; files whenever they are moved."
msgstr ""
"EPS grafike niso vključene v &DVI; datoteko. Ker morajo biti EPS datoteke "
"prisotne, ko se &DVI; datoteka pretvarja v PS, morajo EPS datoteke "
"spremljati &DVI; datoteke vedno, ko so te premaknjene."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now you can call &latex;, and a &DVI;-PS converter like <application>dvips</"
"application> to create your &PostScript; document. If your goal is a PDF "
"document, you should run <command>dvips</command> with option <option>-Ppdf</"
"option> and then call <command>ps2pdf</command>. You will find a lot of "
"documents describing this solution."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj lahko pokličete &latex; in &DVI;-PS pretvornik kot je "
"<application>dvips</application>, da ustvarite vaš &PostScript; dokument. Če "
"je vaš cilj ustvariti PDF dokument, zaženite <command>dvips</command> z "
"možnostjo <option>-Ppdf</option> in nato pokličite <command>ps2pdf</"
"command>. Našli boste, da veliko dokumentov opisuje to rešitev."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3132
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &PostScript; Way of &kile;"
msgstr "&PostScript;-ov način programa &kile;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kile; helps you to get the bounding-box information. If you have installed "
"<ulink url=\"http://www.imagemagick.org/\">&imagemagick;</ulink> package, "
"&kile; will extract this information from the EPS file and insert it as an "
"option. This is done automatically when you select the graphics file. There "
"are two advantages to proceeding like this:"
msgstr ""
"&kile; vam pomaga pridobiti informacije o zunanji obrobi. Če imate nameščen "
"paket <ulink url=\"http://www.imagemagick.org/\">&imagemagick;</ulink>, bo "
"&kile; izvlekel te informacije iz EPS datoteke in jih vstavil kot možnost. "
"To je narejeno samodejno, ko izberete grafično datoteko. Obstajata dve "
"prednosti, če tako nadaljujete:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3141
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The information is already scanned in the dialog, and need not to be done by "
"&latex; later on."
msgstr ""
"Informacije so že skenirane v pogovornem oknu, zato &latex;-u kasneje ni "
"treba narediti tega še enkrat."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Even more important is that the width and height of the picture can be "
"calculated, when the resolution is known. This information will be shown "
"near the top of the dialog, and may serve as a clue when you want to scale "
"the graphics."
msgstr ""
"Še pomembneje je, da sta višina in širina slike lahko izračunani, ko je "
"ločljivost znana. Te informacije bodo prikazane blizu vrha pogovornega okna "
"in lahko služijo kot namig, ko želite povečati grafiko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kile; can also support zipped or gzipped EPS files, which are much smaller "
"than uncompressed EPS files. But, this feature can only be used with a "
"special system setup and a change of your local graphics configuration, as "
"it is described in the <link linkend=\"build_graphics_bitmap\">Bitmap "
"Graphics</link> section."
msgstr ""
"&kile; lahko podpira tudi zazipane ali gzipane EPS datoteke, ki so veliko "
"manjše kot nestisnjene EPS datoteke. Vendar je to lastnost mogoče "
"uporabljati le s posebno nastavitvijo sistema in s spremembo v lokalni "
"nastavitvi vaših grafik, kot je opisano v razdelku <link linkend="
"\"build_graphics_bitmap\">Bitne Grafike</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3162
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &PostScript; Way and Bitmap Graphics"
msgstr "&PostScript; Način in Bitne Grafike"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If your system allows <userinput>shell-escape</userinput>, &kile; also "
"supports an easy way to include bitmap graphics, if you set up your &tex; "
"system properly. There is no need to convert JPEG or PNG graphics, this can "
"be done automatically when the &DVI; file is converted to PS."
msgstr ""
"Če vaš sistem dopušča <userinput>shell-escape</userinput>, potem &kile; "
"podpira tudi lažji način za vključitev bitnih grafik, če nastavite vaš &tex; "
"sistem pravilno. Ni potrebe po pretvarjanju grafik JPEG ali PNG, to se "
"izvede samodejno, ko je &DVI; datoteka pretvorjena v PS."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&latex; needs some information about the file suffixes. The package "
"<userinput>graphicx</userinput> looks for a file <filename>graphics.cfg</"
"filename>, which must be somewhere in your search path for &latex; "
"documents. Search for entries like:"
msgstr ""
"&latex; potrebuje nekaj informacij o priponah datotek. Paket "
"<userinput>graphicx</userinput> poišče datoteko <filename>graphics.cfg</"
"filename>, ki mora biti nekje na vaši iskalni poti za &latex;-ove dokumente. "
"Poiščite vnose, kot so:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:3174
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\\DeclareGraphicsRule{.pz}{eps}{.bb}{}%\n"
"   \\DeclareGraphicsRule{.eps.Z}{eps}{.eps.bb}{}%\n"
"   \\DeclareGraphicsRule{.ps.Z}{eps}{.ps.bb}{}%\n"
"   \\DeclareGraphicsRule{.ps.gz}{eps}{.ps.bb}{}%\n"
"   \\DeclareGraphicsRule{.eps.gz}{eps}{.eps.bb}{}%"
msgstr ""
"\\DeclareGraphicsRule{.pz}{eps}{.bb}{}%\n"
"   \\DeclareGraphicsRule{.eps.Z}{eps}{.eps.bb}{}%\n"
"   \\DeclareGraphicsRule{.ps.Z}{eps}{.ps.bb}{}%\n"
"   \\DeclareGraphicsRule{.ps.gz}{eps}{.ps.bb}{}%\n"
"   \\DeclareGraphicsRule{.eps.gz}{eps}{.eps.bb}{}%"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3176
#, no-c-format
msgid "and replace these lines with:"
msgstr "in nadomestite te vrstice z:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:3178
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\\DeclareGraphicsRule{.pz}{eps}{.bb}{}%\n"
"   \\DeclareGraphicsRule{.eps.Z}{eps}{.eps.bb}{}%\n"
"   \\DeclareGraphicsRule{.ps.Z}{eps}{.ps.bb}{}%\n"
"   \\DeclareGraphicsRule{.ps.gz}{eps}{.ps.bb}{}%\n"
"   % changed or new graphic rules\n"
"   \\DeclareGraphicsRule{.eps.zip}{eps}{.eps.bb}{`unzip -p #1}%   zipped "
"EPS\n"
"   \\DeclareGraphicsRule{.eps.gz}{eps}{.eps.bb}{`gunzip -c #1}%   gzipped "
"EPS\n"
"   \\DeclareGraphicsRule{.jpg}{eps}{}{`convert #1 eps:-}%         JPEG\n"
"   \\DeclareGraphicsRule{.gif}{eps}{.bb}{`convert #1 eps:-}%      GIF\n"
"   \\DeclareGraphicsRule{.png}{eps}{.bb}{`convert #1 eps:-}%      PNG\n"
"   \\DeclareGraphicsRule{.tif}{eps}{.bb}{`convert #1 eps:-}%      TIFF\n"
"   \\DeclareGraphicsRule{.pdf}{eps}{.bb}{`convert #1 eps:-}%      PDF-"
"graphics"
msgstr ""
"\\DeclareGraphicsRule{.pz}{eps}{.bb}{}%\n"
"   \\DeclareGraphicsRule{.eps.Z}{eps}{.eps.bb}{}%\n"
"   \\DeclareGraphicsRule{.ps.Z}{eps}{.ps.bb}{}%\n"
"   \\DeclareGraphicsRule{.ps.gz}{eps}{.ps.bb}{}%\n"
"   % changed or new graphic rules\n"
"   \\DeclareGraphicsRule{.eps.zip}{eps}{.eps.bb}{`unzip -p #1}%   zipped "
"EPS\n"
"   \\DeclareGraphicsRule{.eps.gz}{eps}{.eps.bb}{`gunzip -c #1}%   gzipped "
"EPS\n"
"   \\DeclareGraphicsRule{.jpg}{eps}{}{`convert #1 eps:-}%         JPEG\n"
"   \\DeclareGraphicsRule{.gif}{eps}{.bb}{`convert #1 eps:-}%      GIF\n"
"   \\DeclareGraphicsRule{.png}{eps}{.bb}{`convert #1 eps:-}%      PNG\n"
"   \\DeclareGraphicsRule{.tif}{eps}{.bb}{`convert #1 eps:-}%      TIFF\n"
"   \\DeclareGraphicsRule{.pdf}{eps}{.bb}{`convert #1 eps:-}%      PDF-"
"graphics"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You will find this file, for example in Debian, at <filename>/etc/texmf/"
"latex/graphics.cfg</filename>. The best way to proceed is to copy this file "
"to your local texpath and then change this copy. See your &tex; distribution "
"manual to learn how to get a list of your &tex; folders."
msgstr ""
"To datoteko boste našli, npr. v Debianu na mestu <filename>/etc/texmf/latex/"
"graphics.cfg</filename>. Najboljši način, da nadaljujete, je, da prekopirate "
"to datoteko na vašo lokalno besedilno pot in nato spremenite to kopijo. "
"Glejte priročnik vaše &tex; distribucije, če se želite naučiti, kako "
"pridobiti seznam vaših &tex; map."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With this configuration file you are able to insert bitmap graphics and "
"zipped or gzipped EPS files in &latex;. The command for conversion is given "
"by <command>dvips</command>. When you look at the conversion command you "
"will see that no extra file is created. The result of the conversion process "
"is directly piped into the PS file. The only thing &latex; must know is the "
"size of the graphics, and therefore we need the bounding box, which is "
"provided by &kile;."
msgstr ""
"S to konfiguracijsko datoteko boste lahko vstavili bitno grafiko in zipane "
"ali gzipane EPS datoteke v &latex;. Ukaz za pretvorbo je podan z "
"<command>dvips</command>. Ko pogledate ukaz za pretvorbo, boste videli, da "
"ni ustvarjena nobena dodatna datoteka. Rezultat procesa pretvorbe je takoj "
"neposredno prenesen v PS datoteko. Edina stvar, ki jo mora &latex; še "
"vedeti, je velikost grafike, in zato potrebujemo mejni okvir, ki nam ga "
"zagotovi &kile;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some say that this way is insecure; you have to decide on how to work. In "
"any case, you need no bounding box, as &kile; will extract this information "
"from all types of graphics."
msgstr ""
"Nekateri pravijo, da na način ni varen; odločiti se morate, na kakšen način "
"boste delali. V vsakem primeru ne potrebujete mejnega okvirja, saj bo &kile; "
"izvlekel te informacije iz katere koli grafike."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3201
#, no-c-format
msgid "&pdflatex; and EPS Graphics"
msgstr "&pdflatex; in EPS Grafike"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As already stated, &pdflatex; is not able to handle EPS graphic files, but "
"converters like <link linkend=\"build_graphics_epstopdf\">epstopdf</link> "
"will help. The best way is to include package <filename>epstopdf</filename>, "
"which must follow the <userinput>graphicx</userinput> package."
msgstr ""
"Kot smo že povedali, &pdflatex; ni zmožen procesiranja grafičnih datotek "
"EPS, vendar pri tem pomagajo pretvorniki kot je <link linkend="
"\"build_graphics_epstopdf\">epstopdf</link>. Najboljši način je, da "
"vključite paket <filename>epstopdf</filename>, ki mora slediti paketu "
"<userinput>graphicx</userinput>."

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:3208
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\\usepackage[pdftex]{graphicx}\n"
"   \\usepackage{epstopdf}"
msgstr ""
"\\usepackage[pdftex]{graphicx}\n"
"   \\usepackage{epstopdf}"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now you can already include EPS graphics, if you run <command>pdflatex</"
"command> with option <option>--shell-escape</option>, but we can make it "
"even better and also handle zipped or gzipped EPS files. Again we have to "
"change the graphics configuration file <filename>graphics.cfg</filename> as "
"above. This time we search for:"
msgstr ""
"Zdaj lahko že vključite grafiko EPS, če zaženete <command>pdflatex</command> "
"z možnostjo <option>--shell-escape</option>, vendar lahko to še izboljšamo, "
"saj lahko obdelamo tudi zazipane ali gzipane EPS datoteke. Spet moramo "
"spremeniti konfiguracijsko datoteko za grafike <filename>graphics.cfg</"
"filename> kot zgoraj. Tokrat iščemo za:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:3216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"% pdfTeX is running in pdf mode\n"
"   \\ExecuteOptions{pdftex}%"
msgstr ""
"% pdfTeX is running in pdf mode\n"
"   \\ExecuteOptions{pdftex}%"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3218
#, no-c-format
msgid "and simply add some lines:"
msgstr "in enostavno dodamo nekaj vrstic:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:3220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"% pdfTeX is running in pdf mode\n"
"   \\ExecuteOptions{pdftex}%\n"
"   \\AtEndOfPackage{%\n"
"      \\g@addto@macro\\Gin@extensions{.eps.gz,.eps.zip}%\n"
"      \\@namedef{Gin@rule@.eps.gz}#1{{pdf}{.pdf}{`gunzip -c #1 | epstopdf -f "
">\\Gin@base.pdf}}%\n"
"      \\@namedef{Gin@rule@.eps.zip}#1{{pdf}{.pdf}{`unzip -p #1 | epstopdf -f "
">\\Gin@base.pdf}}%\n"
"   }%"
msgstr ""
"% pdfTeX is running in pdf mode\n"
"   \\ExecuteOptions{pdftex}%\n"
"   \\AtEndOfPackage{%\n"
"      \\g@addto@macro\\Gin@extensions{.eps.gz,.eps.zip}%\n"
"      \\@namedef{Gin@rule@.eps.gz}#1{{pdf}{.pdf}{`gunzip -c #1 | epstopdf -f "
">\\Gin@base.pdf}}%\n"
"      \\@namedef{Gin@rule@.eps.zip}#1{{pdf}{.pdf}{`unzip -p #1 | epstopdf -f "
">\\Gin@base.pdf}}%\n"
"   }%"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With these lines, &pdflatex; is able to handle EPS files, and hopefully "
"there should be no more issues concerning graphics."
msgstr ""
"S temi vrsticami lahko &pdflatex; obdeluje datoteke EPS, in od zdaj naprej "
"ne bi smelo biti več napak v zvezi z grafikami."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3231
#, no-c-format
msgid "Master Document"
msgstr "Master Dokument"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Defining your document as a master allows you to work with separate files, "
"which gives you a parent document (or Master document), and child documents "
"that make up a complete work. After having defined your Master document, "
"with the corresponding command in the <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> menu, all "
"the commands of the <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> menu will apply only to this "
"document, even when you are working on the child documents. You can even "
"close the Master document."
msgstr ""
"Če definirate vaš dokument kot master, vam to omogoča, da delate z ločenimi "
"datotekami, kar vam naredi starševski dokument (ali Master dokument) in "
"otrok dokument, ki skupaj predstavljajo celotno delo. Potem ko ste "
"definirali vaš Master dokument, se bodo z ustreznimi ukazi v meniju "
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> vsi ukazi menija <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> "
"nanašali le na ta dokument, tudi ko delate na vaših otrok dokumentih. Master "
"dokument lahko celo zaprete."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3244
#, no-c-format
msgid "Error Handling"
msgstr "Obravnavanje Napak"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3246
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After you have compiled something, &kile; takes a look at the error messages "
"that were generated. If there are any errors or warnings, they will be "
"briefly reported in the <guilabel>Log and Messages</guilabel> window. One "
"can take a closer look at the messages by selecting "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Build</guimenu><guimenuitem>View Log File</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, or by using the keyboard shortcut <keycombo>&Alt;"
"<keycap>0</keycap></keycombo>. The generated log is then displayed in the "
"<guilabel>Log and Messages</guilabel> view; errors and warnings are "
"highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Potem ko ste prevedli nekaj, gre &kile; čez sporočila o napakah, ki so bila "
"ustvarjena. Če se pojavijo katera opozorila o napakah, bodo o njih na kratko "
"poročano v oknu <guilabel>Beležnica in Sporočila</guilabel>. Sporočila si "
"lahko podrobneje ogledate s klikom na <menuchoice><guimenu>Build</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>View Log File</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali pa z "
"bližnjico na tipkovnici  <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>0</keycap></keycombo>. "
"Ustvarjena beležnica je nato prikazana v pogledu <guilabel>Beležnica in "
"Sporočila</guilabel>; napake in opozorila bodo poudarjena."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:3254
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Viewing the log</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Ogledovanje beležnice</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:3260
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Viewing the log</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Ogledovanje beležnice</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3262
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Viewing the log</para>"
msgstr "<para>Ogledovanje beležnice</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3266
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can easily jump from one message in the log file to another by using the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Build</guimenu><guimenuitem>Next / Previous LaTeX "
"Error / Warning</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu items, or by using the "
"corresponding toolbar buttons."
msgstr ""
"Preprosto lahko skačete od enega sporočila v beležni datoteki do drugega z "
"uporabo elementov menija <menuchoice><guimenu>Build</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Next / Previous LaTeX Error / Warning</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> ali z uporabo ustreznih gumbov orodne vrstice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To jump to the line in the &latex; source where the error or warning "
"occurred, click on the error or warning in the <guilabel>Log and Messages</"
"guilabel> view. &kile; will take you automatically to the offending line."
msgstr ""
"Za skok v vrstico v &latex;-ovi izvorni kodi, kjer je prišlo do napake, "
"kliknite na napako ali opozorilo v pogledu <guilabel>Beležka in Sporočila</"
"guilabel>. &kile; vas bo samodejno popeljal do prave vrstice."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3279
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Watch File Mode"
msgstr "Način Ogledovanja Datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3281
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you launch the <guibutton>Quickbuild</guibutton> command, a viewer of "
"some sort will normally be called after the compilation. If you are not "
"using an embedded viewer, a new window will be opened every time."
msgstr ""
"Ko zaženete ukaz <guibutton>Quickbuild</guibutton>, bo poklican eden od "
"pregledovalnikov takoj po prevajanju. Če ne uporabljate vgrajenega "
"pregledovalnika, se bo vsakič odprlo novo okno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3285
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are adjusting the look of your document, you might launch "
"<guibutton>Quickbuild</guibutton> very often, and have many viewer windows "
"open on your desktop; to avoid this confusion, you can activate the "
"<guibutton>Watch file</guibutton> mode, that will prevent "
"<guibutton>Quickbuild</guibutton> from launching a viewer."
msgstr ""
"Če prilagajate videz vašega dokumenta, boste najbrž zagnali "
"<guibutton>Quickbuild</guibutton> kar precej pogosto, in boste zato imeli "
"odprtih veliko oken pregledovalnika na vašem namizju; da se tej zmedi "
"izognete, lahko aktivirate način <guibutton>Glej datoteko</guibutton>, ki bo "
"preprečila <guibutton>QUickbuild-u</guibutton>, da zažene nov pogled."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3290
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This mode is of course useless with the embedded viewers, as you have to "
"close them anyway to get back to editing the document and recompiling."
msgstr ""
"Ta način je seveda neuporaben z vgrajenimi pregledovalniki, saj jih morate "
"tako ali tako zapreti, če želite nazaj na urejanje svojega dokumenta."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3299
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigating the &latex; Source"
msgstr "Navigiranje Izvorne kode &latex;-a"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3303
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Using the Structure View</title>"
msgstr "<title>Uporabljanje Pogleda Strukture</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Structure</guilabel> view shows the hierarchy of the document "
"being created in &kile;, and allows you to quickly navigate it, showing its "
"segmentation. To navigate around your document, all you need to do is to "
"left click on any label, chapter, section, subsection, etc., and you will be "
"taken to the beginning of the corresponding area."
msgstr ""
"Pogled <guilabel>Strukture</guilabel> prikaže hierarhijo dokumenta, ki se "
"ustvarja v &kile;-u in vam omogoča, da se hitro navigirate po njegovem "
"prikazu segmentacije. Da se navigirate po svojem dokumentu morate le "
"kliknite na oznako, poglavje, razdelek, podrazdelek, itd., in skočili boste "
"na začetek ustreznega območja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3311
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you included a separate &latex; file in your source using the <userinput>"
"\\input</userinput> or <userinput>\\include</userinput> tags, these files "
"will be referred to in the <guilabel>Structure</guilabel> view; double-"
"clicking on their names will make &kile; bring up the included file in the "
"editor window."
msgstr ""
"Če vključite ločeno datoteko &latex; v vašo izvorno kodo z uporabo značk "
"<userinput>\\input</userinput> ali <userinput>\\include</userinput>, bo "
"povezava nanje tudi v pogledu <guilabel>Strukture</guilabel>; z dvojnim "
"klikom na njihovo ime bo &kile; odprl vključeno datoteko v urejevalniku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3316
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The hierarchy tree also has a separate branch for labels used in the text."
msgstr ""
"Drevo hierarhije ima tudi ločeno vejo za oznake uporabljene v besedilu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3333
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the Context Menu"
msgstr "Uporabljanje Kontekstnega Menija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3335
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Most of the entries in the structure view have a lot of entries in the "
"context menu, which you can open with a right mouse click. So look at the "
"structure view in the following picture."
msgstr ""
"Večina vnosov v pogledu strukture ima veliko vnosov v kontekstnem meniju, ki "
"ga lahko odprete z desnim klikom. Poglejte torej pogled na strukturo na "
"naslednji sliki."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:3340
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Using the Structure View</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Uporabljanje Pogleda Strukture</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:3346
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Using the Structure View</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Uporabljanje Pogleda Strukture</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You will find some labels, some sectioning entries, two figure environments "
"and three pictures. If you right click on one of the sectioning entries, a "
"menu with some useful commands will popup. All commands like "
"<guibutton>Select</guibutton>, <guibutton>Delete</guibutton> or "
"<guibutton>Comment</guibutton> will work with all lines, which belong to "
"this section."
msgstr ""
"Našli boste nekaj oznak, nekaj vnosov v razdelke, dva območja figur in tri "
"slike. Če z desno kliknete enega od vnosov razdelkov, se prikaže meni z "
"nekaj uporabnimi ukazi. Vsi ukazi kot so <guibutton>Izberi</guibutton>, "
"<guibutton>Izbriši</guibutton> ali <guibutton>Komentiraj</guibutton> bodo "
"delovali z vsemi vrsticami, ki pripadajo temu razdelku."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:3357
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Context menu for sectioning entries</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Kontekstni meni za vnose razdelkov</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:3363
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Context menu for sectioning entries</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Kontekstni meni za vnose razdelkov</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3368
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking on a figure or table entry will offer some actions with respect to "
"references and a right click on a graphics entry will offer some programs to "
"open the graphics."
msgstr ""
"Klik na vnos figure ali tabele bo ponudil nekaj dejanj v zvezi s sklici, "
"desni klik na vnos grafike pa bo ponudil nekaj programov za odpiranje "
"grafike."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:3372
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>Context menu for figure/tables and graphics entries</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Kontekstni meni za figure/tabele in grafične vnose</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:3378
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Context menu for figure/tables and graphics entries</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Kontekstni meni za figure/tabele in grafične vnose</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3387
#, no-c-format
msgid "Updating the Structure View"
msgstr "Posodabljanje Pogleda Strukture"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3389
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To update your structure view you can either go to "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Refresh Structure</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, hit <keycombo><keycap>F12</keycap></keycombo>, or "
"you can save your document, which will make &kile; update its "
"<guilabel>Structure</guilabel> view."
msgstr ""
"Da posodobite vaš pogled struktura lahko greste pod "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Refresh Structure</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, pritisnete <keycombo><keycap>F12</keycap></"
"keycombo> ali pa shranite svoj dokument, pri čemer bo &kile; posodobil "
"njegov pogled <guilabel>Strukture</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3400
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmarks"
msgstr "Zaznamki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3402
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Bookmarks are your reference to a segment of text or a line inside the "
"&kile; environment. To use a bookmark, select a specific line of your "
"document you would like to return to, then press <keycombo>&Ctrl; <keycap>B</"
"keycap></keycombo>, and &kile; will add a bookmark to this line. "
"Alternatively, you can also set a bookmark by highlighting a line and "
"choosing the menu labeled <menuchoice><guimenu>Bookmarks</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Set Bookmark</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Zaznamki so vaša referenca na segment besedila ali vrstico znotraj &kile;-"
"ovega območja. Če želite uporabiti zaznamek, izberite določeno vrstico "
"dokumenta, v katero se želite vrniti, in nato pritisnite <keycombo>&Ctrl; "
"<keycap>B</keycap></keycombo> in &kile; bo dodal zaznamek na to vrstico. "
"Zaznamek pa lahko po drugi poti ustvarite tudi tako, da označite vrstico in "
"izberete meni z oznako <menuchoice><guimenu>Bookmarks</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Set Bookmark</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3410
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove all your bookmarks, select <menuchoice><guimenu>Bookmarks</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Clear All Bookmarks</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odstraniti vse zaznamke, izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Bookmarks</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Clear All Bookmarks</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3419
#, no-c-format
msgid "Projects"
msgstr "Projekti"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3423
#, no-c-format
msgid "Working with Projects"
msgstr "Delo s Projekti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3425
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In &kile; you can create and work with <emphasis>projects</emphasis>. A "
"project is a group of &latex;, graphic, &bibtex;, or other files that "
"contain all the information that is used to build your complete document. A "
"typical project would be a document consisting of several chapters, written "
"in different <literal role=\"extension\">.tex</literal> files; all of them "
"could be included in a project, to make the whole document easier to manage. "
"The specifications of the project are stored in a special file, with "
"extension <literal role=\"extension\">.kilepr</literal>."
msgstr ""
"V &kile;-u lahko ustvarite in delate s <emphasis>projekti</emphasis>. "
"Projekt je skupina &latex;-ovih grafik, &bibtex;-ovih ali drugih datotek, ki "
"vsebujejo vse informacije, ki jih potrebujete, da zgradite celoten dokument. "
"Tipični projekt bi bil dokument, sestavljen iz več poglavij, ki so napisani "
"v različnih <literal role=\"extension\">.tex</literal> datotekah; vse so "
"lahko vključene v projekt, da je upravljanje z dokumentom lažje. "
"Specifikacije projekta so shranjene v posebni datoteki s končnico <literal "
"role=\"extension\">.kilepr</literal>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3432
#, no-c-format
msgid "A Project adds the following functionalities:"
msgstr "Projekt doda naslednje funkcionalnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3435
#, no-c-format
msgid "You need not set a master document, &kile; does this automatically."
msgstr ""
"Ni vam potrebno nastavljati master dokumenta, &kile; naredi to samodejno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3436
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Project files can easily be archived together by going to "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Project</guimenu><guimenuitem>Archive</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"Projektne datoteke se da preprosto arhivirati skupaj tako, da greste pod "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Projekt</guimenu><guimenuitem>Archive</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3437
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Files and Projects</guilabel> view shows which files are "
"included in the project."
msgstr ""
"Pogled <guilabel>Datoteke in Projekti</guilabel> prikaže, katere datoteke so "
"vključene v projekt."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3439
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After opening a project, any file that was previously opened will be "
"restored with the original encoding and highlighting."
msgstr ""
"Potem ko odprete projekt, bo katera koli datoteka, ki je bila prej odprta, "
"obnovljena z originalnim enkodiranjem in poudarki."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3441
#, no-c-format
msgid "Code completion works across all project files."
msgstr "Dopolnjevanje kode deluje čez vse datoteke projekta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3442
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reference completion works across all project files."
msgstr "Dopolnjevanje sklicev deluje čez vse datoteke projekta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3443
#, no-c-format
msgid "Citation completion works across all project files."
msgstr "Dopolnjevanje citatov deluje čez vse datoteke projekta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3444
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search in all project files."
msgstr "Išči v vseh datotekah projekta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3445
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specify custom quickbuild and &makeidx; command."
msgstr "Navedi poljubna ukaza za quickbuild in &makeidx;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3448
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can find all project related commands in the <guilabel>Project</"
"guilabel>-menu. From there you can open, close and manage your projects."
msgstr ""
"Vse ukaze v zvezi z projekti lahko najdete v meniju <guilabel>Projekt</"
"guilabel>. Od tam lahko odprete, zaprete in upravljate z vašimi projekti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3454
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating a Project"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje Projekta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3456
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a project, select <menuchoice><guimenu>Project</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>New Project...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Projekt</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Project...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, da ustvarite nov projekt."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:3459
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Project creation window</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Okno za ustvarjanje projekta</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:3465
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Project creation window</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Okno za ustvarjanje projekta</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3469
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You will be asked to give the following information to create your project:"
msgstr "Povprašani boste po informacijah za ustvarjanje vašega projekta:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3473
#, no-c-format
msgid "Title of your project (<guilabel>Project title</guilabel> text field)."
msgstr ""
"Naslov vašega projekta (besedilno polje <guilabel>Naslov projekta</"
"guilabel>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3476
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The title of the project will be used to create a name of the project file "
"by transforming to lowercase and adding <filename role=\"extension\">."
"kilepr</filename> extension."
msgstr ""
"Naslov projekta se bo uporabil za naslov projektne datoteke tako, da se bodo "
"vse velike črke spremenile v male, zadaj pa bo dodana končnica <filename "
"role=\"extension\">.kilepr</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3481
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A folder where the project file will be stored (<guilabel>Project folder</"
"guilabel> text field)."
msgstr ""
"Mapa, kjer bodo shranjene datoteke projekta (besedilno polje "
"<guilabel>Projektna mapa</guilabel>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3486
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to create a new main file of the project check the "
"<guilabel>Create a new file and add it to this project</guilabel> item."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti novo glavno datoteko projekta, glejte element menija "
"<guilabel>Ustvari novo datoteko in jo dodaj k projektu</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3491
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you fill out the <guilabel>Filename</guilabel> box, you have to include "
"a relative path from where the <filename role=\"extension\">.kilepr</"
"filename> project file is stored (see the <guilabel>Project folder</"
"guilabel> item)."
msgstr ""
"Ko boste izpolnili okvirček <guilabel>Ime datoteke</guilabel>, morate "
"vključiti relativno pot od tam, kjer je shranjena <filename role=\"extension"
"\">.kilepr</filename> datoteka (glej element <guilabel>Projektna mapa</"
"guilabel>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3496
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type of the created file, <guilabel>Empty File</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Article</guilabel>, <guilabel>Book</guilabel>, <guilabel>Letter</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Report</guilabel>, &etc; can be chosen from a visual "
"list at the bottom of the <guilabel>File</guilabel> panel."
msgstr ""
"Vrsto datoteke, ki jo ustvarjate, <guilabel>Prazna Datoteka</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Članek</guilabel>, <guilabel>Knjiga</guilabel>, <guilabel>Pismo</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Poročilo</guilabel>, &etc; lahko izberete iz seznama na "
"dnu plošče <guilabel>Datoteka</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3501
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Extensions for the default files in the project can be selected using the "
"<guilabel>Extensions</guilabel> panel. Your choice will be used to define "
"the files that should be opened when you choose "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Project</guimenu><guimenuitem>Open All Project Files</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item and in the &kile; wizards. The "
"extensions in the text field should be separated with spaces."
msgstr ""
"Razširitve za privzete datoteke v projektu se lahko izbere s ploščo "
"<guilabel>Extensions</guilabel>. Vaša izbira bo uporabljena za določitev "
"datotek, ki naj bi se odprle, ko izberete element seznama "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Project</guimenu><guimenuitem>Open All Project Files</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> in &kile;-ove čarovnike. Imena razširitev naj bodo "
"v besedilnem polju ločene s presledki."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3510
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>The Files and Projects View</title>"
msgstr "<title>Pogled Datoteke in Projekti</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3512
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Files and Projects</guilabel> view is a button of the sidebar "
"menu. From this view, you can see the structure of your project, its files, "
"and the name of the <literal role=\"extension\">.kilepr</literal> file that "
"stores the project information. Adding, removing, or changing options in "
"your project is done via the <guilabel>Files and Projects</guilabel> view."
msgstr ""
"Pogled <guilabel>Datoteke in Projekti</guilabel> je gumb na meniju stranske "
"vrstice. S tem pogledom lahko vidite strukturo vašega projekta, njegovih "
"datotek in ime datoteke <literal role=\"extension\">.kilepr</literal>, v "
"kateri so shranjene informacije o projektu. Dodajanje, odstranjevanje ali "
"spreminjanje možnosti v vašem projektu se da izvesti s pomočjo pogleda "
"<guilabel>Datoteke in Projekti</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:3519
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Files and Projects View</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Datoteke in Projekti</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:3525
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Files and Projects View</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Datoteke in Projekti</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3527
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>The Files and Projects View</para>"
msgstr "<para>Datoteke in Projekti</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3535
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding and Removing Files"
msgstr "Dodajanje in Odstranjevanje Datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3537
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add a file to your project, open any &tex; file, right click on its name "
"in the <guilabel>Files and Projects</guilabel> view, and select "
"<guilabel>Add to Project</guilabel>. If you have opened multiple projects, a "
"dialog box will pop up in which you can specify to which project the file "
"should be added."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodati datoteko vašemu projektu, odprite datoteko &tex;, desno "
"kliknite na njeno ime v pogledu <guilabel>Datoteke in Projekti</guilabel> in "
"izberite <guilabel>Dodaj k Projektu</guilabel>. Če imate odprtih več "
"projektov, se bo prikazalo pogovorno okno, v katerem lahko navedete, "
"kateremu projektu želite dodati to datoteko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3546
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also right-click on the project's name in the <guilabel>Files and "
"Projects</guilabel> view, and select <guilabel>Add Files...</guilabel> to "
"bring up a file selection dialog."
msgstr ""
"Prav tako lahko desno kliknete na ime projekta v pogledu <guilabel>Datoteke "
"in Projekti</guilabel> in izberete <guilabel>Dodaj Datoteke... </guilabel>, "
"da se prikaže pogovorno okno za izbor datoteke."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:3551
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Adding a file to a project</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Dodajanje datoteke k projektu</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:3557
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Adding a file to a project</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Dodajanje datoteke k projektu</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3559
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Adding a file to a project</para>"
msgstr "<para>Dodajanje datoteke k projektu</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3563
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove a file from a project, right-click on it and select "
"<guilabel>Remove File</guilabel>. This does <emphasis>not</emphasis> delete "
"your file (and also does not close it), but only removes it from the list of "
"files contained in the <literal role=\"extension\">.kilepr</literal> "
"extension."
msgstr ""
"Če želite iz projekte odstraniti datoteko, desno kliknite nanjo in izberite "
"<guilabel>Odstrani Datoteko</guilabel>. To <emphasis>ne</emphasis> izbriše "
"vaše datoteke (in je tudi ne zapre), temveč jo le odstrani iz seznama "
"datotek, ki jih vsebuje razširitev <literal role=\"extension\">.kilepr</"
"literal>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3569
#, no-c-format
msgid "Archiving your Project"
msgstr "Arhiviranje Projekta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3571
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kile; allows you to easily backup your project by storing all its files "
"into a single archive (often known as a <emphasis>tarball</emphasis>). To "
"archive your project, right-click on its name in the <guilabel>Files and "
"Projects</guilabel> view, or select <menuchoice><guimenu>Project</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Archive</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"&kile; vam omogoča, da preprosto varnostno kopirate svoj projekt tako, da "
"shranite vse njegove datoteke v en sam arhiv (poznan kot <emphasis>tarball</"
"emphasis>). Desno kliknite na ime projekta v pogledu <guilabel>Datoteke in "
"Projekti</guilabel>, da arhivirate vaš projekt, ali pa izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Project</guimenu><guimenuitem>Archive</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3576
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, all files in a project are added to the archive. If you do not "
"want to include a certain file in the archive, right-click on it in the "
"<guilabel>Files and Projects</guilabel> view, and uncheck the "
"<guilabel>Include in Archive</guilabel> option."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto se bodo vse datoteke v projektu dodale v arhiv. Če ne želite "
"vključiti določene datoteke, desno kliknite nanjo v pogledu "
"<guilabel>Datoteke in Projekti</guilabel> in odkljukajte možnost "
"<guilabel>Vključi v Arhiv</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3580
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The archive operation is currently realized by executing the <command>tar</"
"command> from the project folder (where the <literal role=\"extension\">."
"kilepr</literal> file is located)."
msgstr ""
"Operacija arhiviranja je trenutno realizirana z izvajanjem ukaza "
"<command>tar</command> iz mape s projektom (kjer se nahaja datoteka <literal "
"role=\"extension\">.kilepr</literal>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3589
#, no-c-format
msgid "Project Options"
msgstr "Možnosti Projekta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3591
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kile; has a few options related to your project that can be set. To change "
"them, right-click on the title of your project and select <guilabel>Project "
"Options</guilabel>, and you will have the option of changing:"
msgstr ""
"&kile; ima nekaj možnosti v povezavi z vašim projektom, ki jih je mogoče "
"nastaviti. Desno kliknite na naslov vašega projekta in izberite "
"<guilabel>Možnosti Projekta</guilabel>, da spremenite te možnosti, in lahko "
"boste spreminjali:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3596
#, no-c-format
msgid "The title of your project."
msgstr "Naslov vašega projekta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3597
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default file extensions."
msgstr "Privzeto končnico datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3598
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Master document."
msgstr "Master dokument."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3599
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Quickbuild command."
msgstr "Ukaz za Quickbuild."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3600
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &makeidx; options."
msgstr "&makeidx; možnosti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3619
#, no-c-format
msgid "Closing a Project"
msgstr "Zapiranje Projekta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3621
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To close a project, select the <guilabel>Files and Projects</guilabel> view "
"from the vertical toolbar, right click on your project title, and then "
"select <guimenuitem> Close</guimenuitem>. This will close your project, all "
"the files associated with your project, and will also add the name of the "
"project you just closed to <guisubmenu>Open Recent Project...</guisubmenu> "
"in the <guimenu>Project</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Če želite zapreti projekt, izberite pogled <guilabel>Datoteke in Projekti</"
"guilabel> iz navpične orodne vrstice, desno kliknite na naslov projekta in "
"nato izberite <guimenuitem>Zapri</guimenuitem>. S tem boste zaprli vaš "
"projekt in vse datoteke povezane s projektom, ime tega projekta pa bo dodano "
"v <guisubmenu>Odpri Nedavni Projekt...</guisubmenu> v meniju "
"<guimenu>Projekt</guimenu>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3633
#, no-c-format
msgid "Document Encoding"
msgstr "Kodiranje Dokumenta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3635
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kile; editor allows you to read, convert and save text in the character "
"encoding your document needs. With this it is possible, for example, to use "
"accented characters, such as are commonly used in Italian or French, "
"directly in &latex; documents. Selecting the encoding for your document can "
"be done in two ways:"
msgstr ""
"Urejevalnik za &kile; vam omogoča, da berete, pretvarjate in shranjujete "
"besedilo v takem načinu kodiranja, ki ga vaš dokument potrebuje. S tem je na "
"primer mogoče uporabljati znake z naglasom, ki so pogosto uporabljeni v "
"italijanščini ali francoščini, neposredno v &latex;-ovih dokumentih. "
"Kodiranje za vaš dokument lahko izberete na dva načina:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3641
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"One way to set the document encoding is by using the submenu "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure Kile...</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Editor</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, where you can set "
"the default character encoding for all files."
msgstr ""
"Prvi način nastavljanja kodiranja dokumenta je z uporabo podmenija "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Nastavi Kile...</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Editor</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, kjer lahko "
"nastavite privzet način kodiranja znakov za vse datoteke."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:3646
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Set the default character encoding</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Nastavi privzet način kodiranja znakov</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:3652
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Set the default character encoding</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Nastavi privzet način kodiranja znakov</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3657
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A second way to set the encoding for a document is to choose the desired "
"encoding within the wizard to create a new document."
msgstr ""
"Drugi način nastavljanja kodiranja znakov za dokument je, da izberete želeno "
"kodiranje v čarovniku za ustvarjanje novega dokumenta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3661
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&latex; itself only understands ASCII, which represents a very limited set "
"of characters. Hence, it is not possible to use accented characters "
"directly. To use them nevertheless, a special syntax was invented: such as "
"for example <userinput>\\\"e</userinput> for <computeroutput>ë</"
"computeroutput>. The <application>inputenc</application> package is "
"available to help you with this. It is included in the preamble using "
"<userinput>\\usepackage[latin1]{inputenc}</userinput>, where the optional "
"argument specifies the encoding you would like to use (nowadays in most "
"cases <userinput>utf8</userinput>). This tells &latex; to translate all of "
"the <userinput>ë</userinput>'s you wrote to <userinput>\\\"e</userinput>'s "
"before compiling. Please refer to the <application>inputenc</application> "
"documentation directly for more information. Last but not least: remember to "
"make sure that your file is <emphasis>actually</emphasis> saved in the same "
"encoding you specified for the <application>inputenc</application> package!"
msgstr ""
"Sam &latex; razume le ASCII kodiranje, ki predstavlja zelo omejen nabor "
"znakov. Zato neposredna uporaba znakov z naglasom ni mogoča. Da jih kljub "
"temu lahko uporabljate, morate uporabiti posebno sintakso: kot je na primer "
"<userinput>\\\"e</userinput> za <computeroutput>ë</computeroutput>. Paket "
"<application>inputenc</application> vam lahko pomaga pri tem. Vključi se ga "
"v preambulo z značko <userinput>\\usepackage[latin1]{inputenc}</userinput>, "
"kjer neobvezni argument določa kodiranje, ki ga želite uporabljati (dandanes "
"je to največkrat <userinput>utf8</userinput>). To pove &latex;-u naj prevede "
"vsakega <userinput>ë</userinput>, ki ste ga napisali, v <userinput>\\\"e</"
"userinput> preden prevede izvorno kodo. Prosimo, oglejte si dokumentacijo "
"<application>inputenc</application> za več informacij. In še nazadnje: "
"prepričajte se, da je vaša datoteka <emphasis>dejansko</emphasis> shranjena "
"v istem načinu kodiranja, kot ste ga navedli za paket <application>inputenc</"
"application>!"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3672
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This multitude of different character coding tables has created numerous "
"problems: for example, you cannot write a course of Turkish in French "
"without losing one language's special characters. There is general agreement "
"that, sooner or later, everybody will switch to <ulink url=\"http://www."
"unicode.org\">Unicode</ulink>. There are many implementations of Unicode, "
"and <abbrev>UTF-8</abbrev> is the most successful in &Linux;; &Windows;&reg; "
"relies instead on the more cumbersome and less flexible <abbrev>UCS-2</"
"abbrev>. Most distributions have already begun setting their default "
"encoding to <abbrev>UTF-8</abbrev>, and therefore you may be very interested "
"in using the <userinput>utf8</userinput> argument to the "
"<userinput>inputenc</userinput> package."
msgstr ""
"Ta množica različnih tabel za kodiranje znakov je povzročila številne "
"težave: na primer, ne morete napisati tečaja turščine v francoščini, ne da "
"bi izgubili posebne znake enega jezika. Obstaja splošno soglasje, da bodo "
"prej ali slej vsi prešli na <ulink url=\"http://www.unicode.org\">Unicode</"
"ulink>. Obstaja veliko implementacij Unicode-a in <abbrev>UTF-8</abbrev> je "
"najuspešnejši na sistemih &Linux;; &Windows;&reg; se namesto tega zanaša na "
"bolj okornega in manj fleksibilnega <abbrev>UCS-2</abbrev>. Večina "
"distribucij je že začela nastavljati njihov privzet način kodiranja na "
"<abbrev>UTF-8</abbrev>, zato boste najbrž rade volje uporabili argument "
"<userinput>utf8</userinput> za paket <userinput>inputenc</userinput>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3685
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &ucs; Package"
msgstr "&ucs; Paket"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3686
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you don't have the &ucs; package installed, you can proceed as follows:"
msgstr "Če še nimate nameščenega paketa &ucs;, lahko nadaljujete tako:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3688
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Get the &ucs; package from <ulink url=\"http://www.ctan.org/tex-archive/"
"macros/latex/contrib/unicode/\">CTAN</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Pridobite paket &ucs; iz <ulink url=\"http://www.ctan.org/tex-archive/macros/"
"latex/contrib/unicode/\">CTAN</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3692
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To install it, unpack the downloaded file and place it in a folder listed in "
"your $<envar>TEXINPUTS</envar> environment variable. This can also be set "
"inside &kile;."
msgstr ""
"Da ga namestite, morate razpakirati nameščeno datoteko in jo postaviti v "
"mapo, ki je navedena v vaši okoljski spremenljivki $<envar>TEXINPUTS</"
"envar>. To se da storiti v &kile;-u."

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:3697
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\\usepackage{ucs}\n"
"\\usepackage[utf8]{inputenc}"
msgstr ""
"\\usepackage{ucs}\n"
"\\usepackage[utf8]{inputenc}"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3703
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>XeLaTeX</title>"
msgstr "<title>XeLaTeX</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3705
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are using <userinput>XeLaTeX</userinput>, you can simply load the "
"<userinput>xltxtra</userinput> package. It will additionally load all the "
"required packages."
msgstr ""
"Če uporabljate <userinput>XeLaTeX</userinput>, lahko enostavno namestite "
"paket <userinput>xltxtra</userinput>. Ta bo dodatno prenesel vse potrebne "
"pakete."

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:3707
#, no-c-format
msgid "\\usepackage{xltxtra}"
msgstr "\\usepackage{xltxtra}"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3713
#, no-c-format
msgid "&cjk; Support"
msgstr "&cjk; Podpora"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3715
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adding support for ideographic languages is quite tricky. However, once you "
"are done with it, it will work quite well. Other than installing packages, "
"there is some extra configuration work to do."
msgstr ""
"Dodajanje podpore za ideografske jezike je precej težavno. Vendar, ko boste "
"z njim končali, bo deloval precej dobro. Poleg nameščanja paketov je treba "
"opraviti še nekaj dodatnega konfiguracijskega dela."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3719
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Your &Linux; distribution might already have a &cjk; (Chinese, Japanese, "
"Korean) package ready for you, so you might be saved the hassle of manually "
"installing everything. Do check before going forward!"
msgstr ""
"Vaša distribucija &Linux;-a ima za vas morda že pripravljen paket &cjk; "
"(Chinese, Japanese, Korean), zato vam bo morda prihranjeno nameščanje vsega "
"na roke. Vseeno to preverite, preden greste naprej!"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3723
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is the possibility of using the &ucs; package in order to write short "
"snippets of &cjk; text, but that option is seriously limited as it does not "
"handle, among other things, newlines. Instead, we will install the complete "
"&cjk;-&latex; package and make it work for both &latex; and &pdflatex;. A "
"lot of this material has been inspired by <ulink url=\"http://www.ece.uci."
"edu/~chou/\">Pai H. Chou</ulink>'s <ulink url=\"http://www.ece.uci.edu/~chou/"
"unicode-tex.html\">page about how to setup &pdflatex;</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja možnost uporabe paketa &ucs; za pisanje nekaj kratkih delčkov "
"besedila v &cjk;, vendar je ta možnost resnično omejena, saj med drugim ne "
"poskrbi niti za nove vrstice. Namesto tega bomo mi namestili celoten paket "
"&cjk;-&latex; in ga usposobili za oba, &latex; in &pdflatex;. Navdih za "
"večino tega materiala smo črpali iz <ulink url=\"http://www.ece.uci.edu/"
"~chou/\">Pai H. Chou</ulink>-jeve <ulink url=\"http://www.ece.uci.edu/~chou/"
"unicode-tex.html\">strani, kako vzpostaviti &pdflatex;</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3733
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Download the <ulink url=\"http://www.ctan.org/tex-archive/help/Catalogue/"
"entries/cjk.html\">&cjk;</ulink> package. Copy its unpacked files to an "
"appropriate subfolder of $<envar>TEXMF</envar>, just as you did with the "
"&ucs; package before (see <xref linkend=\"ucs\" role=\"select: title "
"pageabbrv\"/>). The files will be unpacked in a <filename>CJK/X_Y.Z</"
"filename> folder; it is not important that you take them out, though it will "
"probably be tidier and easier for you to maintain."
msgstr ""
"Namestite paket <ulink url=\"http://www.ctan.org/tex-archive/help/Catalogue/"
"entries/cjk.html\">&cjk;</ulink>. Kopirajte njegove nerazpakirane datoteke v "
"ustrezno podmapo $<envar>TEXMF</envar>, kot ste prej to naredili s paketom "
"&ucs; (glej <xref linkend=\"ucs\" role=\"select: title pageabbrv\"/>). "
"Datoteke bodo razpakirane v mapi <filename>CJK/X_Y.Z</filename>; ni nujno, "
"da jih vzamete ven, vendar jih boste tako najbrž bolj urejeno in lažje "
"vzdrževali."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3742
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now you have to download a font that supports all the &cjk; characters you "
"need. You can choose any <literal role=\"extension\">*.ttf</literal> file "
"that covers them, but in this walkthrough we will use <ulink url=\"ftp://ftp."
"wu-wien.ac.at/pub/www/Netscape/communicator/extras/fonts/windows/Cyberbit.ZIP"
"\">Cyberbit</ulink>. Unzip the file and rename <filename>Cyberbit.ttf</"
"filename> to <filename>cyberbit.ttf</filename>, since uppercase might "
"confuse your system."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj morate namestiti slog pisave, ki podpira vse &cjk; znake, ki jih boste "
"potrebovali. Izberete lahko katero koli <literal role=\"extension\">*.ttf</"
"literal> datoteko, ki poskrbi za to, vendar bomo v naši demonstraciji "
"uporabili datoteko <ulink url=\"ftp://ftp.wu-wien.ac.at/pub/www/Netscape/"
"communicator/extras/fonts/windows/Cyberbit.ZIP\">Cyberbit</ulink>. Razširite "
"datoteko in jo preimenujte iz <filename>Cyberbit.ttf</filename> v "
"<filename>cyberbit.ttf</filename>, saj lahko velike črke zmedejo sistem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3748
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Place <filename>cyberbit.ttf</filename> in a folder together with <ulink url="
"\"http://delloye.free.fr/Unicode.sfd\"><filename>Unicode.sfd</filename></"
"ulink>, and generate the <literal role=\"extension\">*.tfm</literal> and "
"<literal role=\"extension\">*.enc</literal> files with the command "
"<userinput><command>$ ttf2tfm cyberbit.ttf -w cyberbit@Unicode@</command></"
"userinput>. For some reason, sometimes this does not produce the hundreds of "
"files it should. Should that happen in your case, you can download both "
"<ulink url=\"http://www.ece.uci.edu/~chou/unicode/cyberbit-tfm.tgz"
"\"><literal role=\"extension\">*.tfm</literal></ulink> and <ulink url="
"\"http://www.ece.uci.edu/~chou/unicode/cyberbit-enc.tgz\"><literal role="
"\"extension\">*.enc</literal></ulink> files."
msgstr ""
"Premaknite <filename>cyberbit.ttf</filename> v mapo skupaj z <ulink url="
"\"http://delloye.free.fr/Unicode.sfd\"><filename>Unicode.sfd</filename></"
"ulink> in zgenerirajte datoteki <literal role=\"extension\">*.tfm</literal> "
"in <literal role=\"extension\">*.enc</literal> z ukazom <userinput><command>"
"$ ttf2tfm cyberbit.ttf -w cyberbit@Unicode@</command></userinput>. Iz nekega "
"razloga včasih to ne proizvede stotine datotek, kot bi moralo. V tem primeru "
"lahko prenesete obe datoteki <ulink url=\"http://www.ece.uci.edu/~chou/"
"unicode/cyberbit-tfm.tgz\"><literal role=\"extension\">*.tfm</literal></"
"ulink> in <ulink url=\"http://www.ece.uci.edu/~chou/unicode/cyberbit-enc.tgz"
"\"><literal role=\"extension\">*.enc</literal></ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3759
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Place the <literal role=\"extension\">*.tfm</literal> files in an "
"appropriate folder, say <filename>$<envar>TEXMF</envar>/fonts/tfm/bitstream/"
"cyberbit/</filename>; the <literal role=\"extension\">*.enc</literal> files "
"may be installed in <filename>$<envar>TEXMF</envar>/pdftex/enc/cyberbit/</"
"filename>."
msgstr ""
"Premaknite datoteke <literal role=\"extension\">*.tfm</literal> v primerno "
"mapo, npr. <filename>$<envar>TEXMF</envar>/fonts/tfm/bitstream/cyberbit/</"
"filename>; datoteke <literal role=\"extension\">*.enc</literal> je možno "
"namestiti v <filename>$<envar>TEXMF</envar>/pdftex/enc/cyberbit/</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3764
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now we need a map file to connect the <literal role=\"extension\">*.enc</"
"literal> files to the font. Download <ulink url=\"http://delloye.free.fr/"
"cyberbit.map\"><filename>cyberbit.map</filename></ulink> and install it in "
"<filename>$<envar>TEXMF</envar>/pdftex/config/</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj potrebujemo zemljevidno datoteko, da povežemo datoteke <literal role="
"\"extension\">*.enc</literal> z slogom pisave. Prenesite datoteko <ulink url="
"\"http://delloye.free.fr/cyberbit.map\"><filename>cyberbit.map</filename></"
"ulink> in jo namestite v <filename>$<envar>TEXMF</envar>/pdftex/config/</"
"filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3769
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Download another file, <ulink url=\"http://delloye.free.fr/c70cyberbit.fd"
"\"><filename>c70cyberbit.fd</filename></ulink>, and place it in an "
"appropriate folder. You may choose, for example, <filename>$<envar>TEXMF</"
"envar>/tex/misc/</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Prenesite še eno datoteko, <ulink url=\"http://delloye.free.fr/c70cyberbit.fd"
"\"><filename>c70cyberbit.fd</filename></ulink>, in jo premaknite v primerno "
"mapo. Izberete lahko na primer <filename>$<envar>TEXMF</envar>/tex/misc/</"
"filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3774
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The last file we have to generate is a &PostScript; Type 1 font, necessary "
"to read &DVI; files generated with &latex;. Run the command "
"<userinput><command>$ ttf2pfb cyberbit.ttf -o cyberbit.pfb</command></"
"userinput>, and copy the resulting <filename>cyberbit.pfb</filename> to a "
"folder such as <filename>$<envar>TEXMF</envar>/fonts/type1/cyberbit/</"
"filename>."
msgstr ""
"Zadnja datoteka, ki jo moramo ustvariti je &PostScript; slog pisave Tipa 1, "
"ki je nujen za branje datotek &DVI;, ki so ustvarjene z &latex;-om. Poženite "
"ukaz <userinput><command>$ ttf2pfb cyberbit.ttf -o cyberbit.pfb</command></"
"userinput> in kopirajte rezultat <filename>cyberbit.pfb</filename> v mapo, "
"kot je na primer <filename>$<envar>TEXMF</envar>/fonts/type1/cyberbit/</"
"filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3780
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Let's now place <filename>cyberbit.ttf</filename> among the fonts where "
"&latex; can find it. You could place it in a folder named <filename>"
"$<envar>TEXMF</envar>/fonts/truetype/</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj pa premaknite datoteko <filename>cyberbit.ttf</filename> med sloge "
"pisave, kjer jo &latex; lahko najde. Premaknete jo lahko v mapo z imenom "
"<filename>$<envar>TEXMF</envar>/fonts/truetype/</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3784
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check the configuration file you find at <filename>$<envar>TEXMF</envar>/"
"web2c/texmf.cnf</filename>, and make sure that the line mentioning "
"<envar>TTFONTS</envar> is uncommented and points to the folder where you "
"saved <filename>cyberbit.ttf</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Preverite konfiguracijsko datoteko, ki jo najdete na mestu <filename>"
"$<envar>TEXMF</envar>/web2c/texmf.cnf</filename> in se prepričate, da ni "
"zakomentirana vrstica <envar>TTFONTS</envar> in da kaže na mapo, kjer ste "
"shranili <filename>cyberbit.ttf</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3789
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To make it possible for &pdflatex; to use your &cjk; fonts, it is necessary "
"that you add a line in the configuration file <filename>$<envar>TEXMF</"
"envar>/pdftex/config/pdftex.cfg</filename>. Add <userinput>map +cyberbit."
"map</userinput> in the file to complete the configuration for &pdflatex;."
msgstr ""
"Da lahko &pdflatex; uporablja sloge pisave &cjk;, je nujno, da v "
"konfiguracijsko datoteko dodate vrstico <filename>$<envar>TEXMF</envar>/"
"pdftex/config/pdftex.cfg</filename>. Dodajte <userinput>map +cyberbit.map</"
"userinput> v datoteko, da dokončate konfiguracijo za &pdflatex;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3795
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To configure &latex; so that you can produce &DVI; files with &cjk; "
"characters, you have to add a line in file <filename>ttfonts.map</filename>. "
"The file might be in a folder named <filename>$<envar>TEXMF</envar>/ttf2pk/</"
"filename>, but you will probably have to look for it. Append the line "
"<userinput>cyberbit@Unicode@ cyberbit.ttf</userinput> to it."
msgstr ""
"Da konfigurirate &latex; tako, da lahko proizvedete &DVI; datoteke z &cjk; "
"znaki, morate dodati vrstico v datoteko <filename>ttfonts.map</filename>. "
"Datoteka je morda v mapi imenovani <filename>$<envar>TEXMF</envar>/ttf2pk/</"
"filename>, vendar jo boste najbrž morali poiskati. Dodajte ji vrstico "
"<userinput>cyberbit@Unicode@ cyberbit.ttf</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3802
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now, you only have to run <userinput><command>texhash</command></userinput> "
"and the system should be ready."
msgstr ""
"Vse kar morate zdaj še storiti, je zagnati <userinput><command>texhash</"
"command></userinput> in sistem bi moral biti pripravljen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3807
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To test whether your configuration is correct, you can try to compile <ulink "
"url=\"http://www.math.nus.edu.sg/aslaksen/cs/sample-utf8.tex\">this test "
"file</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Da stestirate, ali je vaša konfiguracija pravilna, lahko poskusite prevesti "
"<ulink url=\"http://www.math.nus.edu.sg/aslaksen/cs/sample-utf8.tex\">to "
"testno datoteko</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3812
#, no-c-format
msgid "&cjk; Troubleshooting"
msgstr "&cjk; Iskanje Napak"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3814
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are many things that can go wrong when adding &cjk; support manually. "
"If something seems not to work, the following checklist might help you."
msgstr ""
"Veliko stvari lahko gre narobe, ko sami dodajate &cjk; podporo. Če nekaj ne "
"deluje pravilno, vam bo morda pomagal naslednji seznam."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3820
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Obviously, since you run &latex; as a user and not as root, you must "
"<emphasis>allow</emphasis> ordinary users to access the new files. Make sure "
"all folders and files are accessible using the <command>chmod</command> "
"command."
msgstr ""
"Ker zaganjate &latex; kot uporabni in ne kot koren, morate "
"<emphasis>dovoliti</emphasis> navadnim uporabnikom, da lahko dostopajo do "
"novih datotek. Prepričajte se, da so vse datoteke in mape dostopne z ukazom "
"<command>chmod</command>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3825
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If &latex; writes a &DVI; without problems, but you cannot view it, it is "
"almost certainly because of some problems in the automatic generation of "
"<literal role=\"extension\">*.pk</literal> fonts. They are supposed to be "
"generated on the fly when viewing a &DVI; file, but this might fail for a "
"number of reasons: double-check <filename>ttfonts.map</filename> for your "
"custom line first. However, it might happen that your <command>ttf2pk</"
"command> command, which is usually invoked by the &DVI; viewer, has been "
"compiled <emphasis>without</emphasis> support for the <application>kpathsea</"
"application> libraries. If this is the case, <userinput><command>ttf2pk</"
"command> <option>--version</option></userinput> will make no mention of "
"<application>kpathsea</application>. As support for these libraries is "
"necessary, you might have to find a new package, or recompile "
"<application>FreeType 1</application> yourself."
msgstr ""
"Če &latex; napiše &DVI; brez problemov, vendar si je vi ne morete ogledati, "
"je to skoraj gotovo zaradi problemov s samodejnim generiranjem slogov pisave "
"<literal role=\"extension\">*.pk</literal>. Morali bi se zgenerirati sproti, "
"ko si ogledujete datoteko &DVI;, vendar to se lahko ponesreči iz številnih "
"razlogov: najprej drugič preglejte vašo spremenjeno vrstico v  "
"<filename>ttfonts.map</filename>. Kakor koli lahko se je zgodilo, da se je "
"vaš ukaz <command>ttf2pk</command>, ki ga ponavadi pokliče &DVI; "
"preegledovalnik, prevedel <emphasis>brez</emphasis> podpore za knjižnice "
"<application>kpathsea</application>. Če je to problem, potem "
"<userinput><command>ttf2pk</command> <option>--version</option></userinput> "
"ne bo omenil <application>kpathsea</application>. Kot podporo za te "
"knjižnice boste morda morali najti nov paket ali pa sami ponovno prevesti "
"<application>FreeType 1</application>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3847
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I input &cjk; in Unicode?"
msgstr "Kako vstavim &cjk; v Unicode?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3849
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are a number of different input engines, and the choice can depend "
"also on personal preference. The author uses <ulink url=\"http://www.scim-im."
"org/projects/skim\"><application>Skim</application></ulink>, a port to &kde; "
"of the <ulink url=\"http://www.scim-im.org\"><application>Scim</"
"application></ulink> engine. Refer to your distribution's documentation to "
"learn how to install these programs. Configuration of such programs can be "
"tricky too, in the case of <application>Skim</application> you will have to "
"define an environment variable <userinput><envar>XMODIFIERS</envar>="
"\"@im=SCIM\"</userinput> <emphasis>before</emphasis> starting "
"<application>X</application>."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja številno različnih vhodnih gonilnikov in izbira le-tega je lahko "
"odvisna od vaše osebne preference. Avtor uporablja <ulink url=\"http://www."
"scim-im.org/projects/skim\"><application>Skim</application></ulink>, vrata v "
"&kde; od gonilnika <ulink url=\"http://www.scim-im.org\"><application>Scim</"
"application></ulink>. Oglejte si dokumentacijo vaše distribucije, če se "
"želite naučiti, kako namestiti te programe. Konfiguracija teh programov zna "
"biti težavna, v primeru, da uporabljate <application>Skim</application>, "
"boste morali definirati okoljske spremenljivke <userinput><envar>XMODIFIERS</"
"envar>=\"@im=SCIM\"</userinput> <emphasis>preden</emphasis> zaženete "
"<application>X</application>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3870
#, no-c-format
msgid "Help"
msgstr "Pomoč"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3874
#, no-c-format
msgid "Help Documents"
msgstr "Dokumenti Pomoči"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3876
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&latex; is a rather sophisticated system, where basic features can be "
"expanded by a great variety of additional packages. &kile; provides numerous "
"different ways to aid the user."
msgstr ""
"&latex; je sofisticiran sistem, kjer je mogoče osnovne funkcije in lastnosti "
"razširiti z veliko različnimi dodatnimi paketi. &kile; zagotavlja številne "
"različne načine, da pomaga uporabniku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3880
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <menuchoice><guimenu>Help</guimenu> <guisubmenu>LaTeX Documentation</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> submenu includes links on documentation for all the "
"included packages and an additional &latex; reference."
msgstr ""
"Podmeni <menuchoice><guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu> <guisubmenu>LaTeX "
"Documentation</guisubmenu></menuchoice> vključuje povezave za vse vključene "
"pakete in dodatne &latex;-ove reference."

#. Tag: guimenu
#: index.docbook:3888
#, no-c-format
msgid "Documentation Browser"
msgstr "Brskalnik Dokumentacij"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3889
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A handy tool to browse all &latex; topics. Please install &latex; help "
"packages for your distribution if you need the full-fledged documentation "
"compendium."
msgstr ""
"Uporabno orodje za brskanje po &latex;-ovih temah. Namestite si &latex;-ov "
"paket pomoči za vašo distribucijo, če potrebujete popolno dokumentacijo."

#. Tag: guimenu
#: index.docbook:3893
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>LaTeX</guimenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>LaTeX</guimenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3894
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A full unofficial reference for &tex; and friends. This is not only a "
"description of all programs, but some important packages are also mentioned. "
"It also includes a full reference manual of &latex; commands&mdash;ideal for "
"looking up a particular piece of formatting while writing a document. As "
"this document is really extensive, it is referenced in &kile; by three "
"bookmarks."
msgstr ""
"Popolna neuradna referenca za &tex; in prijatelje. To ni le opis vseh "
"programov, ampak so omenjeni tudi nekateri pomembni paketi. Vključuje tudi "
"celoten referenčni priročnik za &latex; ukaze&mdash;idealen za iskanje "
"določenega dela oblikovanja med pisanjem dokumenta. Ker je ta dokument res "
"obsežen, se nanj sklicuje &kile; s tremi zaznamki."

#. Tag: guimenu
#: index.docbook:3903
#, no-c-format
msgid "LaTeX Commands"
msgstr "LaTeX Ukazi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3904
#, no-c-format
msgid "Another alphabetical index of the most common &latex; commands."
msgstr "Še eno abecedno kazalo najpogostejših &latex; ukazov."

#. Tag: guimenu
#: index.docbook:3909
#, no-c-format
msgid "LaTeX Environments"
msgstr "LaTeX Območja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3910
#, no-c-format
msgid "An alphabetical index of the most common &latex; environments."
msgstr "Abecedno kazalo najpogostejših &latex; območij."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3920
#, no-c-format
msgid "Context Sensitive Help"
msgstr "Kontekstno občutljiva pomoč"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3922
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kile; also supports a context sensitive help, which is called with "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo>,"
"<keycap>K</keycap>. In <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure Kile...</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Kile</"
"guimenuitem><guilabel>Help</guilabel></menuchoice> you can choose whether "
"you want to use &kile;'s &latex; reference or the help system of &tetex;/"
"&texlive;, which is the default setting."
msgstr ""
"&kile; podpira tudi kontekstno občutljivo pomoč, ki je priklicana z "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo>,"
"<keycap>K</keycap>. V meniju <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Nastavi Kile...</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Kile</"
"guimenuitem><guilabel>Help</guilabel></menuchoice> lahko izberete, ali "
"želite uporabljate &kile;-ov &latex; sklic ali sistem pomoči za &tetex;/"
"&texlive;, ki je privzeta nastavitev."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3945
#, no-c-format
msgid "Searching for Keywords"
msgstr "Iskanje Ključnih Besed"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3947
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is not always easy to find the right document as &tetex;/&texlive; ships "
"with a huge number of help documents. In order to facilitate this process, "
"&tetex;/&texlive; provides a tiny program called <application>texdoctk</"
"application>. It provides a database of all the help documents, for which "
"&kile; offers a user-friendly interface."
msgstr ""
"Ni vedno lahko najti pravega dokumenta, saj &tetex;/&texlive; ustvarja "
"veliko dokumentov pomoči. Da si olajšate ta proces, je &tetex;/&texlive; "
"ustvaril majhen program <application>texdoctk</application>. Zagotavlja bazo "
"podatkov za vse dokumente pomoči, za katere &kile; ponuja uporabniku "
"prijazen vmesnik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3965
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All the documents are grouped into categories. Additionally, one can search "
"for package names or keywords. &kile; will then show only the help documents "
"matching the search string."
msgstr ""
"Vsi dokumenti so združeni v kategorije. Dodatno lahko iščete po imenih "
"paketov ali ključnih besedah. &kile; bo nato prikazal le dokumente z "
"ujemajočim nizom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3981
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A mouse double-click or the <keycap>Space</keycap> key will start a viewer "
"for the selected document. This can be an arbitrary document, not only a "
"&DVI;, PS, PDF or &HTML; document. &kile; takes the &kde; settings into "
"account in order to start an appropriate viewer."
msgstr ""
"Dvojni klik z miško ali tipko <keycap>Space</keycap> bo zagnal "
"pregledovalnik za izbrani dokument. To je lahko poljuben dokument, ne le "
"&DVI;, PS, PDF ali &HTML; dokument. &kile; upošteva nastavitve &kde;-ja, da "
"zažene pravilni pregledovalnik."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3991
#, no-c-format
msgid "User Defined Help"
msgstr "Uporabniško Določena Pomoč"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3993
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Besides this static &tetex;/&texlive; documentation, &kile; also supports a "
"more flexible variable way for help documents. In the <guimenu>Help</"
"guimenu> menu &kile; has a special <guimenu>User help</guimenu> submenu, "
"where the user can add documents of his or her own choice. These can be the "
"most important documents of the &tetex;/&texlive; documentation, or even "
"self-written documents. It is also possible to enter URLs."
msgstr ""
"Poleg statične &tetex;/&texlive; dokumentacije &kile; podpira tudi bolj "
"fleksibilen način za dokumente pomoči. V meniju <guimenu>Help</guimenu> ime "
"&kile; poseben podmeni <guimenu>User help</guimenu>, kjer lahko uporabnik "
"doda dokumente po svoji izbiri. To so lahko najpomombnejši dokumenti &tetex;/"
"&texlive; dokumentacije ali celo dokumenti, ki jih je uporabnik napisal sam. "
"Možno je vnesti tudi URL-je."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4000
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go to <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure Kile...</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Kile</guimenuitem><guilabel>Help</guilabel></"
"menuchoice> and choose the <guibutton>Configure</guibutton> button to "
"configure this <guimenu>User help</guimenu> menu. You can add, remove or "
"move menu entries around, and insert separators to optimize the structure of "
"the menu."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Nastavi "
"Kile...</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Kile</guimenuitem><guilabel>Help</"
"guilabel></menuchoice> in izberite gumb <guibutton>Configure</guibutton>, da "
"konfigurirate ta meni <guimenu>User help</guimenu>. Lahko dodajate, "
"odstranjujete ali premikate vnose in vstavljate ločila, da optimizirate "
"strukturo menija."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:4009
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Dialog: configure user defined help entries</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Pogovorno okno: konfiguriraj vnose uporabnikov za pomoč</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:4015
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Dialog: configure user defined help entries</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Pogovorno okno: konfiguriraj vnose uporabnikov za pomoč</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4020
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pressing the <guibutton>Add</guibutton> button will open another dialog, "
"where you can edit the name of the menu entry, and choose the corresponding "
"file or &URL;. The second button to the right of the text field launches "
"&konqueror;, which can be used to determine the correct &URL;."
msgstr ""
"S pritiskom na gumb <guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton> boste odprli še eno "
"pogovorno okno, kjer lahko urejate imena vnosov v meni in zanje izbirate "
"ustrezne datoteke ali &URL;-je. Drugi gumb na desni strani besedilnega polja "
"zažene &konqueror;, ki ga lahko uporabite, da določite pravilni &URL;."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:4026
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Dialog: add a new helpentry</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pogovorno okno: dodaj nov vnos pomoči</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:4032
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Dialog: add a new helpentry</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno: dodaj nov vnos pomoči</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4037
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After finishing the configuration, all the entries will appear in the "
"<guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu of &kile; as a special menu entry <guimenu>User "
"help</guimenu>."
msgstr ""
"Potem ko končate s konfiguracijo, se bodo vsi vnosi prikazali v &kile;-ovem "
"meniju <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu> kot posebni vnos menija <guimenu>User help</"
"guimenu>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:4041
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Userhelp menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Meni uporabniške pomoči</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:4047
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Userhelp menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Meni uporabniške pomoči</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4058
#, no-c-format
msgid "Credits and License"
msgstr "Zasluge in Licenca"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4060
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kile; is an open-source user-friendly &latex; / &tex; source code editor. "
"It runs on systems that have the &kde; Desktop Environment installed. &kde; "
"is available for several architectures including &Linux; and other Unix-like "
"systems."
msgstr ""
"&kile; je odprtokodni uporabniku prijazen urejevalnik &latex;-ove / &tex;-"
"ove izvorne kode. Deluje na sistemih, ki imajo nameščeno &kde;-jevo Namizno "
"Okolje. &kde; je dostopen za več arhitektur, vključno z &Linux;-om in "
"drugimi sistemi, podobnimi Unixu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4064
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many thanks are owed to the people who strive to continue the &kile; project "
"and to those who sacrifice numerous hours of their time to develop tools we "
"can all use under the &GNU; license. Up-to-date information about "
"contributors can be found in the <guimenuitem>About &kile;</guimenuitem> "
"dialog from the <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Velika hvala ljudem, ki so odločeni, da nadaljujejo projekt &kile; in "
"tistim, ki so žrtvovali številne ure svojega časa, da so razvili orodja, ki "
"jih lahko vsi uporabljamo pod licenco &GNU;. Ažurne informacije o tistih, ki "
"so kaj prispevali, so dostopne v pogovornem oknu <guimenuitem>O &kile;-u</"
"guimenuitem> iz menija <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4070
#, no-c-format
msgid "Many thanks to all those involved!"
msgstr "Velika zahvala vsem, ki so sodelovali!"

